Umubare w'abanduye indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19) mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza wiyongera ku buryo bwihuse, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abanduye icyorezo cya coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza ko mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Urugaga rw'Ubukungu rw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza ari ho bimeze, bikaba byemeza ko nubwo icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri mu bihe bitandukanye bitewe n'igihugu, ariko ko gikomeje kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Dukurikije ubunararibonye bw'Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe bigomba kongera ubwiteganyirize ku kwiyongera kw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazakenera kwitabwaho mu by'ubuzima, cyane cyane mu by'indembe.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, havumbuwe itsinda ry'abantu banduye pneumonia bafite inkomoko idatangajwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'u Bushinwa cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko intandaro y'iki cyorezo ari koronavirusi nshya ubu yitwa coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yiswe icyorezo cya koronavirusi (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko abantu 80% bafite COVID-19 bafite indwara yoroshye, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bw'ibihaha bufite cyangwa budafite pneumonia, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu barwayi bagera kuri 14%, COVID-19 iba indwara ikomeye isaba kuvurirwa mu bitaro mu gihe abasigaye 6% baba barwaye indwara ikomeye isaba kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye ibipimo by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza (UK) maze tugereranya n'iby'Intara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'umuryango w'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza n'uw'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'u Bushinwa, COVID-19 yageze no mu bindi bihugu, kandi uko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyakwirakwijwe mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi muri iki gihe, ni ko kirimo gukwirakwira muri iki gihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu nomero yo ku ya 5 Werurwe ya Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. batangaje ku barwayi ba mbere b'i Burayi bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 hakurikijwe ibisobanuro by'abarwaye OMS.
Muri EU/EEA, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye, batangajwe n'u Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bari bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abanduye COVID-19 bari bamaze kugaragara mu bihugu byose 30 bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza (UK), aho hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 na yo, hari hamaze kuvugwa abantu 39,768 banduye n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye, aho abantu 17,750 banduye n'abantu 1,441 bapfuye bari mu Butaliyani honyine.
Kubona umubare w'abarwaye COVID-19 n'umubare w'abarwaye
Mu kigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC), imibare y'abamaze kwandura COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi hose, iboneka mu masoko yemewe gusa, nk'uko bitangazwa na Minisiteri y'ubuzima y'icyo gihugu, inzego z'ubuzima ku rwego rw'igihugu n'iz'akarere na OMS, buri munsi ihita isubirwamo saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma ibijyanye n'uko COVID-19 iteye muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, no kubigereranya n'uko bimeze mu Butaliyani.
Nk'igereranyo cy'ubwandu bw'abarwaye COVID-19, twabaze iminsi 14 y'ubwandu bushya bw'abarwaye COVID-19, bityo tuzirikana ko COVID-19 yagaragaye mu buryo busanzwe muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'ukwezi kwa mbere kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twagaragaje kandi umubare w'abantu bose bagejejweho amakuru kuri buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo ugereranyije n'abo mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Iterambere rya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Imimerere y'ubwandu bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange yakurikije iy'Intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo 1).
Ku bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 watangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma wiyongera cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibikoresho by'inyongera).
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'ubwiyongere bw'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byagaragaje ko ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwiyongera mu buryo bumwe (Inyandiko y'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Igaragaza ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza byari byamaze gutangazwaho umubare w'abantu bose bagereranywa n'abo mu Butaliyani mu byumweru 3 gusa mbere y'aho cyangwa mbere yaho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abantu baburiwe ko banduye COVID-19 wiyongera cyane mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Uko abantu bagaragaraho ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bigaragaza ko icyorezo cy'iyi ndwara cyateye imbere mu bihugu byose mu buryo bungana.
Ibi ni mu gihe ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, imiterere y'ubuvuzi rusange mu bihugu bitandukanye, ibisobanuro bitandukanye by'abarwayi mu bihugu bitandukanye, n'amabwiriza atandukanye yo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo hamenyekane ko bafite COVID-19, harimo no gupima abahuye n'ubwandu.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu Butaliyani basobanuye ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe muri utwo turere byari byamaze kugera ku bushobozi bwabyo bwose.
Ubu amakuru ku bijyanye no kwakira abantu banduye COVID-19 mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu cyumba cy'indembe aboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ku barwayi 6% na 1% gusa (amakuru ntabwo agaragazwa).
Icyakora, zigomba gukusanywa mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo zuzuze amakuru y'ubugenzuzi agamije cyane cyane umubare w'abantu banditswe barwaye n'umubare w'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini mu kuboneka kw'ibitanda byo kwitaho cyane n'ibitanda byo kwitaho by'ibanze mu Burayi, kuva kuri 29.2 mu Budage kugeza kuri 4.2 ku baturage 100,000 muri Porutugali.
Ibi bisobanuye ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite amikoro aruta cyangwa ari make ugereranyije n'Ubutaliyani (12.5 y'ibitanda byo kwita ku barwayi barembye n'ibyo mu buryo bwo hagati ku baturage 100.000 mu 201011).
Imigaragarire y'ibishushanyo mbonera bijyanye no guhaza ubushobozi bwo kwita ku buzima, hamwe n'ingero kuri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza by'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro bafite ibyago byo kurenza 90% by'ibitanda byo kwitabwaho cyane, bitangwa mu cyiciro cya gatandatu cy'igenzura ry'ibyago ryihuse rya ECDC kuri COVID-19.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu abarwayi benshi babarizwa mu turere tumwe na tumwe mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bw'imyuga ikomeye bikunze kwita ku baturage bo mu turere runaka, amakuru y'abarwayi n'ibitaro by'ubuvuzi bw'imyuga yagombye gushyirwa ku murongo wa Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Ubunararibonye bw'Ubutaliyani n'imiterere y'ibibera mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri gutera imbere mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi barembye cyane bigomba kwitegura ibintu bishobora kubaho mu gihe SARS-CoV-2 yaba ikomeje gukwirakwizwa mu baturage kandi umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakenera ubuvuzi ukazamuka, cyane cyane mu bigo byita ku barembye cyane, nk'uko bimeze mu duce twibasiwe n'icyorezo cy'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ry'ibyago rya vuba aha rya ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, burangwa n'ibikorwa kandi bwuzuye ni ngombwa kugira ngo hatinda ikwirakwizwa rya SARS-COV-2, hamwe no kuva ku buryo bwo kwirinda ukagera ku buryo bwo kugabanya, kubera ko kwiyongera kwihuse kw'umubare w'abanduye bishobora kutabona igihe gihagije cyo gusobanurira, kwemera no guhuza abategura ibyemezo n'ibitaro uko bikwiye mu gihe bidashyirwa mu bikorwa hakiri kare.
Igenzura ryihuta ry'ibyago ryerekana kandi ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari umwanya muto ibihugu bifite wo kongera ingufu mu kurwanya icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya igitutu ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Bitabaye ibyo, birashoboka ko mu minsi cyangwa ibyumweru biri imbere, inzego z'ubuzima zo mu bindi bihugu bigize EU/EEA zizahura n'ikibazo cy'ubwandu bushya bukeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Icyorezo cya Koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3000 no kwanduza abarenga 80.000 mu Bushinwa n'ahandi ku isi, bigatuma abantu bahura n'akaga.
Kimwe na virusi yacyo ihwanye, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bantu ibihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kwandura ivuye ku ducurama kandi igateza ibimenyetso bisa n'ibyo binyuze mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Ariko, COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'ubukana bw'indwara nkeya kurusha SARS ariko irandura cyane kandi igira ingaruka ku bantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko no ku bagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare wihuta wiyongera w'ibitabo byerekana indwara nshya, iyi ngingo igerageza gutanga isesengura ryihariye kandi ryuzuye ry'iki kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi cyihuta.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze ku bijyanye n'indwara, impamvu z'iyi ndwara, virusi, uburyo bwo kuyitahura, uburyo bwo kuyivura, uko ishobora kuvuka, n'uko wayirinda.
N'ubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bigikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko iyi nteruro izadufasha gusobanukirwa no kurandura iyo ndwara iteje akaga.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi tariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye urwibutso rutazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu rugo mu biruhuko byose ndetse no mu byumweru byinshi nyuma y'aho bitewe n'icyorezo cy'indwara nshya.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na virusi ya koronavirusi (CoV) yateje icyorezo cya SARS mu 2003; bityo, ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (WHO) ryise SARS-CoV-2, naho iyi ndwara y'icyorezo yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze gikwirakwira mu gihugu cyose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yateye abantu barenga 80,000 bagaragaweho COVID-19, abarwayi barenga 40,000 bakaba barekuwe kandi abarwayi barenga 3,000 bakaba barapfuye.
OMS iraburira ko COVID-19 ari umwanzi wa rubanda wa 1 kandi ko ishobora kuba ifite imbaraga ziruta iz'iterabwoba.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, inyandiko zirenga 200 zagiye zisohoka kuri COVID-19 harimo isesengura ry'ubwandu, indwara n'ingaruka zayo, gusuzuma no kuvura kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yagaragaje urutonde rw'ubwoko bw'ubwandu bwa virusi yatoranyijwe mu barwayi benshi.
Ubu bushakashatsi bugerageza gushushanya muri make iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi mu gice gishya kandi cyihuta.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tuzajya tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, indwara yo mu burasirazuba bwo hagati ifata imyanya y'ubuhumekero (MERS, icyorezo cyadutse mu 2012).
Nanone, tuzasuzuma ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana no kwirinda iyo ndwara no kumenya uko izaba imeze, ndetse n'ibindi bibazo bimwe na bimwe bikiri ingorabahizi.
CoVs zagiye zireba nk'indwara zitari izica abantu, ahanini zitera hafi 15% by'indwara z'ibicurane 4.
Icyakora, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye na CoVs z'abantu ziteza indwara cyane incuro ebyiri, ni ukuvuga SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zateye icyorezo ku ikubitiro mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, maze bidatinze zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi zirimo uburwayi buteye ubwoba n'impfu.
Bityo rero, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho. Ishusho.1,1, ibibyimba by'ubuhumekero bw'ibihaha bifite inkomoko itaramenyekana byatangajwe bwa mbere muri Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019 kuri Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, hasohotse urutonde rwa CoV.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, havuzwe umuntu wa mbere wanduye yaturutse i Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyo cyorezo cyahise gikwirakwira mu mijyi, intara no mu bihugu byari bikikije icyo gihugu.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, havuzwe ko abashinzwe ubuzima banduye, bikaba byerekana ko abantu bashobora kwandurirana.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan wafunzwe ndetse n'ingendo zose za rusange zirahagarikwa.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere ku ndwara bwatanze amakuru y'uko mu barwayi 41 bagaragaweho n'ubwandu, 21 gusa ari bo bahuye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja ryo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, aho iyi ndwara yatangiriye ku nyamaswa zitazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo ari ikibazo cy'indwara y'indwara ku isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yandikwaga, iyi ndwara yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa bwose no mu bindi bihugu hafi 50 ku isi hose (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo 2).2).
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda bihinduka vuba, ubugari n'uburemere by'icyorezo biracyari mu nzira zo kugaragazwa.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8,866 harimo 4,021 bemeje ko barwaye COVID-19 bwasohoye igishushanyo cy'icyorezo gishya nk'uko gikurikira (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
Abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 bafite imyaka yose, ariko cyane cyane mu bafite imyaka 30-65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47,7%) cy'abantu banduye bari hejuru y'imyaka 50, bake cyane bari munsi y'imyaka 20, kandi abantu 14 gusa banduye bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yanduje abagabo benshi (0.31/100,000) kurusha abagore (0.27/100,000).
