Abarwayi bakunze kugira impiswi zidakunze kumera nk'iz'abandi, bagakomereka cyane mu bihaha, kandi bakagira ibibazo bikomeye by'ubuhumekero (ARDS).
Iyo indwara ya ARDS iravutse, iyo umuntu atazi icyo akora, iyo imvubura igenda yiyongera, n'iyo indwara igenda irushaho gukomera, bituma umwuka wo mu mubiri utongera guhinduka.
Kudakora neza kw'udutsi tw'umwimerere wa I na II bigabanya igipimo cy'imiti y'umwimerere kandi bigatuma umunaniro wo hejuru w'umubiri wiyongera, bityo bikagabanya ubushobozi bw'ibihaha bwo kwaguka no kongera ibyago byo guhagarara kw'ibihaha.
Ku bw'ibyo, akenshi ibipimo bibi cyane by'indwara yo mu gatuza bihuza n'indwara ikomeye cyane.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, isesengura rya mbere ry'indwara ya COVID-19 ryagaragaje ko habonetse gusakara kw'udutsi two mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, guhinduka kw'urwagashya rwa hyaline, no kwinjira kw'udutsi two mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, n'utuvungukira tw'ingingo z'umubiri mu bihaha by'umurwayi wapfuye azize iyi ndwara, bihuye n'indwara y'ubwandu bw'agakoko n'indwara ya SARS na ARDS kandi bisa n'ibya SARS n'abarwayi ba MERS.
Gupima SARS-CoV-2 RNA hifashishijwe ikoranabuhanga rya RT-PCR (reverse-transcriptase polymerase chain reaction) byakoreshejwe nk'ingamba z'ingenzi mu gusuzuma COVID-19.
Icyakora, kubera umubare munini w'ibinyoma by'ibitaragenze neza, bishobora kwihutisha icyorezo, ibimenyetso byo kwa muganga byatangiye gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma (bitacyishingira gusa kuri RT-PCR) mu Bushinwa ku ya 13 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibintu nk'ibyo byabaye no ku barwayi ba SARS.
Ku bw'ibyo, ibintu by'ingenzi kandi by'ingenzi cyane kugira ngo haboneke umuti w'ukuri wo kurwara, ni ugupimisha amateka y'indwara, ibimenyetso byo kwa muganga, ibipimo bya laboratwari n'ibyavuye mu isuzuma ry'imikorere y'izamuka ry'umuriro.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda rya Feng Zhang ryasobanuye uburyo bwo gukoresha uburyo bwa SHERLOCK bushingiye kuri CRISPR mu gutahura SARS-CoV-2, bushobora gutahura ibice bya RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 y'ubwoko bwa 20 × 10-18 mol/L kugeza kuri 200 × 10-18 mol/L (10-100 kopi kuri microlitiro y'ibyinjira) hakoreshejwe igipimo cy'uburebure mu gihe kitageze ku isaha kandi nta gikoresho gikenewe gikenewe.
Twizeye ko ubu buryo bushya bushobora kongera cyane ubudahangarwa n'ubworoherane bw'imiti iyo bugaragarira mu bipimo by'imiti.
Kubera ko nta bumenyi buhagije bafite kuri CoV nshya, abaganga bashobora cyane cyane kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19, mu gihe bagerageza gukoresha uburyo butandukanye bwo kuvura bwakoreshejwe cyangwa bwatanzwe mbere mu kuvura izindi CoVs nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV n'izindi ndwara z'ibyorezo (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe2).2).
Ubu buryo bwo kuvura burimo imiti yica virusi, imiti igabanya ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri, imiti ya steroide, plasma y'abarwayi bakize, imiti y'Abashinwa, n'ubufasha bwo mu mutwe.
Ndetse na plasma y'abarwayi bakize, byasabwe ko yakoreshwa mu kuvura.
Ibigo by'imiti by'imiti biri guhatanira gukora udukingirizo n'udukingirizo tw'iyo virusi.
SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane cyane ibihaha mu ntangiriro, kandi birashoboka ko yibasira n'izindi ngingo zigaragaza ACE2, urugero nk'urw'igifu n'impyiko, ariko ku kigero gito.
Nyamara, indwara yo guhumeka nabi no kunanirwa guhumeka ni byo bibangamiye abarwayi cyane kandi bikaba ari byo bihitana benshi.
Bityo rero, ubufasha bwo guhumeka ni ingenzi cyane mu kugabanya ibimenyetso no kurokora ubuzima kandi burimo kuvura umwuka wa oxygene muri rusange, umwuka wa oxygene ufite umuvuduko mwinshi, guhumeka bidasaza, no guhumeka imashini bihuta bitewe n'uburemere bw'indwara.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye byo mu buhumekero bagomba gufashwa n' uburyo bwo gukoresha umwuka mu mubiri (extracorporeal membrane oxygenation, ECMO), uburyo bwo gukoresha umwuka mu mubiri mu gihe umuntu aba afite ikibazo cy' umutima cyangwa mu buhumekero, ubwo bukaba ari uburyo bwo kuvura umutima n' ubwonko buhindura ibindi bintu, bukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara z' umutima cyangwa z' ubuhumekero zishobora gushyira ubuzima bw' umuntu mu kaga.
Byongeye kandi, kubungabunga igipimo cya electrolyte, kwirinda no kuvura ubwandu bw'ibanze no guturika kw'ibyuma, no kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi ni iby'ingenzi ku barwaye SARS-CoV-2.
Byarazwi ko umuyaga wa cytokine uturuka ku buryo bwo kurwanya indwara bw'umubiri mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Igitutu cya cytokine ni uburyo bwo gusubiza kw'imitsi y'umubiri bugaragarira mu kurekura urukurikirane rw'imiti yitwa cytokines harimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, na MCP-1.
Izi cytokine zituma ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri zisohora umubare munini w'imitwe y'inyongera y'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri (free radicals) ari nayo mpamvu nyamukuru ituma habaho indwara y'indwara y'indwara y'imitsi yo mu bwonko (ARDS) n'uburangare bw'ingingo nyinshi.
Gukomeza ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri ni ingenzi mu kuvura amagufa y'indwara ya cytokine, cyane cyane ku barwayi barwaye indwara ikomeye.
Kortikosteroide na tocilizumab, anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody, zakoreshejwe mu kuvura cytocine storm.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuvura cytocine mu gihe cy'ibiza ni ukugabanya uburyo bw'ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri buturuka ku ngirabuzimafatizo za T; guhagarika IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; gukumira JAK; blinatumomab; kugabanya ibimenyetso bya cytokine 4; n'ababuza HDAC.
Steroide, nk'ibigabanya ubudahangarwa, zakoreshwaga cyane mu kuvura SARS mu kugabanya uburemere bw'ibyangiritse biturutse ku bwandu.
Ariko, imiti ya steroide mu maraso menshi ntiyagira akamaro ku ngaruka zikomeye z'ibihaha ku barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19.
Ahubwo, bishobora gutera ingaruka z'ibanze, cyane cyane uburwayi bw'imitsi y'amaraso, bigira ingaruka zikomeye ku isura.
Nyamara, uburyo bwo gufata kortikosteroid mu gihe gito mu maraso ari hasi kugeza ku rugero ruciriritse bwasabwe gukoreshwa mu buryo bw'ubushishozi ku barwayi ba COVID-19 barembye cyane.
Kugeza igihe iyi nkuru yandikiwe, nta miti ikoreshwa mu kurwanya virusi yari yaremejwe ko ifite akamaro.
Ariko, ikoreshwa ry'imiti ya remdesivir mu maraso, ikoreshwa mu buryo bw'imiti igaragaza imiterere ya nucleotide, ryagaragaye ko rifite akamaro ku murwayi w'umunyamerika urwaye COVID-19.
Remdesivir ni umuti mushya uvura virusi wateguwe na Gilead mu ntangiriro yo kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi ya Ebola na Marlburg.
Nyuma y'aho, remdesivir yagaragaje kandi ko ishobora kubuza izindi virusi za RNA z'ubwoko bumwe harimo virusi za MERS na SARS.
Ishingiye kuri ibyo, Gilead yahaye Ubushinwa iyo miti kugira ngo ikore igeragezwa ku bantu babiri banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibisubizo by'ibyo bigeragezwa birategerejwe cyane.
Byongeye kandi, baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir na ribavirin byatanzwe nk'imiti ishobora kwifashishwa mu kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bukabije.
Iyo umuntu afashwe n' imiti ya lopinavir/ ritonavir, ashobora kugira isesemi, kugira isesemi, kuruka, kwangirika k' umwijima n' izindi ngaruka mbi.
Gukoranaho kw'iyi miti n'indi miti ikoreshwa mu barwayi bigomba gukurikiranwa neza.
Plasma y'abarwayi bakize n'ubwiyongere bw'abashobora kuvurwa
Gukuramo amaraso y'abarwayi bakize indwara yandura, kugira ngo bajye kuvura abandi barwayi barwaye indwara nk'iyo, cyangwa se kugira ngo barinde abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza kwandura iyo ndwara, byatangiye kera cyane.
Koko rero, abarwayi bakira akenshi baba bafite ingano y'umubiri w'ubwirinzi bw'indwara mu maraso yabo.
Imubiri ni immunoglobuline (Ig) ikorwa na B lymphocytes mu kurwanya indwara zitera indwara n'ibindi bintu by'inyamahanga kandi zimenya uturemangingo tw'umwihariko mu ndwara zitera indwara kandi zikababuza gukora.
Hashingiwe kuri ibyo, plasma yakusanyijwe mu maraso y'itsinda ry'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 maze bayashyizwe mu barwayi 10 bari barwaye cyane.
Ibimenyetso byabo byatangiye kugabanuka mu gihe cy'amasaha 24, biherekejwe no kugabanuka kw'ubwiyongere bw'uburwayi bw'umwimerere n'ubwiyongere bw'ibinyabuzima byanduza virusi, ndetse no kuzamura igipimo cy'umwuka wa oxygene mu maraso.
Ariko kandi, hakenewe igenzura no gusobanurwa kugira ngo uburyo bushyireho ikoreshwa ku rwego runini mbere y'uko haboneka uburyo bwihariye bwo kuvura.
Byongeye kandi, bitewe n'ingaruka z'ubuvuzi, hari ingaruka mbi ziterwa no gukoresha plasma zigomba kwitabwaho witonze.
Urugero, abasirikare b'umubiri bashobora gukabya gukabya igisubizo cy'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri no gutera indwara y'indwara ya cytokine, ishobora kuba ishobora gushyira ubuzima mu kaga.
Ubusanzwe, umubare w'abarwayi bafite ubukana bw'umubiri mu maraso uba ari muto, kandi hakenerwa cyane plasma mu kuvura abarwayi barwaye cyane.
Biragoye guhita utunganya no gukora udukingirizo tw'umwihariko ku buryo twakwifashisha mu kurwanya icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Niyo mpamvu ari ngombwa cyane kandi bihuje n'ukuri kwinjiza uturemangingo twa B mu barwayi bakira no kumenya kode z'ibinyabuzima zandikaho udukingirizo dukora cyangwa guhitamo udukingirizo dukora ku mirire y'ingenzi ya virusi.
Muri ubwo buryo, dushobora kongera umusaruro w'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
TCM yakoreshejwe mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye mu Bushinwa mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi.
Ariko kandi, ingaruka zayo zishingiye cyane ku ruvange rw'ibintu byinshi mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'uburyo indwara ivurwa hashingiwe ku mitekerereze ya TCM.
Ibyinshi mu bice by'ingenzi bikora biracyari ibanga cyangwa ntibirasobanuka neza kuko bigoye gukuramo no kugenzura ibyo bice cyangwa imiterere yabyo myiza.
Kugeza ubu, kubera ko nta miti yihariye kandi ikora neza ya COVID-19, TCM yabaye bumwe mu buryo bukomeye bwo kuvura bwagenewe abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa byoroheje cyangwa se abakize icyiciro gikomeye.
Urugero, capsules Shu Feng Jie Du na Lian Hua Qing Wen bagaragaye ko ari ingirakamaro mu kuvura COVID-19.
Imibare yo gukira ku barwayi ba COVID-19 yabonetse mu ntara nyinshi zo mu Bushinwa zakoresheje TCM ku 87% by'abarwayi, harimo Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%), na Hunan (50%), mu gihe intara ya Hubei yakoresheje TCM ku kigero cya 30% gusa cy'abarwayi ba COVID-19, ari yo ifite umubare muto cyane wo gukira (13%).
Icyakora, ibi ni ugupima gusa kuko hari ibindi bintu byinshi bigira ingaruka nko kuba umubare w'abarwayi n'uburyo barembye bigomba kugenzurwa.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boli Zhang na bagenzi be bakoze ubushakashatsi bugamije kugereranya uburyo bwo kuvura bw'ubuvuzi bwo mu burengerazuba (WM) bwonyine n'uburyo buhuriweho bwo kuvura bwa WM na TCM.
Basanze igihe gisabwa kugira ngo umubiri usubire mu buryo, ibimenyetso biveho, no kujya mu bitaro ari kigufi cyane mu itsinda ry'abarwaye bakoresheje WM+TCM kurusha mu itsinda ry'abarwaye bakoresheje WM gusa.
Igitangaje cyane, ni uko ikigero cy'ibimenyetso by'indwara by'indwara (kuva ku zoroheje kugera ku zigoye) cyari hasi cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM kurusha mu itsinda rya WM gusa (7.4% ugereranyije na 46.2%), kandi igipimo cy'abapfa cyari hasi mu itsinda rya WM+TCM kurusha mu itsinda rya WM gusa (8.8% ugereranyije na 39%).
Nyamara, ubuziranenge n'umutekano bya TCM biracyategereje ibizamini by'ubugenzuzi ku bipimo binini no mu bigo byinshi.
Byaba kandi bishishikaje kumenya imiterere y'ibikorwa no gusobanura neza ibice by'ubuvuzi bwa TCM cyangwa imikorere yabyo, niba bishoboka.
Abarwayi bakekwaho cyangwa bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 bakunze kugira ubwoba bw'iyi ndwara yandura cyane ndetse ishobora no kwica, kandi abantu bashyizwe mu kato na bo bakunze kugira umunaniro, ubwigunge n'uburakari.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso by'ubwandu nk'umuriro, hypoxia, no gukorora ndetse n'ingaruka mbi z'imiti nk'ubushyuhe buterwa na kortikosteroid zishobora gutera guhangayika no guhangayika cyane.
Mu gihe cy'intangiriro y'icyorezo cya SARS, havuzwe indwara nyinshi zo mu mutwe zirimo kwiheba bikabije, guhangayika, guhindagurika mu byiyumvo, kurakara mu bwenge, ibimenyetso by'indwara zo mu mutwe, kwiheba ndetse no kwiyahura.
Gukurikirana abantu bahuye n'indwara no gushyira abantu mu kato, nk'imwe mu ngamba z'ubuzima rusange zo guhangana n'icyorezo cya COVID-19, bishobora gutuma abantu barushaho kugira impungenge no kwishinja ingaruka z'ubwandu, izo gahunda zo gushyira abantu mu kato no kubaciraho iteka ku miryango yabo n'inshuti zabo.
Bityo, ubuvuzi bwo mu mutwe bugomba gutangwa ku barwayi ba COVID-19, abantu bakekwaho kuba barwaye, n'abantu bahuye na bo kimwe n'abaturage muri rusange babukeneye.
Ubufasha mu by'imitekerereze bugomba kuba bukubiyemo gushyiraho amatsinda y'abahanga mu by'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe, gushyikirana mu buryo busobanutse kandi buhoraho n'amakuru y'ukuri ku byerekeye icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 n'amabwiriza y'uburyo bwo kuvurwa, no gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga by'umwuga mu kwirinda kwegera abandi.
Inkingo z'ingirakamaro ni ingenzi mu guhagarika uburyo bw'indwara ziva mu nyamaswa no ku bantu banduye zigera ku nyamaswa zanduye kandi akenshi zikunganira ubuvuzi bwa virusi mu kurwanya ibyorezo biterwa na virusi zigenda zigaragara.
Hakozwe ingamba zo gukora inkingo z'ibinyabutabire S kugira ngo haboneke abasirikare barwanya SARS-CoV barinda umubiri kandi/cyangwa barinda umubiri igihe kirekire.
Inkingo z'ubuzima zidakomanya SARS zagiye zisuzumwa ku matungo yo mu nyamaswa.
Icyakora, nta n'ubwo hashobora kuboneka urukingo rw' ubu bwoko mu bantu bageze mu zabukuru n' abantu bashobora kuba bafite ibyago byo gupfa, cyangwa ngo hagaragazwe uburyo bakingira indwara z' ubwandu bwa virusi zo muri zo, mbere y'uko hatangira ubushakashatsi ku barwayi.
Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko SARS yarangiye mu myaka 17 ishize kandi nta murwayi mushya wigeze avugwa kuva icyo gihe.
Ku rundi ruhande, abantu bagaragaye rimwe na rimwe kandi mu matsinda y'indwara ya MERS bakomeje kugaragara mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati kandi bakwirakwira mu tundi turere bitewe n'uko hari inyamaswa z'inyamaswa zikomeje kuba inkomoko y'indwara mu turere dutuwe n'abantu.
Uburyo bwo gukingira MERS bwashyizweho hakoreshejwe virusi yabuze ingufu, plazmide za ADN, ibikoresho bitwara virusi, nanoparticles, uduce tumeze nka virusi n'uduce tw'ibinyabutabire twongeye guhuzwa, kandi zimwe muri zo zashakishijwe mu nyamaswa.
Gushyiraho urukingo rwizewe kandi rukora neza rw'urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2 ku bantu batanduye ni igikorwa cyihutirwa kandi cy'ingenzi mu kurwanya icyorezo gikomeje.
Icyakora, biragoye gutsinda iki kibazo kubera igihe kirekire (umwimerere w'amezi 18) gikenewe mu gukora urukingo n'imiterere y'ubwoko bw'ubwoko bwa CoV.
Nk'indwara nshya, COVID-19 yatangiye kugaragaza uburyo bwose bwo kwivuza mu bihumbi by'abarwayi.
Akenshi, abarwayi bashobora gukira buhoro buhoro nta ngaruka z'uburwayi.
Ariko, kimwe na SARS na MERS, COVID-19 nayo ifitanye isano n'uburwayi n'urupfu mu barwayi bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
Ni yo mpamvu kubaka igishushanyo mbonera cy'uko indwara ishobora kuzafata igihe kirekire ari ngombwa ku nzego z'ubuzima kugira ngo zihe serivisi z'ibanze, cyane cyane mu turere tudafite amikoro ahagije.
Hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe kugeza ubu, ibintu bikurikira bishobora kugira ingaruka cyangwa bikaba bifitanye isano n'ibyago byo kurwara COVID-19 (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe ya33):
Imyaka: Imyaka ni yo yari igipimo cy'ingenzi cyane cyerekana ko SARS ishobora kuvurwa, ibyo bikaba ari ukuri no kuri COVID-19.
COVID-19 yibasiye cyane cyane abantu bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 30-65 aho 47.7% by'abo barwaye bari hejuru y'imyaka 50 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8.866 nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Abarwayi basabwaga kwitabwaho cyane bagaragaraga cyane ko babaga bafite izindi ndwara n'ubundi bubabare kandi bari bakuze cyane kurusha abatarwaye (mu kigereranyo cy'imyaka 66 ugereranyije na 51), ibyo bikaba byerekana ko kuba umuntu akuze ari kimwe mu bintu bigira ingaruka ku barwaye COVID-19.
Igitsina: SARS-CoV-2 yanduje abagabo benshi kurusha abagore (0.31/100,000 ugereranyije na 0.27/100,000), nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Indwara z'uburwayi n'izindi ndwara z'uburwayi: Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara umutima no kugira ibibazo by'imitima.
Imirimo y'umutima ni yo yari intandaro y'urupfu mu barwaye SARS.
Byavuzwe ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kwihuza na cholangiocytes ifite ACE2-positive, bishobora gutera ibibazo by'umwijima ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ni ngombwa kumenya ko imyaka y'umuntu n'indwara ifitanye isano rya bugufi, kandi bishobora kuba byatera ibibazo hagati yabo.
Ibimenyetso bya laboratwari bidasanzwe: igipimo cya C-reactive protein (CRP) mu maraso kigaragaza uburemere bw'uburwayi cyangwa imvune mu mitsi kandi byemejwe ko bishobora kuba impamvu yo kubara indwara, igisubizo ku miti, ndetse no gukira.
Hari kandi igitekerezo cyo guhuza igipimo cya CRP n'uburemere n'imiterere y'indwara ya COVID-19.
Byongeye kandi, kongera lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), na creatine kinase (CK) nabyo bishobora gufasha mu guhanura ingaruka.
Izi enzymes zigaragara cyane mu ngingo nyinshi, cyane cyane mu mutima no mu mwijima, kandi zisohotse mu gihe imyanda yangiritse.
Bityo rero, ni ibimenyetso bisanzwe bigaragaza ko umutima cyangwa impyiko zidakora neza.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'indwara: radiographie y'igifu n'uko ibimenyetso by'indwara bigenda byiyongera mu gihe runaka, bigomba kwitabwaho hamwe n'ibindi bibazo byo kumenya ingaruka n'ibibazo bya COVID-19.
Gukoresha imiti yo mu bwoko bwa steroide: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, imiti yo mu bwoko bwa steroide ikoreshwa mu kurwanya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, akenshi ikoreshwa nk'umuti w'inyongera mu ndwara zandura, kugira ngo igabanye uburemere bw'indwara ziterwa n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
Kubera ko imiti ya kortikosteroide yabaga mu maraso menshi yakoreshwaga cyane mu barwayi ba SARS bari bafite uburwayi bukomeye, benshi mu barokotse bari bafite uburwayi bw'amagufwa bubahata mu gihe cy'ubuzima bwabo bwose kandi ubuzima bwabo bukaba bubi.
Ni yo mpamvu, niba ari ngombwa, imiti ya steroïde ikwiye gukoreshwa ku gipimo gito kandi mu gihe gito ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Umunaniro wo mu mutwe: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19 abarwayi benshi bagize umunaniro udasanzwe kuko akenshi bagiye bamara igihe kirekire bari mu kato kandi bafite impungenge nyinshi, ndetse no kubona abo mu miryango yabo n'abandi barwayi bapfa.
Ni ngombwa gutanga ubufasha bw'imitekerereze n'ubufasha bw'igihe kirekire kugira ngo aba barwayi babashe kuva mu bibazo no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe kugeza ubu, COVID-19 isa n'aho ifite ibimenyetso bitandukanye n'iby'indwara ya SARS.
Uretse kwigana mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwigana mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru kandi igatera ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubwandu, kimwe n'izindi CoVs zitera ibicurane bisanzwe.
Ni yo mpamvu abarwayi banduye mu cyiciro cya mbere cyangwa igihe cyo kwinjiza virusi mu mubiri wabo bashobora kubyara virusi nyinshi mu gihe bakora imirimo yabo ya buri munsi, bigatuma bigorana cyane kugenzura icyorezo.
Ariko, SARS-CoV yafashwe nk'igenda irandura iyo abarwayi barwaye cyane, mu gihe ubwandu bwinshi butari bwabaho mu cyiciro cya mbere.
Bityo rero, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu kirakomeye cyane kandi biragoye kucyirinda kurusha icyorezo cya SARS.
Muri iki gihe mu Bushinwa hakorwa ingamba zikomeye zirimo gufunga Wuhan n'indi mijyi ihakikije no gushyira mu kato abantu hafi ya bose mu cyizere cyo guhagarika ikwirakwizwa rya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo ibyo bikorwa byangije cyane ubukungu n'ibindi bice by'igihugu, umubare w'abarwayi bashya uragenda ugabanuka, bikaba bigaragaza ko icyorezo cyagabanutse.
Ibipimo by'ibyishimo ni uko icyorezo kizarangira muri Werurwe kandi igihe cyo kugabanuka k'icyorezo kizamara amezi 3-4.
Icyakora, hari izindi mpuguke zitari zifite icyizere nk'icyo.
Paul Hunter, et al., bagereranyije ko COVID-19, isa n'iyandura cyane kurusha SARS, itazarangira mu 2020.
Ira Longini, et al., bashyizeho uburyo bwo guhanura uko icyorezo kizarangira kandi batanga igitekerezo cy'uko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura bibiri bya gatatu by'abatuye isi.
Itsinda ry'abantu bo muri Canada batangaje ko SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu bipimo byo hagati mu muriro no mu muhogo by'abarwayi bakize kandi bavuye mu bitaro mu byumweru 2 mbere yaho, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko virusi nshya yagaragaye ishobora kuba icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane.
Icyakora, mu Bushinwa hagaragaye ibimenyetso by'ibimenyetso bishimishije bishingiye ku kugabanuka kw'umubare w'abanduye bashya, bigaragaza ko ingamba zo muri iki gihe zishobora kuba zaragize icyo zigeraho.
Ebola yari yitezweho mbere na mbere gutera ubwandu bwa miliyoni imwe n'impfu zigera kuri miliyoni imwe n'igice.
Icyakora, binyuze mu kato gakomeye no gushyira abantu mu kato, amaherezo iki cyorezo cyashyizwe mu maboko.
Birashoboka, kimwe na SARS-CoV, ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugabanuka mu kwanduza amaherezo ikaza gupfa cyangwa ikaza kuba virusi itatera indwara cyane ikanabaho n'abantu.
Kugereranya icyorezo cya COVID-19 n'icya SARS na MERS biratangazwa hasi (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo cya 55)).
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura cyane binyuze mu gukorora cyangwa guhumeka, kandi birashoboka ko ishobora kwandura no mu buryo butaziguye n'ibintu byanduye virusi.
Iyi virusi kandi yabonetse mu myanda, bikaba byerekana ko hashobora kubaho uburyo bushya bwo kuyandura binyuze mu myanda.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa ku barwayi 138 bwagaragaje ko 41% by'abarwayi bashobora kuba baratewe n'indwara zo mu bitaro, harimo abarwayi 17 bari barwaye izindi ndwara mbere ndetse n'abakozi 40 bo mu nzego z'ubuzima.
Bityo rero, hakwiye gushyirwa ingamba zikomeye mu kurinda abantu, cyane cyane abatanga ubufasha mu by'ubuzima, abakozi bo mu nzego z'imibereho, abagize umuryango, abakozi bakorana, ndetse n'abareba ibintu bagirana imishyikirano n'abarwayi cyangwa abantu banduye.
Uburyo bwa mbere bwo kwirinda bwakoreshwa mu kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura ni ukwambara udupfukamunwa; gukoresha udupfukamunwa two mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi n'udupfukamunwa two mu bwoko bwa N95 (series # 1860s) bifasha mu kugabanya ikwirakwizwa rya virusi.
Udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi dutuma udutonyanga tw'amazi tw'umuntu ushobora kuba yaranduye tutabasha gutembera mu kirere cyangwa ngo tumumare ku bintu, aho bishobora kwanduza abandi.
Ariko, udupfukamunwa N95 (series # 1860s) ni two twonyine dushobora kurinda umuntu guhumeka virusi z'ibice bito bya 10 na 80 nm, aho virusi 5% gusa ari zo zishobora kwinjira burundu; SARS-CoV-2 imeze kimwe na SARS-CoV mu bunini kandi zombi zifite hafi 85 nm.
Kubera ko uduce dushobora kwinjira no mu masike eshanu z'ubuvuzi zashyizwe hamwe, abashinzwe ubuzima bahura n'abarwayi mu buryo butaziguye bagomba kwambara masike N95 (series # 1860s) ariko ntibagire n'amasike y'ubuvuzi.
Usibye udupfukamunwa, abashinzwe ubuzima bagombye kwambara imyenda yo kwiherera kugira ngo barusheho kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura virusi.
Nanone virusi ishobora kwandurira umuntu ikoresheje amaso.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yanduye SARS-CoV-2 nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95; virusi ishobora kuba yarinjiye mu mubiri we binyuze mu maso ye yanduye.
Bityo, abatanga ubuvuzi bagomba kandi kwambara udukingirizo cyangwa amadarubindi arebana n'amaso ari ku maso, igihe bakorana n'abarwayi.
Ku baturage muri rusange bo mu turere twugarijwe cyangwa dushobora kuba twugarijwe, birasabwa cyane ko buri wese akaraba intoki akoresheje isabune zanduza kenshi kurusha uko bisanzwe, kugerageza kuguma mu nzu mu kwishyira mu kato no kugabanya imikoranire n'abantu bashobora kuba banduye.
Abantu bagomba kuba ahantu hateganye n'umurwayi, ntibagire aho bahurira na metero imwe.
Izi ngamba ni uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura no kwirinda ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 yaje nk'agakoko gashya ku isi y'abantu, kuba ari ko gakomoka kuri SARS-CoV nk'uko byatangajwe ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 byagombye kuba byaratumye Ubushinwa butera ingamba zikomeye zishingiye ku kwibuka cyane icyorezo cya SARS mu 2003.
Icyakora, tariki ya 19 Mutarama 2020 ni bwo umuyobozi w'ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara mu mujyi wa Wuhan yahumurije abaturage ababwira ko virusi nshya ifite ubwandu buke kandi ko ubushobozi bwo kubyara bw'umuntu ku wundi bufite aho bugarukira, kandi ko kwirinda no gukumira iyi ndwara atari ikibazo.
Ubu butumwa bworoheje cyane impungenge z'abaturage, cyane cyane mu gihe igihugu cyose cyari gitegura Umunsi Mukuru w'Igitumba, kandi igihe gikomeye cyo gukumira indwara ku kigero cyacyo gito muri Wuhan cyari cyarabujijwe.
Ibi bigo byo kurwanya indwara mu Bushinwa bishobora gufata isomo rikomeye muri iki gikorwa kandi bigakora ibintu bikomeye mu gihe kizaza.
Urugero, izi nzego zagombye (1) kwitonda cyane mu gutangaza amakuru mu ruhame kuko buri jambo rifite agaciro ku baturage kandi rishobora guhindura imyumvire n'ibyemezo byabo; (2) kwita cyane ku makuru adasanzwe ava mu mavuriro aho gutegereza raporo zisanzwe ziturutse ku baganga cyangwa abayobozi; (3) gushyiraho ingamba zikomeye mu kwirinda icyorezo gishobora kuba mu gihe cy'icyiciro cyacyo cya mbere aho kugerageza guhumuriza abaturage; (4) gushyiraho imyitozo igamije kandi ifite ingaruka nziza mu buryo bworoshye kugira ngo abantu barusheho gusobanukirwa iby'indwara z'ibyorezo kandi bagerageze kandi banonosore uburyo bwo guhangana n'ibyo bibazo mu muryango.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 giterwa n'agakoko gashya ka SARS-CoV-2 cyatangiye mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019.
Mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, cyakwirakwiriye mu Bushinwa bwose no mu bindi bihugu hafi 50 ku isi hose mu gihe twandikaga iyi nkuru.
Kubera ko iyi virusi isa cyane na SARS-CoV kandi ibimenyetso byayo bikaba bisa na COVID-19 na SARS, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatumye abantu bumva ko SARS igenda isubira.
Icyakora, hari itandukaniro rikomeye hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, ari na byo bikenewe cyane mu gukumira icyorezo no kuvura abarwayi.
COVID-19 ifata abantu bageze mu zabukuru cyane kurusha urubyiruko, abagabo bakaba ari bo bayifata cyane kurusha abagore, kandi ubukana n'umubare w'abapfa biri hejuru cyane ku bantu bageze mu zabukuru kurusha urubyiruko.
SARS ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cy'abapfa kurusha COVID-19 (10.91% ugereranyije na 1.44%).
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bandura virusi n'ubwo baba badafite ibimenyetso mu gihe abarwayi ba SARS bo ubusanzwe babikora iyo barwaye cyane, ibyo bikaba bituma gukumira ikwirakwizwa rya COVID-19 bigorana cyane kuruta SARS.
Ibi bisobanuye mu rugero runaka impamvu SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira cyane mu buryo bwihuse kandi ku buryo bwagutse kurusha SARS-CoV.
Ibipimo bisanzwe bya RNA byo gupima SARS-CoV-2 bishobora kuba ari nta cyo bitanga ku barwayi bamwe na bamwe ba COVID-19.
Ku rundi ruhande, abarwayi bakize bashobora kongera kugaragaza ko banduye.
Ibyo byagaragaye byongera cyane ibyago byo gukwirakwira kwa virusi.
Kubera iterambere ryihuta cyane ry'ubushakashatsi kuri COVID-19, hari ibibazo byinshi bikomeye bigomba gukemurwa, ni ibi bikurikira:
SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse he?
Nubwo 96% by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bya SARS-CoV-2 byabonetse ko bihuriye hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na CoVs ebyiri zimeze nka SARS-CoV zo mu ducurama, ntabwo dushobora kwemeza ko SARS-CoV-2 ikomoka mu ducurama.
Ni ibihe biremwa by'ibinyabuzima byanduje virusi ivuye ku nyamaswa ya mbere, urugero nk'ibinyabwoya, ikaza ku bantu?
Iyo tutazi ibisubizo bya #1 na 2, ntituba dushobora guhagarika kwanduza neza, kandi icyorezo gishobora kongera kuba igihe icyo ari cyo cyose.
Nubwo uburyo bwo gukora imiterere y'ibinyabuzima n'ubw'ibinyabuzima bwagaragaje ko SARS-CoV-2 ifata ACE2, ni gute koko virusi yinjira mu bice by'imiyoboro y'ubuhumekero igateza impinduka z'indwara zikurikiraho?
Ese iyo virusi ifata kandi ingirabuzimafatizo z'izindi ngingo zisohora ACE2?
Nitudafite ibisubizo bisobanutse by'ibyo bibazo, ntituzashobora guhita tumenya indwara neza kandi tukayivuza neza.
Ni iki kizakurikiraho?
Ni gute virusi ihinduka mu buryo bw'imiterere yayo mu gihe yandurira mu bantu?
Mbese, bizakwira isi yose, cyangwa bizakendera nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS cyangwa bizongera kugaruka rimwe na rimwe nk'uko byagenze kuri grippe?
Ni ngombwa ariko bishobora gufata igihe runaka kugira ngo dushake ibisubizo by'ibibazo byavuzwe haruguru hamwe n'ibindi byinshi.
Ariko kandi, uko ibyo byadusaba amafaranga yaba angana kose, nta kindi twakora uretse guhagarika icyorezo vuba uko bishoboka kose, maze ubuzima bwacu bukagaruka nk'uko bwari bumeze.
Inkomoko ya zoonotique ya koronavirusi y'abantu
Impinduka n'amahinduka byagiye bituma koronavirusi n'izindi virusi zibyitwaramo, harimo n'abantu, bikomeza kubaho mu gihe cy'imyaka ibihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, virusi ebyiri za CoVs (HCoVs) z'abantu zari zizwiho gutera indwara zoroheje, urugero nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze (SARS) n'icy'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS) byahinduye isura, bigaragaza ukuntu ubwandu bwa HCoV bushobora kuba bubi cyane kandi bugashyira ubuzima bw'umuntu mu kaga.
Igisasu cya SARS-CoV-2 cyagaragaye mu Bushinwa bwo hagati mu mpera za 2019 cyongeye gushyira CoVs mu mwanya w'ibanze maze kidutangaza kubera ko cyandura cyane ariko kikaba kitatera indwara cyane ugereranyije na SARS-CoV yo mu bwoko bwacyo.
Indwara ya HCoV ni zoonote kandi gusobanukirwa inkomoko ya zoonote ya HCoV byadufasha cyane.
HCoV nyinshi zaturutse ku ducurama aho zitera indwara.
Hari n'abasanzwe bamenyekanye bafite ibyari by'ibanze bya HCoVs.
Kumenya inyamaswa z'ingenzi cyane bifite ingaruka zigaragara mu kwirinda indwara z'abantu.
Gushakisha imikoranire ya CoV n'umurwaza mu nyamaswa bishobora kandi kuvamo ubushishozi bw'ingenzi ku ndwara ya CoV mu bantu.
Muri iyi nkuru, turatanga ibikubiye mu bumenyi buhari ku byerekeye za HCoVs ndwi, twibanda ku mateka y'ubushakashatsi bwabo ndetse n'inkomoko yabo yo mu bwoko bw'inyamaswa n'ubwandu bw'ubwoko bw'inyamaswa.
Icy'ingenzi, ni ugereranya no gutandukanya za HCoV zitandukanye dushingiye ku ihinduka rya virusi n'igikorwa cyo kongera guhuza ingirabuzimafatizo.
Muri iyi nkuru, turaganira ku cyorezo cya CoV disease 2019 (COVID-19).
Byongeye kandi, ibisabwa kugira ngo umuntu ahindure nyir'urugo neza n'ibikubiye mu iterambere ry'agakoko gatera indwara ku buremere bw'indwara nabyo birashimangirwa.
Koronavirusi (CoVs) ni zo zigize umuryango wa Coronaviridae, ugizwe n'itsinda ry'indwara za virusi za RNA z'impimbano, zifite imiterere myiza, z'umugozi umwe.
Iyi virusi ifite genome nini cyane yo hagati ya 26 na 32 kilobases mu virusi za RNA, yiswe CoVs kubera imiterere yayo imeze nk'ikamba mu gihe cy'ubushakashatsi bw'intoki.
Ku bijyanye n'imiterere, CoVs zifite genomes zidashyizwe mu bice kandi zifite imiterere y'imiterere isa n'iyazo.
Hafi 2/3 by'ubwoko bwa genome burimo ibice bibiri binini by'ibisate by'ibisate by'ibisate by'ibisate (ORF1a na ORF1b), bihindurwa muri pp1a na pp1ab replicase polyproteins.
Iyo poroteyine nyinshi zikurwamo, haboneka poroteyine 16 zitagira ingingo, zitwa nsp1~16.
Igice gisigaye cya genome kirimo ORFs z'indangamuntu z'ibinyabuzima, harimo spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) na nucleoprotein (N).
Hari umubare w'indangamuntu z'ibinyabutabire byihariye kandi zandikishwa n'indangamuntu zitandukanye za CoVs.
Hashingiwe ku itandukaniro ry'urukurikirane rw'ibinyabuzima, CoVs zigabanyijwemo amoko ane (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), muri yo amoko beta-CoV arimo HCoVs nyinshi kandi agabanyijwemo amoko ane (A, B, C na D).
Ubuhamya bw'ibinyabuzima bwagaragaje ko ibishyimbo n'imbeba ari zo nkomoko y'ibinyabuzima bya alpha-CoV na beta-CoVs, mu gihe inyoni ari zo nkomoko y'ibinyabuzima bya gamma-CoV na delta-CoV.
Mu myaka ibihumbi, CoVs yagiye igenda irenga imipaka y'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima, kandi zimwe muri zo zaje kuba udusimba tw'ingenzi dutera indwara ku bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hari CoVs zirindwi z'abantu (HCoVs) zizwi.
Muri zo harimo HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni za alpha-CoVs.
Izindi beta-CoV eshanu harimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus ikomeye ifata imyanya y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV), coronavirus y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS-CoV) na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 akenshi bitera ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'icyorezo cy'ibicurane cyangwa isesemi.
Ibinyuranye n'ibyo, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 iheruka kumenyekana ifite ubushobozi bwo gutera indwara, iteza ubwandu bukomeye bw'umuyoboro wo munsi w'ubuhumekero ku barwayi benshi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kugira indwara y'ubuhumekero bukomeye (ARDS) n'ibimenyetso byo hanze y'ibihaha.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwavumbuwe mu mwuka w'umura w'abarwayi barwaye ibicurane mu myaka ya za 60.
Kuva icyo gihe, hari ubumenyi bwinshi bwongerewe binyuze mu bushakashatsi bwimbitse ku HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi bitera ibimenyetso byo kwihagarika.
Koko rero, igitekerezo cyari cyemewe na benshi ko ubwandu bwa HCoVs muri rusange nta ngaruka bufite kugeza igihe icyorezo cya SARS cyadutse.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byateye abantu benshi mu mateka y'iki gihe, cyanduza abantu barenga 8000, cyahitanye abagera kuri 10%.
Hashize imyaka icumi, indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (Middle East respiratory syndrome) (MERS) yateye icyorezo cy'indwara idakira mu Karere ka Arabiya, ikwirakwira hirya no hino ku isi.
Iyi virusi nshya ya HCoV (2019-nCoV) yo mu mwaka wa 2019, nyuma yaje guhindurirwa izina yitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni yo nyirabayazana w'icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) gikomeje, cyahitanye abantu barenga 3.120 kandi cyanduza abantu barenga 91.000 guhera ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Abantu bagiye bamenyekana kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kigiye kuza.
Izo virusi zirindwi zose za HCoV zifite inkomoko zo mu nyamaswa ziva mu ducurama, imbeba cyangwa inyamaswa zo mu rugo.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi byemeza ko HCoVs zose zaturutse ku nguge, aho virusi ziba zifite ubushobozi bwo kwihanganira imimerere y'ubwoko runaka kandi ntizitera indwara, ariko zigaragaza ko zinyuranye cyane.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateje ibibazo bikomeye mu buvuzi, mu bumenyi, mu mibanire y'abantu no mu mibereho myiza y'abantu mu Bushinwa no ku isi hose.
Gushakisha inkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoVs bitanga urwego rwo gusobanukirwa amateka ya kamere, imbaraga zitwara no guhagarika ibintu byo gusimbuka kw'amoko.
Ibi kandi bishobora kuyobora cyangwa koroshya gushakisha ahantu ho kubika, hagati no kongera inyamaswa z'abashiki ba SARS-CoV-2, bifite ingaruka zikomeye mu gukumira ibyago byo gukwirakwira mu gihe kizaza.
Muri iki cyegeranyo, turatanga ibisobanuro by'uko virusi za HCoV ziterwa n'inyamaswa, uko zikwirakwira hagati y'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima n'uko zitewe.
By'umwihariko, turashimangira kandi tukaganira ku ngingo rusange y'uko virusi z'ababyeyi ba HCoVs ubusanzwe zitandura mu binyabuzima biba mu mazi yazo, ariko zikaba zishobora kwandura nyuma yo kwanduza ubwoko bushya.
Nanone kandi twasuzumye ko iterambere rya HCoV rigaragaza ko ubwandu bukomeza kwiyongera, akenshi iyo ubwandu bugabanutse, ubwandu bugenda bugabanuka.
Ibyavuye mu cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 na byo byiganjemo muri iyi nkuru.
Imiryango ya CoVs yo mu nyamaswa yamenyekanye kuva mu mpera za 1930.
Mbere y'uko HCoV-229E yo mu bwoko bwa B814 ikorwa bwa mbere ku ndwara y'umukozo y'abarwayi bari baranduye imbeho, za CoVs zitandukanye zari zarakorewe mu nyamaswa zitandukanye zafashwe n'iyo ndwara, harimo inkoko, imbeba, inka, ingurube, injangwe n'imbwa.
Mu myaka mirongo ishize, havumbuwe za HCoV zirindwi.
Incamake y'amateka y'ibyavumbuwe na HCoV mu buryo bw'igihe (Imbonerahamwe ya 1) yaba ari iy'inyigisho kandi y'inyigisho.
Igisasu cya mbere cya HCoV-229E cyadukanye mu gice cyo mu bwonko cy'abarwayi bafite ubwandu bw'igice cyo hejuru cyo mu bwonko mu mwaka wa 1966, nyuma gihindurwa kugira ngo gikure mu bisasu byo mu bihaha bya WI-38.
Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaje ibimenyetso by'ibicurane bisanzwe, birimo umutwe, guhumura, kumva batameze neza no kuribwa mu muhogo, bafite umuriro no gukorora mu bantu 10~20% by'abanduye.
Nyuma y'aho mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yavanywe mu turemangingo no mu mikorobe y'ibisimba by'imishwi.
Imiterere y'ubwandu bwa HCoV-OC43 isa n'igaragaza ibimenyetso nk'ibya HCoV-229E, bikaba ari ibimenyetso bidashobora gutandukanywa no kwandura izindi ndwara z'ibiyobyabwenge byo mu nzira y'ubuhumekero nka virusi ya influenza A na rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi birakwirakwizwa ku isi hose, kandi bikunze kwandura cyane cyane mu gihe cy'itumba mu bihe by'ikirere cyifashe.
Ubusanzwe, igihe cyo kwinjiza iyi virusi zombi ni igihe kiri munsi y'icyumweru kimwe, gikurikirwa n'uburwayi bw'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko byemejwe n'ubushakashatsi ku bantu b'abakorerabushake, abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza banduye HCoV-229E bagize imbeho idakomeye.
Gusa abarwayi bake bafite ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara bagaragaje ubwandu bukomeye bw'imiyoboro y'ubuhumekero.
SARS, nanone izwi ku izina rya atypical pneumonia, ni yo ndwara ya mbere y'icyorezo yandujwe na HCoV mu mateka y'abantu kandi igaragaza ko ari SARS-CoV, HCoV ya gatatu yavumbuwe.
Icyorezo cya mbere cya SARS cyatangiye mu mpera za 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateje abantu 8,096 banduye na 774 bapfuye, cyakwirakwira mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane myinshi.
Usibye abafite ubwandu bukomeye, byemejwe ko buri murwayi ashobora kubyara abarwayi babiri, igihe cyo kubyara ni iminsi 4 kugeza ku minsi 7 kandi ko virusi igera ku rwego rwo hejuru ku munsi wa 10 w'uburwayi.
Abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV mu ntangiriro barwaye indwara yo kubabara mu mutwe, kubabara umutwe, umuriro, kugira ibyiyumvo bibi no guhindagurika, bakurikirwa no guhumeka nabi, gukorora no guhumeka nabi nk'ibimenyetso by'ihindagurika.
Lymphopenia, ibibazo by'imikorere y'umwijima, no kwiyongera kwa creatine kinase ni bimwe mu bibazo bikunze kugaragara muri laboratwari mu gihe cy'indwara ya SARS.
Ibyangiritse mu nkokora z'umura, kwiyongera kw'uturemangingo tw'uruhu no kwiyongera kw'udutsi tw'utubumbe na byo byarabonetse ku barwayi ba SARS.
Abagera kuri 20 kugeza kuri 30% by'abarwayi nyuma y'aho bakenera kwitabwaho cyane no gukoreshwa ibyuma by'umwuka.
Uretse mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, inzego nyinshi zirimo urwungano ngogozi, impyiko n'impyiko nazo zishobora kwandura muri izo ndwara zikomeye, akenshi ziherekezwa n'umwuzure wa cytokine, ushobora kwica cyane cyane ku barwayi bafite ubudahangarwa.
Iyi virusi yabanje kuvumburwa mu cyuma cy'umuntu wafashwe mu bihaha, cyakozwe ku muntu w'incuti y'umurwayi wa mbere wari waragiye muri Hong Kong avuye i Guangzhou.
Kuva icyo gihe, hashyizweho imbaraga nyinshi mu bushakashatsi ku bijyanye na HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yavanwe mu mwana w'amezi 7 wo mu Buholandi mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2004.
Byatangiye byemejwe ko bikunze kugaragara ku bana bato, abageze mu za bukuru n'abarwayi bafite ubwirinzi buke bafite indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Kurwara coryza, conjunctivitis, umuriro, na bronchiolitis ni ibisanzwe mu ndwara ziterwa na HCoV-NL63.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bw'ubwigenge bwasobanuye iby'ubwigenge bwa virusi imwe mu cyiciro cy'umuhozi cy'umwana w'umuhungu w'amezi 8 urwaye pneumoniya mu Buholandi.
Nubwo yagaragaye mu Buholandi, mu by'ukuri ikwirakwizwa ku isi hose.
Hagenwe ko HCoV-NL63 igira uruhare ku 4.7% by'indwara z'ubuhumekero, kandi ubwiyongere bwayo bukaba bufata umwanya munini mu mpeshyi, mu rugaryi no mu itumba.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano n'indwara y'uruhu ituma umuntu atabasha kuruka, nanone izwi nka croup.
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yavanywe ku mugabo w'imyaka 71 wari waragiye mu bitaro arwaye pneumonia na bronchiolitis muri Hong Kong.
Uretse pneumoniya n'uburwayi bw'umura bwo mu mazuru, HCoV-HKU1 byavuzwe ko bifitanye isano no gukomera cyane kw'indwara y'ubuhumekero.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 yabonetse ku isi hose, iteza indwara zo mu buhumekero zitari nyinshi.
Izi HCoV enye zose zanduye mu baturage zahuye neza n'abantu kandi muri rusange ntizikunze guhinduka ngo zitere indwara zikomeye, nubwo impanuka zabayeho ku mpamvu zitamenyekanye, nk'uko byagenze mu gihe gito cyane cy'ubwoko bw'indwara bw'ubwoko bwa HCoV-NL63 bufite ubukana bwinshi, buherutse kuvugwa ko butera indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi mu Bushinwa.
Muri rusange, iyo izi HCoVs zibonye ubushobozi bwo kwanduza neza no gukomeza kubaho mu bantu, na zo ziba zidafite ubukana cyangwa ubwandu.
MERS-CoV yabonetse bwa mbere mu 2012 mu bihaha by'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 wafashe indwara y'umwijima ukabije ndetse n'impyiko zikaramba muri Arabiya Sawudite.
Mu gihe abenshi mu barwayi bemejwe na laboratwari bakomoka mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, hari abanduye baturuka mu bindi bihugu bazanye n'ubwandu bwa kabiri buturutse ku bantu bahuye na bo cyane cyane mu bihugu bitandukanye by'i Burayi no muri Tuniziya.
Mu 2015 hari ikindi cyorezo cya kabiri cyagaragaye muri Koreya y'Epfo, aho abantu 186 bagaragaye ko banduye.
Ibimenyetso bya MERS bisa n'ibya SARS, birangwa n'ubwiyongere bw'impyiko z'umura.
Bitandukanye na SARS, abarwayi benshi barwaye MERS na bo bagaragaje uburwayi bwo mu mubyimba, ubu buryo bukaba ari bwo bwonyine bwa MERS mu ndwara ziterwa na HCoV.
Abarwayi barenga 30% bagaragaza ibimenyetso byo mu nda, urugero nk'iseru no kwihekura.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, abantu barenga 2500 bagaragaye ko banduye, abarwayi bakaba barapfa ku kigero kiri hejuru cya 34.4%, bituma MERS-CoV iba imwe muri za virusi zica abantu cyane kurusha izindi.
Hagati mu kwezi kwa 12 kugeza mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2019, amatsinda y'abarwayi barwaye umusonga bamenyekanye ko bafite isano n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bavumbuwe i Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero bwo hasi iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 ari ikibazo cy'ihungabana ry'ubuzima rusange gihangayikishije Isi yose, ndetse ryanacyise COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, abantu 90,053 ku isi hose bamaze kwandura, aho umubare w'abapfa ku bw'iyi ndwara ari 3.4%.
By'umwihariko, umubare w'abapfa muri Hubei, mu Bushinwa ni 4.2%, mu gihe hanze yawo ari 1.2%.
SARS-CoV-2 iteza ubwandu bukomeye bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, igaragara nk'umuriro, inkorora no guhumeka nabi.
Nanone hari abarwayi bamwe na bamwe barwaye ibibyimba.
Indwara y'ibihaha ni kimwe mu bimenyetso bikomeye cyane kandi ishobora guhita igera ku ndwara y'ubuhumekero bw'ingutu.
Nubwo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zisa cyane bitewe n'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima bifite ibice 82%, zigira amashami atandukanye mu giti cy'ubwoko.
SARS-CoV-2 bigaragara ko idateza indwara cyane ariko ishobora gukwirakwira cyane ugereranyije na SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Abantu bafite ibimenyetso byanduye SARS-CoV-2 bagiye babonwa kandi bashobora kuba ari bo batuma ikwirakwira ku isi mu buryo bwihuse.
Kugereranya no gutandukanya SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi HCoV esheshatu byerekana ko hari ibyo zihuriyeho n'ibyo zisa n'ibitahuriyeho.
Icya mbere, igihe cyo kwandura no igihe indwara ya HCoV imara, birasa.
Muri urwo rwego, SARS-CoV-2 ikurikiza icyerekezo rusange cya za HCoV esheshatu.
Icya kabiri, uburemere bw'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 buri hagati ya SARS-CoV na HCoVs enye zanduye mu baturage (ni ukuvuga HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63).
Ku ruhande rumwe, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugaragaza ibintu bikunze kugaragara mu gihe cy'ubwandu bw'indwara ya HCoVs yandurwa mu baturage, harimo no kugaragaza ibimenyetso bidasanzwe, byoroheje cyangwa bitagaragara.
Ku rundi ruhande, igice gito cy'abantu barwaye COVID-19 ikomeye na bo bashobora kugaragara nk'uko bimeze ku ndwara ya SARS-CoV, nubwo igipimo kiri hasi cyane.
Icya gatatu, ikwirakwizwa rya SARS-CoV-2 rigaragaza n'imiterere ishishikaje iranga virusi ya HCoVs yandurira mu baturage na SARS-CoV.
Ku ruhande rumwe, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugera ku rugero rwo hejuru nko ku bwandu bwa HCoVs bwanduye abantu.
Ku rundi ruhande, haracyari gukorwa ubushakashatsi ngo harebwe niba ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwagabanuka nyuma yo kwandura mu bantu nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Amaherezo, kimwe n'izindi HCoVs, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugaragara mu ngero z'imyanda.
Niba ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 buturuka mu kinywa bugakora uruhare rukomeye nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS-CoV nibura mu mimerere runaka, bigomba gusobanurwa n'ubushakashatsi bw'igihe kizaza.
Ni ngombwa cyane kureba niba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugaragaza ibihe nk'uko bigenda ku Butagatifu bw'Imitsi y'Abantu.
