Icya gatatu, CoVs zihinduka ku buryo budahindagurika kandi kenshi mu gihe cyo kongera gusubiramo RNA binyuze mu buryo bwihariye bwo guhitamo kopi.
Mu murandasi ikora nk'urwungano, guhinduranya insoro bikunze kubaho mu gihe cyo kwandura RNA ya CoV.
RNA zingana cyane kandi zingana z'igihe kirekire zishobora kongera guhuza kugira ngo ziteze CoV nshya.
Ibimenyetso bya phylogenetic byo kongera kwihuza mu buryo bw'ibanze byabonetse muri HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-OC43, ndetse no muri CoVs zo mu nyamaswa nka bat SL-CoV na batCoV-HKU9.
Imishyikirano ya virusi n'umurwayi mu bijyanye no kwanduzanya
Usibye ibintu bitatu bya virusi byavuzwe haruguru, ubufatanye bwa virusi n'umurwayi w'umurwayi ni indi mpamvu y'ingenzi igira ingaruka ku kwanduzanya hagati y'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima.
Muri iyi raporo, gusubiramo SARS-CoV bifatwa nk'urugero rusanzwe, byerekanye kandi ibimenyetso byerekana ko habaho gutoranya kw'ibinyabuzima byanduza mu gihe cy'ubwandu hagati y'ubwoko bumwe.
Hashingiwe ku isesengura ry'igereranya hagati ya SARS-CoVs z'abantu n'iz'ibyatsi, SARS-CoV itekereza ko ihinduka mu buryo bwihuse mu mitungo itandukanye, cyane cyane mu mihinduranyirize yo mu bwoko bwa proteyine ya S.
Ubusanzwe, RBD iri muri poroteyine S ya CoV ifatanya n'imikorere y'ingirabuzimafatizo kandi igatoranywa cyane n'igisubizo cy'umurwayi.
Muri SARS-CoV, RBD iri muri 318 kugeza 510 muri amino acides ku gice cya S1, gihuza ACE2 y'umuntu kimwe n'ibinyabutabire byayo kugira ngo virusi yinjire.
RBD ya SARS-CoV ifite ubushobozi bwo kumenya ACE2 receptors z'inyamaswa zitandukanye, harimo ingunzu, ingurube, imbeba n'imbwa y'injangwe, bituma virusi ishobora kwandura hagati y'ubwoko butandukanye bw'inyamaswa.
Mu by'ukuri, ibisigisigi 6 by'iminyungugu ya amino acide byonyine byabonetse ko bitandukanye n'iby'abantu n'utundi dukoko tw'ibinyabuzima tw'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa RBD, kandi 4 muri byo biri mu cyuma gihuza iminyungugu n'imikorere y'iminyungugu ya ACE2.
SARS-CoV yo mu bwoko bw'inkoko ifite ihinduka ry'imiterere ya K479N na S487T muri RBD yayo, ibyo bikaba bishobora kongera isano y'imikorere y'indangamuntu ya poroteyine ya spike n'umuntu ACE2 receptor.
Mu yandi magambo, ibi bisobanuro by'amarozi abiri ya amino bishobora kuba ingenzi mu kwanduza virusi abantu.
Birakwiye ko tuzirikana ko SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye receptor z'ingirabuzimafatizo zimwe na SARS-CoV.
Itandukaniro rya 30% hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV mu gice cya S1 cya poroteyine ya S ryumvikanisha ko isano y'imiterere ya poroteyine ya S yayo na ACE2 y'umuntu ishobora kuba yarahindutse.
Koko rero, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe hifashishijwe uburyo bwa cryo-EM bugaragaza ko ubu bucuti bukomeye hagati y'iyi nzira yo guhuza n'abantu buruta inshuro 10 cyangwa 20 ubwo hagati ya ACE2 y'umuntu na poroteyine S ya SARS-CoV.
Byaba kandi ari ingirakamaro kumenya niba hari ibindi bikoresho by'ingenzi bishobora gukenerwa mu kwanduza SARS-CoV-2.
Igitangaje ni uko HCoV-NL63 na yo yifatanya na ACE2 ariko ifite igice cya S gitandukanye.
Hari izindi receptors nyinshi za HCoV, nka aminopeptidase N kuri HCoV-229E, na 9-O-acetylated sialic acid kuri HCoV-OC43.
Bashobora kandi kuba baragize uruhare mu gutuma izo CoVs zihuza n'abantu nyuma yo kwanduzanya hagati y'ubwoko butandukanye buturutse ku nyamaswa zibamo.
Uretse ibyuma byakira mu ngirabuzimafatizo, ingaruka z'ubwandu bwa HCoVs hagati y'ubwoko runaka na zo zigengwa n'ibindi bintu byo kuba umuntu yishingikiriza ku wundi kandi bikamugena.
Itandukaniro ry'ibi binyabuzima hagati y'abantu n'ibinyabuzima bisanzwe by'ibinyabuzima bya HCoVs nk'ibicurane, ingamiya n'ibikeri bishobora kuba inzitizi mu kwanduzanya hagati y'ubwoko.
HCoVs zigomba kwigarurira ibintu by'abashyingiranywe kandi zikagena ibintu bibuza abashyingiranywe kwanduzanya neza hagati y'ubwoko.
Muri urwo rwego, ibigenga imiterere ya mikorobi muri iki gice cy'ingenzi cy'ubufatanye bw'agakoko gatera virusi n'umurwayi biracyari ngombwa ko bigaragazwa kandi bigashyirwa mu bikorwa.
Gusuzuma mu buryo butagira aho buhuriye n'ubwoko bwa virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo butagira aho bushingiye kuri jenome no mu buryo bufite aho buhuriye n'ubwoko bwa virusi, hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga rihambaye cyane rya CRISPR, bishobora gutanga umusaruro.
Ivuka rya virusi nshya ya HCoV: gusubira ku murongo wa mbere
Ubwinshi bwa CoVs z'inguge butanga amahirwe menshi yo kuvuka kwa HCoVs nshya.
Muri ubwo buryo, CoVs z'igicuri zikora nk'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima bya HCoVs.
Byongeye kandi, ihinduka ry'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima n'imiterere y'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima na byo bituma HCoV ikomeza gutera imbere kandi bigira uruhare rw'ingenzi muri iyi nzira.
Urugero, kubona cyangwa gutakaza za gene nshya zandika poroteyine bishobora guhindura cyane imiterere y'agakoko gatera virusi.
Muri poroteyine z'inyongera za SARS-CoV, ORF8 yatekerejweho kuba ingenzi mu kumenyera abantu, kuko virusi z'ingwe zifitanye isano na SARS-CoV zaciwe ariko basanga zandika poroteyine zitandukanye za ORF8.
Hari uburyo bwo gusenya 29 nucleotide bw'indwara ya SARS-CoV bwabonetse mu bwoko bw'indwara bwatowe mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo cy'abantu.
Iri kuraga ritandukanya ORF8 ikagira ORF8a na ORF8b kandi bivugwa ko ari impinduka ihinduka ituma habaho guhinduranya ba nyir'ubwite.
Uretse ibyo, SARS-CoV ifite amateka y'ishobora kongera kwihuza n'imiryango ya alpha- na gamma-CoVs, aho umubare munini w'uturere duto twongeye kwihuza twabonetse muri RNA-dependent RNA polymerase.
Ahantu h'ubushushanyo bundi kandi hagaragaye mu nsp9, mu bice byinshi bya nsp10, no mu bice bya nsp14.
Ni na ko byagaragaye ko icyorezo cya MERS-CoV cyagize ingaruka zo kongera guhuza ibisekuru bitandukanye, byabereye mu ngamiya zo muri Arabiya Sawudite.
Uretse SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, ibindi bintu byongera kubaho byarabonetse no mu zindi HCoVs, aho HCoVs ihurira n'izindi CoVs z'inyamaswa mu maraso yazo atari ay'inyamaswa.
Birakwiye kandi ko umuntu akomeza kuzirikana ko gutoranya kw'abantu bishobora gutuma habaho impinduka zitari zitezwe muri jenome za virusi, bishoboka ko biterwa no koroshya virusi mu guhitamo ingufu, nko mu mikorere y'umubiri w'uwanduye.
Urugero rw'izo ngaruka ni ugutakaza ORF4 yuzuye mu bwoko bwa HCoV-229E bw'icyitegererezo, biturutse ku kuzimanganya kwa nucleotide ebyiri.
Mu gihe ORF4 itariho yagaragaye mu mikorobe n'ubwoko bw'ingamiya bifitanye isano na HCoV-229E, alpaka alpha-CoV igaragaza ko hari nucleotide imwe yashyizwe mu mubiri, bigatuma habaho guhinduranya ishusho.
Icya nyuma ariko si cyo cya nyuma, ni uko ihinduka ry'ubwoko bushya bwa HCoVs na ryo rituruka ku gitutu cyo gutoranya mu mashyamba yabo.
Ibimenyetso by'indwara cyangwa ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa byabonetse igihe inguge zafashwe na CoVs, byerekana ubwumvikane hagati ya CoVs n'inguge.
Byagaragaye ko imikara yihanganira CoVs mu buryo bw'umubiri n'imikorere.
Urugero, amakosa mu kubyutsa ibisubizo by'indwara z'ubwonko mu ngona bigabanya neza indwara ziterwa na CoVs.
Uretse ibyo, imikorere y'uturemangingo twica mu buryo bw'umwimerere mu ducurama iracika bitewe n'uko receptor NKG2/CD94 y'uturemangingo twica mu buryo bw'umwimerere itera ubudahangarwa n'urwego rwo kugaragara ku rugero ruto rw'imikorere y'udutsiko tw'ubwoko bwa I rw'uturemangingo tw'ingenzi tw'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima.
Byongeye kandi, igipimo cyo hejuru cy'ubwoko bwa ogisijeni bw'ubwoko bwa reactive (ROS) buturuka ku bikorwa byo mu mubiri by'ibicurane bishobora guhagarika ikwirakwizwa rya CoV kandi bikagira ingaruka ku gusubiramo kwa exoribonuclease, bityo bigatuma habaho ihitamo ry'uko habaho ubwoko bwa virusi bwanduza indwara cyane iyo bwinjijwe mu wundi murwayi.
Ubwoko bwa CoV bw'ubwandu bwinshi bushobora kandi kuvuka binyuze mu kongera guhuza, bigatuma haboneka poroteyine nshya cyangwa ibiranga poroteyine kugira ngo umurwayi yihindure.
Bityo rero, si ibintu byapfuye kubaho gutya gusa, ko za HCoV eshatu nshya zagiye zigaragara mu myaka makumyabiri ishize.
CoVs ntizitera indwara cyangwa ngo zitere ibimenyetso byoroheje mu nyamaswa ziba zirimo nk'imbeba n'ingamiya.
Zifata igihe kirekire cyane, ariko ntizitera ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
Aha niho hari ibanga ry'impamvu z'uko abanduye batagira ibimenyetso bagaragara n'icyatuma abantu barwara cyane.
Ibimenyetso bikomeye by'iyi ndwara biterwa ahanini n'uko umubiri w'umuntu uba ufite ubudahangarwa bwo kwirinda indwara ndetse n'ibihe by'umunaniro w'umubiri, aho uko ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri buba bukomeye, ari nako uburwayi bw'ibihaha buba bukomeye.
Ku rundi ruhande, mu bantu batanduye, ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri bw'umuntu bwagiye buvanwaho kugira ngo CoV itangire kwongera kwiyongera.
Iyi nzira yo guhagarika imikoreshereze y'ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri ishobora kugira akamaro mu kuvura SARS-CoV-2.
Igisubizo cya interferon gikomeye cyane cyane mu mpyisi.
Bityo rero, gutanga interferon yo mu bwoko bwa I nibura mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 ku bantu, bigomba kuba ari ingirakamaro.
Byongeye kandi, NLRP3 inflammasome activation mu ibinyamushongo ntabwo ikora neza.
Muri ubwo buryo, kubuza NLRP3 guturika hakoreshejwe MCC950 bishobora kuba ingirakamaro mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ivuka rya SARS-CoV-2 rikurikiza icyerekezo rusange cy'uko SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV byavutse.
Mu gihe beta-CoV y'ingwe ifite 95% by'imiterere y'ubwoko bumwe bwa nucleotide na SARS-CoV yabonetse, hari n'izindi bat-CoV zifite 96% by'imiterere y'ubwoko bumwe bwa nucleotide na SARS-CoV-2.
Mu gihe byagiye bigaragara ko inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bw'ibishwi n'izindi zo ku masoko zirimo virusi zifite aho zihuriye na SARS-CoV, nta nyamaswa z'imbere ziri mu nzira zo kwanduza SARS-CoV-2 zigeze zigaragara.
Hamaze kuboneka beta-CoVs za pangolins zisa cyane na SARS-CoV-2, byerekana ko pangolins zishobora kuba imwe mu nyirizina z'inyongera cyangwa beta-CoVs za pangolin zishobora gutanga ibice by'utugingo ku bwoko bwa nyuma bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo ibibazo bikiriho, nta gihamya igaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 yakozwe n'umuntu yaba yagambiriwe cyangwa se mu buryo bw'impanuka.
CoVs zongeye kugaragara cyane kubera icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 giherutse kwaduka.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikorobe za CoVs mu ducurama n'izindi nyamaswa bwahinduye cyane uko tubona akamaro k'inkomoko ya zoonotic n'uko inyamaswa z'inyamaswa zanduza za HCoVs abantu.
Ibimenyetso biboneka hose byagaragaje ko SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 bikomoka ku ducurama kandi bikandurira ku bantu binyuze mu bikoresho byo mu nda.
Kubera ko ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV buturuka ku guhura kw'abantu n'ibinyamushongo ku masoko, gufunga amasoko y'ibicuruzwa n'ibinyamushongo byaho byari gutuma icyorezo cya SARS kirangira.
Hakurikijwe iyo mpamvu, ingona zagombye gukurwa ku masoko kugira ngo hirindwe ko zishobora kwandura, bitewe n'uko havumbuwe amoko menshi y'ubwoko bwa beta-CoV bw'ingona bufitanye isano rya hafi na SARS-CoV-2.
Icyakora, niba SARS-CoV-2 yandurira ku bantu binyuze mu ngona n'izindi nyamaswa zo mu bwoko bw'ibinyamushongo n'uburyo yandurirwa, bizasobanuka mu bushakashatsi buzakorwa mu gihe kizaza.
Ku rundi ruhande, MERS-CoV imaze igihe kirekire iboneka mu ngamiya z'ingamiya.
Izo ngamiya ni ibikoresho by'ingenzi mu gutwara abantu, kandi ni zo abaturage bo muri ako gace bakuraho inyama, amata, uruhu n'ubwoya.
Ziboneka cyane mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati no muri Afurika.
Ku bw'ibyo, ntibishoboka gutamba ingamiya zose mu rwego rwo kurwanya MERS, nk'uko byagenze mu masoko y'inyamaswa zo mu ishyamba yo mu Bushinwa mu rwego rwo kwirinda ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2.
Kugira ngo indwara ya MERS ihagarikwe, hagomba gufatwa ingamba zirambuye zo gukora inkingo zikora neza zo kurwanya MERS-CoV ku ngamiya, zifatanyije n'izindi ngamba zo kurwanya ubwandu.
Kubera ko tudashobora kurandura iyi virusi, hashobora kuvuka izindi z'ubwoko bushya bw'indwara zitera indwara.
Ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoV zoonotic zirimo zikwirakwira mu ishyamba.
By'umwihariko, CoVs z'ibicurane bifite ubushobozi bwo kwanduza inyamaswa zinyuranye cyane.
Hari amahirwe menshi ko izi zoonotic CoVs zishobora guhinduka no kongera kwihuza, bigatuma habaho CoVs nshya zishobora kwandura cyane kandi/cyangwa zikaba zishobora kwica abantu mu gihe kizaza.
Umuco wo kurya inyamaswa zo mu gasozi mu duce tumwe na tumwe two mu Bushinwa wagombye kureka kugira ngo abantu bajye bareka kugirana imishyikirano n'inyamaswa bitari ngombwa.
Mu gihe SARS, MERS na COVID-19 ari byo bigerageza abantu, hakwiye gushyirwaho gahunda yo kwitegura neza no guhangana na byo.
Mu by'ukuri, virusi nyinshi zabayeho ku isi mu gihe kirekire cyane.
Baguma mu mazi yabo bwite kugeza igihe hazabaho amahirwe yo gukwirakwiza.
Nubwo ibinyamibwa bifite ibintu byinshi bituma virusi zisakara, amahirwe y'abantu yo kugirana imishyikirano n'ibinyamibwa n'ibindi biremwa byo mu ishyamba ashobora kugabanuka niba abantu bigishijwe kwitandukanya na byo.
Ni ngombwa gukomeza gukurikirana ibinyabuzima by'ibimera kugira ngo turusheho gusobanukirwa neza ibidukikije bya CoVs n'ibinyabuzima by'ibanze byazo, bikaba bizagaragara ko ari ingirakamaro mu gukumira kwanduzanya kw'ibinyabuzima n'abantu no kwirinda ko habaho ibyorezo by'ibyorezo mu gihe kizaza.
Mu gusoza, uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda virusi zitera zoonote ni uko abantu bakomeza kwirinda ahantu haboneka virusi zitera zoonote.
Hari ibice byinshi by'igihimbaza cy'inkomoko ya SARS-CoV-2 mu bantu bikiri kubura.
Mbere na mbere, niba ibishishi byanduza virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ku nkoko, bizashishikaza kureba mu bihe bihe ibishishi n'inkoko byashoboraga gusangira ahantu hamwe mu buryo bw'ibidukikije.
Icya kabiri, niba dusaba ko injangwe z'ingore zifite uruhare rugaragara mu kwanduza abantu, uburyo abantu bagirana imishyikirano n'izo nyamaswa bugomba kumenyekana.
Icya gatatu, niba inyamaswa y'ikirere ya gatatu ikora nk'umurwayi w'ukuri, uburyo igirana imishyikirano n'amoko atandukanye arimo abantu, ibishyimbo na pangolin bigomba gusobanurwa.
Amaherezo, kubera ko inyamaswa nyinshi ziruka, harimo n'inyamaswa zo mu rugo, zishobora kuba zishobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2, hakwiye gukorwa igenzura n'igeragezaho uburyo bwo kwanduza.
Niba ari urukwavu, pangolin cyangwa ikindi gikoko gihumeka, byitezwe ko SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa virusi zayo z'ababyeyi zisa nkaho zisa zizamenyekana mu mikoro yayo mu gihe kizaza.
Ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi bikomeje muri aka gace bizatanga ibisobanuro ku buryo SARS-CoV-2 yagiye ihinduka mu nyamaswa, bikaba bifite ingaruka zikomeye mu gukumira no kurwanya COVID-19 mu bantu.
Ni ngombwa kuvugurura ibipimo by'isuzuma ry'indwara ya COVID-19 ikekwaho kuba ifite ibimenyetso n' igaragaza ko ifite ibimenyetso
Ku wa 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryasohoye amabwiriza yihuse yo gutanga inama ku gusuzuma no kuvura ubwandu bushya bwa coronavirus (2019-nCoV) bwo mu 2019, kandi aya mabwiriza yadufashije kubona ubunararibonye bwacu no kugira icyo avuga ku kurwanya iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Ariko, indwara ya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu n'ubumenyi bwacu bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro dushingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu kwivuza; bityo, ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura nazo zikomeza kuvugururwa.
Muri iyi baruwa, twasubije igitekerezo kimwe ku mabwiriza yacu kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya by'ibipimo bya "Uwibasirwa n'icyorezo" na "Uwanduye byemejwe" hakurikijwe amabwiriza mashya yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 (verisiyo ya karindwi) yatanzwe na Komite y'igihugu y'ubuzima muri Repubulika y'abaturage y'Ubushinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, icyorezo cya koronavirusi nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) cyateye icyorezo, ubu cyiswe ku mugaragaro icyorezo cya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19) kandi virusi yiswe coronavirus 2 y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yagaragaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryashyizeho amabwiriza yihuse kandi yashyizwe ku rubuga rwa interineti mu kinyamakuru cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubuvuzi mu gisirikare ku itariki ya 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Byatumye abantu benshi babitekerezaho cyane kuva cyasohoka.
Icyakora, twibuke ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu buzamuka buhoro buhoro bushingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi; bityo, ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura na zo zikomeza kuvugururwa.
Urugero, amabwiriza yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 yasohowe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'u Bushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), hagati y'itariki ya 16 Mutarama 2020 n'iya 3 Werurwe 2020, yasohoye inyandiko zirindwi zose hamwe, aho hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe byahindutse cyane.
Ubu rero ubuyobozi bwacu bwahawe igitekerezo na Zhou et al., batanze igitekerezo cyoroshye cyo gutanga amanota hashingiwe ku bumenyi bwabo mu buvuzi.
Igikorwa cyabo cyongereye ibimenyetso bishya ku mabwiriza yacu kandi kandi gitanga ubufasha bw'agaciro kuri iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Dushyigikira umurimo wabo w'ingenzi kandi tukabagaragariza ko tubashimira.
Icyakora, akazi kabo kandi kagomba kuvugururwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza ya vuba y'uburyo bwo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (Verisiyo ya karindwi y'igerageza) n'ubushakashatsi buheruka.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu cyiciro cya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo umuntu yemeze ko hari umuntu urwaye, hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe byo mu mateka y'ibyorezo bigomba guhuzwa n'ibintu bibiri byo mu bimenyetso byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi kugira ngo hakorwe isesengura ryimbitse, cyangwa hakenerwa ibintu bitatu byo mu bimenyetso by'ubuvuzi niba nta mateka y'ibyorezo asobanutse:
Amateka y'ibyorezo: (1) amateka y'urugendo cyangwa kuba mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu turere tuyikikije, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho abantu banduye COVID-19 bari barigeze kuboneka mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (2) amateka y'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 (binyuze mu gupimwa basanganywe aside ya nikleyiki); (3) amateka y'abanduye COVID-19 mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu yindi miryango aho abantu barwaye umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (4) amateka y'abanduye COVID-19 mu itsinda ry'abantu bagaragajweho ubwandu (abantu 2 barwaye umuriro cyangwa bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bagaragaye mu gihe cy'ibyumweru 2 mu duce duto, nko mu rugo, mu biro, mu ishuri n'ibindi).
Ibimenyetso byo kwa muganga: (1) umuriro na/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) ibimenyetso byo mu mashusho byerekana ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) umubare w'utuntu duto twera tw'amaraso ugaragaza ko ari twose, twagabanutse cyangwa twagabanutse mu gihe cy'indwara y'umwanda.
Gusuzuma umuntu wemejwe ko arwaye bigomba gushingira ku muntu ukekwaho kuba arwaye ufite ibimenyetso by'indwara cyangwa seroloji nk'uko bikurikira: (1) kwipimisha PCR mu gihe nyacyo bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubwandu; (2) gusobanura urutonde rwa genome yose ya virusi bigaragaza ko hari ubwandu bumwe bwa virusi nshya za koronavirusi; (3) kwipimisha ubwandu mu misemburo bigaragaza ko hari ubwandu bwa IgM bwihariye n'ubwandu bwa IgG bwihariye bwa SARS-CoV-2; cyangwa guhindura ubwandu bwa IgG bwihariye bwa SARS-CoV-2 bukava ku butandu bugaragaza ko hari ubwandu, cyangwa se igipimo cy'ubwandu cyikuba inshuro ≥4 mu cyiciro cyo gukira kikarenga icy'ubwandu bukomeye.
Twabona ko ikizamini cya PCR cyo mu gihe nyacyo cyo gupima aside nucleic mu nzira z'ubuhumekero cyangwa mu bipimo by'amaraso cyongerewe ku gihangano cya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Ibimenyetso by'indwara by'igishushanyo cy'amaraso byongerewe ku nshuro ya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) n'iya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma ibimenyetso bya seroloji byongerwa ku nshuro ya karindwi.
Izi mpinduka zishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakomeje gukorwa mu gushakisha igikoresho cyiza cyo gutahura aside ya nucleic kugira ngo hamenyekane indwara vuba, kimwe n'ibimenyetso byo mu nzira y'ubuhumekero harimo no gufata ibipimo by'amaraso, byongereye ubushobozi bwo kubona ibipimo bitandukanye, kandi byashyigikiye ko haboneka ibimenyetso by'umubiri runaka mu bipimo byemejwe.
Byongeye kandi, hari ibimenyetso byinshi bidusaba kwitondera abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bidasanzwe n'abadafite ibimenyetso.
Bityo rero, ishusho y'uburyo Zhou et al. yagombaga kuvugururwa, kuko bashyize mu cyiciro umuntu udafite ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi nk'umuntu ufite ibyago bike.
Iyi gahunda yo gutanga amanota igomba no kugenzurwa mu bikorwa no mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi.
Mu gusoza, twizeye ko hari ibindi bihamya bifatika bizatangwa kandi dusaba abasomyi gutanga ibitekerezo byabo.
Mu gusuzuma abakekwaho kuba baranduye na abanduye byemejwe, turasaba gukurikirana no gukurikiza amabwiriza mashya y'ibihugu byabo.
Itsinda ryacu rizongera rivugurure amabwiriza yacu mu gihe gikwiye kugira ngo ritange ubufasha.
Bangladesh yatangaje abantu batanu bashya bapfuye kubera COVID-19, umubare munini w'abantu bapfa buri munsi
Ejo hashize, Bangladesh yemeje ko hapfuye abantu batanu bishwe na COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Uyu ni wo mubare munini w'abantu bapfuye ku munsi umwe kubera iyi virusi.
Kugeza ku munsi w'ejo, Ikigo cya Bangladesh cy'Icyorezo, Gukumira Indwara no Gushakisha (IEDCR) cyatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye banditswe harimo 114 bari kuvurwa n'abandi 33 bakize, bari mu rugo.
Abantu 17 ni bo bamaze gupfa.
Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru cyasohotse ku rubuga rwa interineti, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, yavuze ko mu bapfuye harimo abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Dukurikije uko Dr Meerjady abivuga, babiri bari bafite imyaka iri hejuru ya 60, babiri bari hagati ya 51 na 60, n'undi umwe wari ufite hagati ya 41 na 50.
Yavuze kandi ko babiri mu bishwe bari abo mu mujyi wa Dhaka.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe.
Umukozi wo mu bitaro yabwiye Anadolu Agency, ikinyamakuru cyo muri ako karere, ko umwe mu bapfuye yari Jalal Saifur Rahman, umuyobozi wa Komisiyo yo kurwanya ruswa yo muri Bengali, yitabwaga ku bitaro bya Kuwait Maitree.
Ku wa Gatandatu, mu itangazo rya videwo ku rubuga, Minisitiri w'Ibiduka n'Imihanda muri Bangladesh, Obaidul Quader, yavuze ko ingendo rusange zizakomeza gufunga kugeza ku wa Gatandatu w'icyumweru gitaha, igihe kirekire kurusha uko byari biteganijwe.
Iyi gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo z'abantu bose yari yatangiye ku ya 26 Werurwe, biteganyijwe ko izarangira ku ya 4 Mata.
Gutwara ibintu by'ibanze - nk'imiti, lisansi n'ibiribwa - byari byemewe.
Abantu babiri bagaragaye muri Bangladesh banduye COVID-19 ku itariki ya 8 Werurwe, ni abantu babiri bari bavuye mu Butaliyani, barimo n'umugore w'umwe muri bo.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, abo uko ari batatu bari bamaze gukira.
SARS-CoV-2 imaze kwandura abantu barenga miliyoni ku isi
Ku wa Kane, imibare y'abarwayi bose banduye virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ku isi yose, yarenze miliyoni imwe, nk'uko byagaragajwe n'amakuru ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins.
Abantu bagera ku bihumbi 52 bishwe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19, indwara iterwa na koronavirusi.
Iki gikorwa gikomeye cyabaye umunsi Malawi yemeje abantu ba mbere banduye coronavirus na Zambia ifite umuntu wa mbere yishwe na coronavirus.
Koreya ya Ruguru yatangaje ko, kuva ku wa Kane, ari kimwe mu bihugu bike byasigaye bidafite ubwandu bwa coronavirus.
Kugeza ku munsi w'ejo, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko abantu 1,051,635 ari bo bamaze kwandura, harimo 79,332 mu masaha makumyabiri n'ane yabanjirije saa kumi za mu gitondo ku isaha yo mu Burayi bwo hagati (0800 UTC) ku itariki ya 4 Mata.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, abantu barenga 244 000 banduye icyorezo cya coronavirus, bakaba barapfuye nibura 5900.
Ikigo cy'Itangazamakuru cya CBS cyatangaje, gishingiye ku makuru ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins, ko ku wa Gatatu, muri Amerika hapfuye abantu barenga 1000 bazize ubwandu bwa coronavirus.
Ku isi hose, ibihugu byatangaje ingamba zikarishye zo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara.
Ku wa kane, Sergei Sobyanin, umuyobozi w'umujyi wa Moscou, yongereye igihe cyo gufunga umujyi kugera ku ya 1 Gicurasi.
Ku rwego rw'igihugu, Perezida Vladimir Putin yatangaje ko Abarusiya bazakomeza guhembwa batagiye ku kazi kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Portugal yatoye kongera iminsi 15 ku gihe cy'ibihe bidasanzwe; amatora yaremejwe n'amajwi 215 ashyigikira, cumi batabyemeye, n'amajwi 1 yanga.
Arabiya Sawudite yongereye amasaha yo kuva mu rugo mu mijyi mitagatifu ya Mecca na Medina kugira ngo azamara umunsi wose; mbere, amasaha yo kuva mu rugo yari kuva saa tatu z'ijoro kugeza saa sita za mu gitondo.
Thailand yateganyaga gushyiraho amasaha yo gutaha hagati ya saa kumi n'ebyiri z'ijoro na saa yine za mu gitondo.
Guverineri wa Ohio, Mike DeWine, yatangaje ko leta yongereye igihe cyo kuguma mu rugo kugeza ku ya 1 Gicurasi.
Amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya agabanya umubare w'impapuro z'isuku ku kintu kimwe
Ku cyumweru no ku wa gatandatu nimugoroba, amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya ya Woolworths na Coles yagabanyije imipaka yo kugura impapuro z'isuku ku bipfunyika bibiri na paketi imwe ku gicuruzwa mu maduka yose ku rwego rw'igihugu, buri wese.
ALDI kandi yashyizeho igipimo cy'impapuro imwe ku wa mbere.
Ibi bihano byashyizwe ku mbuga nkoranyambaga nk'ubutumwa ku mbuga nkoranyambaga, no ku mbuga nkoranyambaga za Facebook.
Abaguzi ngo bari bagishakisha ibicuruzwa bitewe no gutinya COVID-19 mu gihe abantu baba bagomba kwiherera.
Ku wa gatatu, Woolworths na yo yagabanyije igura impapuro z'isuku zo koherezwa mu ngo ku icupa rimwe kuri buri busabe.
Ibyo byakozwe nyuma y'uko Woolworths na Coles ku ya 4 n'iya 5 Werurwe batangije gahunda yo gutanga ibicuruzwa mu buryo bw'amapaji ane.
Coles, mu itangazo ryo ku wa 8 Werurwe, yatangaje ko n'ubwo itegeko ry'uko abantu batagomba kugura ibintu birimo ibice bine by'ibyokurya ryatangiye gukurikizwa, "amaduka menshi aracyaragurisha mu gihe cy'isaha imwe gusa nyuma yo kubishyikiriza abaguzi", maze avuga ko ibyo ari "ibintu bitigeze bibaho", mu gihe ALDI, mu butumwa yashyize kuri Facebook ku wa Kabiri, yavuze ko "bitari byitezwe".
Nk'uko umuvugizi wa Woolworths abivuga, mu cyumweru gishize, ibicuruzwa bya Woolworths byazamutse "mu buryo bwihuse".
Iduka rya Costco i Canberra na ryo ryashyizeho imipaka yo gutanga amakarito abiri gusa mu cyumweru gishize.
Kugira ngo barusheho koroshya ibura, Coles yasabye ibicuruzwa binini ku bicuruzwa by'abatanga ibicuruzwa no kongera inshuro byo gutanga, Woolworths yasabye ibicuruzwa byinshi, mu gihe ALDI yateguye ibicuruzwa byateganijwe ku wa gatatu bidasanzwe.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi bo muri Ositaraliya, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa, ariko amategeko y'akarere agena igihe imodoka zitwara ibicuruzwa zizajya zizazirangiriza, bituma ibyo bigorana.
Ategereje ko ibiciro by'umusaruro bizamuka, kubera ko abatanga ibintu bagerageza guhaza ibisabwa, kandi ko ibiribwa byihariye bigabanuka.
Ku wa Kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko nyuma yo gusohora ku isoko mbere y'igihe, amaduka amwe n'amwe adashobora gukora ibiribwa bidasanzwe ku wa Gatatu.
Mu nkuru ya News.com.au, Dr Gary Mortimer, inzobere mu gucuruza mu kigo cya Queensland University of Technology, yavuze ko amaduka yuzuza ibicuruzwa buri joro.
Yavuze ko impapuro z'isuku ari ikintu kinini, gituma umubare muto w'ibicuruzwa ugaragara, kandi iyo bagurishijwe, basiga ibibanza byinshi by'amabati by'ubusa, bikomeza ibyiyumvo byo kubura.
"Coles na Woolworths bafite imyumvire [yuko] niba hari ibintu byinshi ku meza, niba ibicuruzwa nk'ibitabo by'isuku n'ibikoresho by'isuku bishobora [kugurwa] kandi bikaba bihari mu bwinshi, birashoboka ko wagabanya ubwoba" Russell Zimmerman kuri ABC News.
Umunyamyuga utunganya impapuro z'isuku zongeye gukoreshwa, witwaga "Uwifuza ko ibintu bye byangirika" (Who Gives a Crap) yatangaje ko ku wa gatatu w'icyumweru gishize, ibicuruzwa byabo byari byahiye.
Kimberly-Clark, ikora imyenda y'isuku ya Kleenex, na Solaris Paper ikora Sorbent, byashimangiye ko bakora amasaha 24 kuri 24, 24 ku munsi kugira ngo bikomeze gutanga, nk'uko bitangazwa na News.com.au.
Ikinyamakuru Domain.com, ni urubuga rw'ubukungu bw'umutungo utimukanwa, cyatangaje ko bamwe mu bacuruzi b'imitungo batanga impapuro z'isuku ku buntu ku muntu wa mbere ubanza gutanga ibiciro mu cyamunara i Melbourne, mu gihe cyamunara zagabanutse kubera ko abaguzi bari bafite igihe cyo kuruhuka mu mpera z'icyumweru z'umunsi w'abakozi.
Igitabo cyo kuwa kane cya NT News, ikinyamakuru gisohoka buri munsi cyandikirwa i Darwin, cyagaragaje inyandiko y'amapaji umunani yagombaga gucibwa ikagirwa impapuro z'isuku.
Amaduka yabanje kwanga gushyiraho amategeko, nk'uko raporo yo kuri ABC Australia yo ku ya 3 Werurwe ibigaragaza, aho bavuga ko nta gahunda bafite yo gushyiraho amategeko ku byo bagura.
Russell Zimmerman yongeyeho ko hari ibindi bicuruzwa nabyo byifuzwa cyane, birimo udupfukamunwa, imiti yica udukoko, ibicuruzwa byumye, ibyo gukaraba intoki n'ifu.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, hanze ya Ositaraliya, ku cyumweru nimugoroba, supermarket y'Abongereza Ocado yabonetse igura impapuro z'isuku za Andres mu macupa abiri y'impu 12.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyugarije isi yose  indwara iterwa na koronavirusi SARS-CoV-2  ari icyorezo.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza gusa ku kuntu indwara yakwirakwijwe mu buryo bwagutse, ntabwo ryerekeza ku kuntu abantu bamwe na bamwe bafite ibyago bikomeye, OMS yagaragaje ko ari ngombwa gushishikariza za leta kugira icyo zikora:
Ati "Ibihugu byose biracyashobora guhindura icyerekezo cy'iki cyorezo.
Niba ibihugu byabona, bigakora ibizamini, bikagenzura, bigashyira mu kato, bikagenzura kandi bigashyiramo imbaraga abaturage babyo mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo", Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS.
"Turatangazwa cyane n'uko iyi ndwara ikwirakwira ku rugero ruteye ubwoba, kandi ikaba ikomeye, ndetse no kuba nta cyo abantu bakora".
Dukurikije uko Dogiteri Tom Frieden wahoze ari umuyobozi w'ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara abivuga, icyo cyorezo "nta kindi cyigeze kibaho".
Mu magambo yatangajwe na CNN mu kwezi kwa kabiri, yavuze ko "uretse ibicurane, nta yindi virusi yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yavuyeho ikagera ku isi ikomeje gukwirakwira".
Ghebreyesus yagaragaje igitekerezo nk'icyo, avuga ko "nta na rimwe twigeze tubona icyorezo cyatewe na koronavirusi".
Yakomeje agira ati "kandi ntitwigeze tubona icyorezo gishobora gutegekwa icyarimwe".
Iyi mpinduka nshya nk'icyorezo cy'icyorezo yakurikiye icyemezo cya OMS cyo muri Mutarama cyo gutangaza ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange gihangayikishije isi.
Umuyobozi w'ikigo cy'igihugu cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe indwara zandura, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yavuze ko ibyorezo by'iyi ndwara "bigiye kuzagenda birushaho kuba bibi".
Kugeza ku wa kane, Associated Press yatangaje ko ku isi hose habonetse nibura abantu 126,000 banduye COVID-19, bigatuma abantu barenga 4,600 bahasiga ubuzima.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus 201920 ni icyorezo gikomeje cy'indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), iterwa na coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye i Wuhan, mu Bushinwa, mu Kuboza 2019, cyemezwa ko ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange gihangayikishije amahanga ku ya 30 Mutarama 2020, cyemerwa nk'icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri 1.61 miliyoni banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu n'uturere 210, byahitanye abantu bagera ku 97,000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 bamaze gukira.
Imibare y'abarwayi bapfa igera kuri 4% mu Bushinwa, mu gihe ku isi yose iri hagati ya 13.04% muri Algeria na .08% muri Nouvelle Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara harimo umuriro, gukorora no guhumeka nabi.
Bimwe mu bibazo bishobora kubaho harimo pneumonia n'indwara y'ubuhumekero.
Igihe gitangira kuva ku kwanduzwa kugeza igihe ibimenyetso byatangiriye, akenshi ni iminsi igera kuri itanu, ariko gishobora kuva ku minsi ibiri kugera kuri cumi n' ine.
Nta rukingo cyangwa umuti wihariye uvura virusi bizwi.
Ubuvuzi bw'ibanze ni ubuvuzi bugaragaza ibimenyetso no gushyigikira. Ingamba z'ubwirinzi zasabwe zirimo gukaraba intoki, gupfuka umunwa igihe umuntu akoroye, gukomeza kugendera kure abandi bantu, no kugenzura no kwigunga ku bantu bakekwaho kuba baranduye.
Abategetsi ku isi hose babyitabiriye bashyiraho amategeko abuza abantu gukora ingendo, bashyira abantu mu kato, bashyiraho amasaha y'akazi, bashyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda impanuka ku kazi, kandi bagafunga amazu.
Icyorezo cyateye ihungabana rikomeye mu bukungu n'imibereho y'abantu ku isi, gusubikwa cyangwa guhagarika ibikorwa by'imikino, iby'amadini, politiki n'imigenzo ndangamuco, n'ibura ry'ibikoresho ryiyongera bitewe n'uko abantu bagura ibintu mu buryo butunguranye.
Amashuri na za kaminuza byafunze haba ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa urw'akarere mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku kigero cya 99.4 ku ijana by'abanyeshuri ku isi.
Amakuru atari yo ku virusi yakwirakwijwe kuri interineti, kandi habayeho ibikorwa byo kwanga abanyamahanga no kuvangura Abashinwa, abandi bantu bakomoka mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'Iburasirazuba bwa Aziya n'uko bagaragara, n'abandi baturutse mu turere turimo abantu benshi banduye virusi.
Kubera ko ingendo zagabanutse no gufunga inganda zikomeye, habayeho igabanuka ry'imyuka ihumanya ikirere n'ibyuka bya karubone.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) batangaje ko hari umubare munini w'abanduye indwara y'ibihaha ku mpamvu zitazwi ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019, kandi iperereza ryatangiye mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Abenshi mu barwaye bari bafite aho bahuriye n'isoko rya Huanan ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja, bityo iyi virusi ikaba ishobora kuba ifite inkomoko ku nyamaswa.
Virusi yateje iki cyorezo izwi nka SARS-CoV-2, virusi iherutse kuvumburwa ifitanye isano ya hafi na koronavirusi z'ibicurane, koronavirusi za pangolin na SARS-CoV. Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ufite ibimenyetso bya virusi yaje kuvumburwa ko yanduye ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi uwo muntu nta sano rigaragara yari afitanye n'ikigo cy'ubucuruzi cya nyuma.
Mu matsinda y'abantu ba mbere baburiweho ibyaha mu Ukuboza 2019, bibiri bya gatatu byabonetse ko bifitanye isano n'isoko.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, raporo itaremejwe yavuye mu kinyamakuru South China Morning Post yavuze ko umuntu wafashwe ku ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019, mu muntu w'imyaka 55 wo mu ntara ya Hubei, ashobora kuba ari we wa mbere. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko, nk'uko bivugwa ko abanduye bashya bagabanutse mu Bushinwa ariko bakiyongera mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, umubare w'abanduye bashya hanze y'Ubushinwa warenze ku mubare w'abanduye bashya mu Bushinwa ku ncuro ya mbere.
Hari aho usanga hari umubare munini w'abatabwaho indwara, cyane cyane mu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Gashyantare, abarwayi bari bake cyane mu rubyiruko, aho abanduye bari munsi y'imyaka 19 bagize 2.4% by'abanduye ku isi. Umujyanama mukuru mu bya siyansi w'Ubwongereza, Patrick Vallance, yagaragaje ko 60% by'abatuye u Bwongereza bari gukenera kwandura mbere y'uko ubwirinzi bw'itsinda bugerwaho.
Abanduye bagereranya umubare w'abantu bapimwe COVID-19, kandi ibizamini byabo byemejwe ko byanduye hakurikijwe amabwiriza ya leta.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu cyari cyasuzumye abaturage bacyo barenga 3%, kandi ibihugu byinshi byagize politiki yo kutagenzura abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa, nka Ubutaliyani, Ubuholandi, Esipanye n'Ubwusuwisi.
Ubushakashatsi bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 16 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama, abagera kuri 86% by'abanduye COVID-19 batari baramenyekana, kandi ko izo ndwara zitagaragajwe ari zo zanduzaga 79% by'abanduye.
Isesengura ry'ibarurishamibare ryasohotse ku ya 30 Werurwe ryagaragaje ko umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani warenze cyane umubare w'abanduye.
Ibipimo by'ibanze by'umubare w'ubushake bwo kongera kubyara (R0) kuri COVID-19 byari kuva kuri 1.4 kugera kuri 2.4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara, bwageze ku mwanzuro w'uko ishobora kuba ari 5.7.
Abantu benshi bafite COVID-19 barakira.
Ku bantu badafite ibimenyetso, igihe kuva ku gutangira kugaragaza ibimenyetso kugeza ku rupfu cyabaye hagati y' iminsi 6 na 41, aho ikikunze kuba iminsi 14.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97,000 bari bamaze kwicwa n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 5 Gashyantare, hafi 80% by'abapfuye bari hejuru y'imyaka 60, naho 75% bari bafite uburwayi bwa mbere harimo indwara z'umutima na diyabete. Imibare y'abapfuye mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko bitewe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 muri rusange yerekeza ku bapfuye basuzumwe bagasanga baranduye COVID hakurikijwe amabwiriza y'ubuvuzi.
Umubare w'abantu bapfuye mu by'ukuri bazize COVID-19 ushobora kuba ari munini cyane, kuko ushobora kuba utarimo abantu bapfa batakorewe ikizamini - urugero, mu rugo, mu bigo byita ku bageze mu za bukuru n'ibindi.
Ibipimo by'ibipimo by'igice by'Ubutaliyani byagaragaje ko umubare w'abantu bapfuye mu gihe cy'icyorezo warenze umubare w'abapfuye ba COVID mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko inshuro zigera kuri 4.5.
Umuvugizi w'ikigo cya Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yemeye ko "tuzi ko [umubare w'abapfuye wavuzwe] ari umubare utagomba kuboneka", amagambo yashimangirwa n'amakuru y'ibyabaye muri Amerika. Bene uko kutabona ibintu neza bikunze kubaho mu gihe cy'ibyorezo, nk'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cya H1N1 cyo mu 2009. Umuntu wa mbere witabye Imana byemejwe ni uwa Wuhan ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020.
Umuntu wa mbere wapfiriye hanze y'u Bushinwa yabaye ku ya 1 Gashyantare muri Filipine, naho uwa mbere wapfiriye hanze ya Aziya aba mu Bufaransa ku ya 14 Gashyantare.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, hanze y'u Bushinwa, abarenga cumi na babiri buri wese yapfuye, muri Irani, Koreya y'Epfo n'u Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu n'uturere birenga mirongo ine byari byatangaje ko hari abantu bapfuye, ku migabane yose uretse Antarctica.
Iyi mibare itandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi igenda ishingirwa ku bwinshi bw'ibizamini, ireme ry'urwego rw'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kuvura, igihe cyashize icyorezo gitangiye, n'imiterere y'abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima rusange. Umubare w'abapfuye ugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye ugaragaza umubare w'abapfuye ugabanyije n'umubare w'abanduye basuzwe mu gihe runaka.
Dukurikije imibare y'ikigo cya Johns Hopkins University, umubare w'abapfa ku isi ni 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020.
Umubare w'abapfa uratandukana bitewe n'uturere.
Mu Bushinwa, imibare y'umubare w'abapfuye n'abanduye yagabanutse kuva kuri 17.3% (ku bantu bagaragayeho ibimenyetso ku itariki ya 1-10 Mutarama 2020) igera kuri 0.7% (ku bagaragayeho ibimenyetso nyuma y'itariki ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Mu bindi bipimo harimo igipimo cy'umubare w'abapfa (CFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abantu bapimwe bahitanwa n'indwara, n'igipimo cy'umubare w'abapfa bahitanwa n'indwara (IFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye (bamaze gupimwa no kutavurwa) bahitanwa n'indwara.
Iyi mibare ntishingiye ku gihe kandi ikurikirana abantu runaka kuva bamenyekana kugeza igihe ikibazo gikemukiye.
Hari intiti nyinshi zagiye zigerageza kubara iyo mibare ku bantu runaka.
Ikigo cya Kaminuza ya Oxford cy'ubuvuzi bushingiye ku bimenyetso kigaragaza ko ikigero cy'abantu bapfa bahitanywe n'ubwandu muri rusange kiri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Igiteranyo cyo hejuru cy'icyo gipimo gihuye n'ibyavuye mu gupima kwa mbere kw'abantu ku bushake kwa COVID-19 mu Budage, no mu bushakashatsi bw'imibare bugaragaza ingaruka zo gupima ku bipimo bya CFR.
OMS ivuga ko icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Igihe cy'icyorezo n'igihe cyacyo cy'imperuka ntibiramenyekana neza kandi gishobora gutandukana bitewe n'aho kizaba giherereye.
Maciej Boni wo muri kaminuza ya Penn State yagize ati "Iyo indwara z'ibyorezo zitararindwa, akenshi zigera ku kigero cyo hejuru, hanyuma zigatangira kugabanuka igihe indwara yabuze abantu bashobora kuyirwanya.
Ariko biragoye ko umuntu yakwiha igihe nyacyo ibyo bizabera".
Umujyanama mukuru mu by'ubuvuzi wa leta y'u Bushinwa, Zhong Nanshan, yavuze ko "bishobora kurangira mu kwezi kwa gatandatu" mu gihe ibihugu byose byashyizwe hamwe bikagendera ku nama za OMS ku ngamba zo guhagarika ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu Ishuri ry'Ubuziranenge n'Ubuvuzi bw'Akarere k'i Londres yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 "igomba kuba ikwirakwira, ishobora kumara umwaka cyangwa ibiri".
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Imperial College iyobowe na Neil Ferguson, birasaba ko abantu bakomeza guhana intera n'abandi "kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba ruhari (bishoboka ko ruzamara amezi 18 cyangwa arenga)".
William Schaffner wo muri Kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati "Ntekereza ko coronavirus idashobora guhera burundu" kandi "ishobora guhinduka indwara y'ibihe, igaruka buri mwaka".
Uburyo bwo kongera kwanduza bizaterwa n'ubushobozi bw'ubwirinzi bw'umushinga w'ubwirinzi bw'ubwoko bw'ubwoko bwanduye.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe kandi abantu banduye bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara ni umuriro (88%) n'inkorora y'umura (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara ni umunaniro, guhumeka amabya (igihonge), kubura impumuro, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu myanya y'umubiri no mu ngingo, kubabara mu muhogo, umutwe, guhinda umushyitsi, gusesa, kuva amaraso, guturika, cyangwa kuribwa mu mazi. OMS ivuga ko hafi umuntu umwe kuri batandatu arwara cyane kandi akabura umwuka.
Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyerekana ibimenyetso by'ubutabazi nk'ubuhumekero buhagaze, ububabare bw'igifu cyangwa igitutu, urujijo rutunguranye, kudahita bikanguka, no kugira isura cyangwa iminwa y'ubururu; inama ni uko byihutirwa kwa muganga mu gihe ibi bimenyetso bihari.
Bamwe mu banduye bashobora kuba nta bimenyetso bafite, nta bimenyetso by'indwara ariko ibipimo byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi batanze inama ko abahuye n'abantu banduye bagombye gukurikiranwa cyane no gusuzumwa kugira ngo hatagira ubanduza.
Abashinwa bagereranya ko umubare w'abatabyumva ari bake ugera kuri 44%.
Igihe gisanzwe cyo kwinjiza mu mubiri (igihe hagati y'ubwandu n'igihe ibimenyetso bitangiriraho) gitangira ku munsi umwe kugeza ku minsi 14; akenshi ni iminsi itanu. Nk'urugero rw'ibitazwi neza, igishushanyo cy'umubare w'abantu banduye COVID-19 batakaje ubushobozi bwabo bwo kumva impumuro cyabanje kuba 30% hanyuma kigabanuka kigera kuri 15%.
Hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe birimo gukorwa kugira ngo tumenye uko iyo ndwara yandura.
Iyi ndwara bivugwa ko yandura cyane cyane mu gihe umuntu ahura n'undi ari hafi ye, ndetse no mu gihe umuntu yitsamuye, yitsamuye cyangwa avuze; aho umuntu ahura n'undi ari hafi ye ari muri metero 1 kugeza kuri 2 (3 kugeza kuri 6).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukorora umuntu atayambaye bishobora gutuma ibitonyanga by'amazi bigera kuri metero 4.5 kugeza kuri metero 8.2.
Hari abavuze ko virusi ishobora kandi kwandurwa n'udutonyanga duto tumara igihe kirekire mu kirere, dushobora kuvuka mu gihe umuntu avuga. Udutonyanga two mu myanya y'ubuhumekero dushobora no kuvuka mu gihe umuntu ahumeka, harimo no mu gihe umuntu avuga, nubwo virusi idakunze gukwirakwira mu kirere.
Utwo dutonyanga dushobora kugwa mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'abantu bari hafi cyangwa se tukaba twajya mu bihaha.
Hari uburyo bwo kuvura, nko gukoresha umuyoboro wo mu cyuma (intubation) no guhumura umutima n'ibihaha (CPR), bishobora gutuma uduhumeka two mu myanya y'ubuhumekero dutandukanywa n'umwuka (aerosol) bityo bigatuma tubyandurira mu mwuka.
Nanone ishobora gukwirakwira iyo umuntu akoze ku kintu cyanduye, harimo uruhu, hanyuma agakora ku maso, ku zuru cyangwa ku munwa.
Nubwo hari impungenge ko ishobora kwandura mu isuku, iki kibazo cyo cyemezwa ko ari gito.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yahakanye ko bishoboka ko SARS-CoV-2 yandura mu isesemi no mu kanwa. Iyi virusi yandura cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, nubwo hashobora kuba hari abantu bayikwirakwiza mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka no mu bihe by'uburwayi bya nyuma.
Abantu basuzumwe basanga baranduye mbere y'iminsi itatu mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira, bikaba byerekana ko umuntu ashobora kwandura mbere y'uko agaragaza ibimenyetso bikomeye.
Hari raporo nke cyane z'abantu bagaragaye ko barwaye nta bimenyetso bagaragaje, ariko hari ibihugu byabonye ko abantu barwaye nta bimenyetso bagaragaza mu gihe cyo gukurikirana abo bahuye na bo.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) kivuga ko nubwo bitamenyekanye neza uburyo iyi ndwara ikwirakwira mu buryo bworoshye, umuntu umwe muri rusange yandurira abandi babiri cyangwa batatu. Iyi virusi ikomeza kubaho ku bintu mu gihe cy'amasaha kugeza ku minsi.
By'umwihariko, virusi yagaragaye ko ishobora kugaragara kugeza ku minsi itatu kuri plastike (polypropylene) no kuri 304 ibyuma bitagira ingeso, ku munsi umwe kuri kartoni, no kugeza ku masaha ane kuri koperasi.
Ariko, ibi biratandukana bitewe n'ubushyuhe n'ubushyuhe. Inyamaswa zo mu ngo n'izindi nyamaswa zafashweho COVID-19.
Nta gihamya kigaragaza ko inyamaswa zishobora kwanduza abantu virusi, nubwo abayobozi bo mu Bwongereza batanga inama yo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kugirana imibonano n'inyamaswa, nk'uko bigenda nyuma yo kugirana imibonano n'ibindi bintu abantu banduye bashobora kuba barakozeho.
Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ni virusi nshya, yabonetse bwa mbere mu bantu batatu barwaye umusonga uterwa n'ubwandu bw'indwara y'ubuhumekero i Wuhan.
Ibiranga byose by'agakoko gashya ka SARS-CoV-2 biboneka mu bwoko bw'agakoko gatera indwara ya koronavirusi gakomoka ku bindi bikoko. Hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu, agakoko gaterwa n'isabune yo mu rugo, igabanya ubwirinzi bwabwo. SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano rya bugufi na SARS-CoV y'umwimerere.
Bitekerezwa ko ifite inkomoko yo mu nyamaswa.
Isesengura ry'imiterere y'umubiri ryagaragaje ko coronavirus ifite imiterere y'ubwoko bwa Betacoronavirus, mu bwoko bw'ibinogo (Sarbecovirus) (umurongo B) hamwe n'ubwoko bubiri buturuka ku ducurama.
Ni 96% bisa ku rwego rwa genome yose n'ibindi by'ibipimo bya virusi ya coronavirus y'inguge (BatCov RaTG13).
Muri Gashyantare 2020, abashakashatsi b'Abashinwa basanze hari itandukaniro rimwe gusa rya aside ya amino mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'urukurikirane rw'ibinyabuzima hagati ya virusi z'ibinyamushongo n'iz'abantu.
Kugeza ubu, ugereranya genome yose byagaragaje ko 92% by'ibinyabuzima byabangikanye hagati ya koronavirusi ya pangolin na SARS-CoV-2, ibyo bikaba bidahagije kugira ngo bigaragaze ko pangolin ari zo zigize umurwayi.
Indwara y'iyi virusi ishobora gusuzumwa by'agateganyo hashingiwe ku bimenyetso, nubwo byemezwa nyuma n'igisubizo cy'umurongo wa polymerases (rRT-PCR) cy'amasohoro yanduye cyangwa tomodensiteri.
Ubushakashatsi bugereranya PCR na CT mu mujyi wa Wuhan bwagaragaje ko CT ifite ubushobozi bwo gusobanukirwa cyane kurusha PCR, nubwo idafite ubushobozi bwihariye, aho byinshi mu bimenyetso byayo bihuza n'ibindi bicurane by'ibihaha n'ubundi burwayi.
Guhera muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika cy'Ubuvuzi bw'Imirasire cyatanze inama ko "CT itakoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa nk'igerageza rya mbere ryo gusuzuma COVID-19".
OMS yasohoye porotokoloni nyinshi zo gupima RNA kuri SARS-CoV-2, iya mbere ikaba yarasohotse ku ya 17 Mutarama.
Iyi kizamini ikoresha uburyo bw'igihe nyacyo bwo gusubiramo mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga (rRT-PCR).
Ikizamini gishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero cyangwa amaraso.
Ubusanzwe ibisubizo biboneka mu masaha make kugeza ku minsi.
Muri rusange iki kigeragezo gikorerwa ku cyuma cyo mu mazuru n'ubwo gishobora no gukoreshwa mu muhogo. Laboratwari nyinshi n'amasosiyete menshi arimo gukora ibipimo bya seroloji, bishobora kuvumbura abasirikare b'umubiri.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, nta na kimwe muri byo cyagaragajwe ko gihuje n'ukuri bihagije ku buryo cyemererwa gukoreshwa ku rwego rwagutse.
Muri Amerika, ikizamini cya seroloji cyakozwe na Cellex cyemejwe ko gikoreshwa mu bihe by'ubutabazi gusa na laboratwari zemewe.
Ibimenyetso byerekana amashusho kuri radiographie na tomographie ya computeri (CT) kubantu bafite ibimenyetso harimo ububiko bwa vitre bw'ibumoso bw'uruhande rw'uruhu kandi butagira amavuta.
Ishyirahamwe ry'ubuvuzi bw'imirasire y'ikirere ryo mu Butaliyani ririmo rirashyiraho urubuga mpuzamahanga rw'amakuru y'ibisubizo by'ibishushanyo ku barwayi bemejwe.
Kubera ko hari ibindi byorezo byanduza nka adenovirus, gufata amashusho nta cyemezo cya PCR bifite ubushobozi buke bwo kumenya COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeye bwakorewe mu Bushinwa bwagereranyije ibiva muri CT yo mu gatuza na PCR kandi bugaragaza ko nubwo tomorare idasanzwe ku ndwara, yihuta kandi ikumva cyane, bityo bikaba byerekana ko ishobora gukoreshwa nk'igikoresho cyo gupima mu turere turimo icyorezo.
Hakozwe imiyoboro y'imitsi igaragara ishingiye ku bwenge bw'ikoranabuhanga kugira ngo hamenyekane ibiranga virusi hakoreshejwe ibipimo bya rukurikirane rw'imirasire n'ibipimo bya CT.
Uburyo bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara burimo gukomeza kugira isuku muri rusange, gukaraba intoki, kwirinda gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa n'intoki zitajabiwe, gukorora cyangwa gusohora mu mpapuro z'uruhu no gushyira izo mpapuro mu icupa.
Abantu bashobora kuba bamaze kwandura bagiriwe inama yo kwambara agapfukamunwa mu ruhame.
Gukurikirana intera hagati y'abantu byasabwe kandi mu rwego rwo kwirinda kwanduzanya. Guverinoma nyinshi zabujije cyangwa zasabye abantu kwirinda ingendo zose z'ingenzi zivuye cyangwa zijya mu bihugu n'uturere byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Ariko, iyi virusi yageze ku rwego rwo gukwirakwira mu baturage mu bice byinshi by'isi.
Ibi bivuze ko virusi ikwirakwira mu baturage, kandi bamwe mu baturage ntibazi aho bayanduye cyangwa uko bayanduye. Abashinzwe ubuzima bita ku muntu ushobora kuba yanduye, basabwa gukoresha ingamba zisanzwe zo kwirinda, kwirinda guhura n'umuntu, no kwirinda amaso. Gukurikirana umuntu wanduye ni uburyo bw'ingenzi ku nzego z'ubuzima bwo kumenya aho yanduye ituruka no kwirinda ko yakwirakwizwa.
Gukoresha amakuru y'ahantu ku matelefoni ngendanwa na leta kuri iyi ntego byatumye impungenge z'ibanga, hamwe na Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 asohora itangazo risaba ko habaho imipaka kuri ubu bwoko bw'igenzura.
Hari porogaramu zitandukanye z'ingendo zakoreshejwe cyangwa zasabwe ko zakoreshwa ku bushake, kandi kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'inzobere arenga icumi yakoraga ku bisubizo by'ibanga, nko gukoresha Bluetooth kugira ngo igaragaze aho umukoresha ahuriye n'izindi telefoni.
Abakoresha bahabwa ubutumwa niba barigeze kuba hafi n'umuntu wanduye COVID-19. Hari ibitekerezo bitari byo ku bijyanye n'uburyo bwo kwirinda ubwandu; urugero, gukaraba mu mazuru no gukaraba mu kanwa ntibikora.
Nta rukingo rwa COVID-19 rubaho, nubwo imiryango myinshi irimo gukora ibishoboka byose ngo irukore.
Gukaraba intoki birasabwa kugira ngo wirinde ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara.
CDC ivuga ko abantu bagomba gukaraba intoki kenshi bakoresheje isabune n'amazi nibura amasegonda makumyabiri, cyane cyane nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero cyangwa igihe intoki zanduye; mbere yo kurya; na nyuma yo guhumeka izuru, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Impamvu ni uko iyo virusi igeze hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu, yicazwa n'isabune yo mu rugo, ikamenagura ikigega cyayo cy'ubwirinzi.
CDC kandi igasaba gukoresha umuti wica udukoko ku ntoki ufite nibura 60% by'umunyu w'alkoho, iyo isabune n'amazi bitaboneka.
OMS igira abantu inama yo kwirinda gukora ku maso, ku mazuru cyangwa ku munwa bakoresheje intoki zidakarabye.
Imirenge ishobora gukorerwa isuku n'imiti itandukanye (mu munota umwe wo kwanduzwa n'imiti yica udukoko ku gice cy'icyuma kitagira ingeso), harimo 6271% ya ethanol, 50100% ya isopropanol, 0.1% ya hypochlorite ya sodium, 0.5% ya peroxide ya hydrogene, na 0.27.5% ya povidone-iodine.
Izindi miti, nka benzalkonium chloride na chrohexidine gluconate, ntizikora cyane.
CDC irasaba ko niba umuntu akekwaho cyangwa hagaragaye ko afite COVID mu kigo nk'ibiro cyangwa aho bita ku bana, ahantu hose nko mu biro, mu bwiherero, ahantu rusange, ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki basangiye nk'ibikoresho bya tablet, touch screen, keyboard, controls za kure, na ATM zikoreshwa n'abarwayi, bigomba gukorerwa isuku.
Imiryango y'ubuzima yagiriye abantu inama yo kwipfuka umunwa n'izuru bakoresheje umukenke cyangwa agapfukamunwa iyo bakoroye cyangwa bahekenya, kandi bagaca agapfukamunwa ako kanya.
Abantu bashobora kuba banduye, basabwa kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi, kuko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya ubunini n'urugendo rw'utuntu tuva mu myanya y'ubuhumekero dutatanye mu gihe umuntu avuze, ahumura cyangwa akoroye.
OMS yatanze amabwiriza y'igihe n'uburyo bwo gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Stephen Griffin, inzobere mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, agira ati "kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya ubushake [bw'abantu] bwo gukora ku maso yabo, ari na byo bitera cyane cyane ubwandu iyo batagize isuku y'amaboko ikwiye".
OMS yatanze inama ko abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza bambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, nk'abita ku muntu urwaye COVID-19, nubwo bemera ko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda gukora ku maso yabo.
Ibihugu byinshi byatangiye gushishikariza abaturage gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, CDC irasaba kwambara udupfukamunwa tudakoreshwa mu buvuzi dukorwa mu mwenda. Ubushinwa bwasabye by'umwihariko ko abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza bakoresha udupfukamunwa dukoreshwa mu buvuzi, cyane cyane iyo bagiranye imishyikirano ya bugufi (1 metero (3 ft) cyangwa munsi yayo) n'abandi bantu.
Hong Kong irasaba kwambara agapfukamunwa igihe uri mu modoka cyangwa mu gihe uri ahantu hari abantu benshi.
Abategetsi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima muri Tayilande barimo gushishikariza abantu gukora udupfukamunwa tw'impu mu rugo no kuyuhagira buri munsi.
Repubulika ya Czech na Silovakiya byabujije abantu kujya hanze batambaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa batatwikiriye amazuru n'umunwa.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye buri wese kwambara agapfukamunwa mu maso igihe agiye ahantu rusange mu rwego rwo kwirinda no kurinda abandi.
Guverinoma ya Otirishiya yategetse ko umuntu wese winjira mu iduka ry'ibiribwa agomba kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Israel yasabye abaturage bose kwambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame.
Taiwan, yatangiye gukora udupfukamunwa miliyoni icumi ku munsi kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu hagati, yasabye abagenzi mu gari ya moshi no muri bisi zo mu mijyi hagati kwambara udupfukamunwa ku ya 1 Mata.
Panama yasabye ko bambara agapfukamunwa igihe cyose bagiye hanze, mu gihe kandi bagerageje gukora agapfukamunwa mu rugo ku badashobora kugura agapfukamunwa.
Udupfukamunwa kandi twakoreshejwe cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Maleziya na Singapour.
Gucunga intera hagati y'abantu (ibizwi no ku izina ry'igenzura ry'umubiri) bikubiyemo ingamba zo kurwanya ubwandu zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu kugabanya cyane abantu bagirana imishyikirano ya bugufi.
Bimwe mu buryo bukoreshwa harimo gushyira abantu mu kato; guhagarika ingendo; no gufunga amashuri, aho bakorera, sitade, ibibuga by'imikino cyangwa ibigo by'ubucuruzi.
Abantu bashobora gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kwirinda guhura n'abandi baguma mu rugo, bagabanya ingendo, bakirinda kujya ahantu hari abantu benshi, bakoresha uburyo bwo gusuhuza abantu badakorana, kandi bakirinda kwegerana n'abandi.
Ubu leta nyinshi zisaba abantu kwirinda kugendana n'abandi mu turere twazahajwe n'icyorezo cyangwa zikabatera inkunga yo kubigenza.
Umubare ntarengwa w'abantu bashoboraga guterana muri Amerika wategetswe n'inzego za leta n'imiryango y'ubuzima wahise ugabanywa uhereye ku bantu 250 (iyo nta cyorezo cya COVID-19 kizwi cyari cyakwirakwijwe mu karere runaka) ukurwa ku bantu 50, nyuma baza kugabanywa kugera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, u Budage bwabujije abantu guteranira ahantu hahurira abantu barenze babiri. Abantu bakuze n'abafite indwara z'ibyorezo nka diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko w'amaraso wo hejuru, n'abasirikare b'umubiri bafite ikibazo, bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye no kugira ibibazo kandi bagiriwe inama na CDC yo kuguma mu rugo aho bishoboka mu duce turimo icyorezo cy'abaturage. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima zatangiye gusimbuza ijambo "gushyira intera hagati y'abantu" ijambo "gushyira intera hagati y'abantu" kugira ngo bisobanure neza ko intego ari ukugabanya imbonankubone mu gihe bakomeza kugirana imishyikirano, haba mu buryo bw'umubiri cyangwa mu buryo bw'inyuma.
Gukoresha ijambo "kwitandukanya n'abandi" byateye impungenge ko abantu bagomba kwiherera mu buryo bwuzuye, aho kubashishikariza gukomeza guhana n'abandi bakoresheje ubundi buryo. Ubuyobozi bumwe bwatanze amabwiriza ajyanye n'ubuzima bw'imyororokere mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Muri izo nama harimo ko umuntu wakorana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu ubana na we gusa, kandi udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso byayo.
Kwigumira mu rugo byasabwe abantu basuzumwe COVID-19 n'abakeka ko banduye.
Ibigo by'ubuzima byatanze amabwiriza arambuye yo kwifungisha mu buryo bukwiriye. Guverinoma nyinshi zashyizeho cyangwa zigisha inama ko abantu bose baba mu turere twibasiwe n'icyorezo bifungira mu kato.
Amabwiriza akomeye cyane yo kwishyira mu kato yatanzwe ku bantu bari mu matsinda afite ibyago byinshi.
Abantu bashobora kuba baranduye COVID-19 n'ababa baherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa akarere karimo ubwandu bw'icyorezo, bagiriwe inama yo kwishyira mu kato k'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe bashoboraga kwandurira bwa nyuma.
Uburyo bwo kurwanya icyorezo ni uguhagarika cyangwa gukinga no kugabanya.
Gukumira indwara bikorwa mu bihe by'intangiriro by'icyorezo kandi bigamije gushakisha no gutandukanya abanduye ndetse no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kurwanya ubwandu no gukingira kugira ngo indwara ihagarike ikwirakwira mu bandi bantu.
Iyo bitagishoboka guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara, ingamba zo kuyirinda zikomeza: hafata ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo no kugabanya ingaruka zayo ku nzego z'ubuzima n'abaturage.
Gushyira hamwe ingamba zo gukumira no kugabanya ingaruka zishobora gukorwa icyarimwe.
Gukumira birasaba ingamba zikomeye cyane kugira ngo icyorezo kihagarikwe, hakagaragazwa ko umubare w'ibanze w'abandura ari munsi y'umubare 1. Kimwe mu bigize uburyo bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cyandura, ni ukugerageza kugabanya igihe cy'icyorezo, bizwi nko gupfundura uruziga rw'icyorezo.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo kuba serivisi z'ubuzima zirasubira kandi bigatanga igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo no kuvura.
Ingamba z'ibanze zidashobora guhagarika icyorezo harimo ingamba zo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko kugira isuku y'amaboko, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwishyira mu kato; ingamba z'abaturage zigamije gusiga intera hagati y'abantu nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika ibikorwa byo guterana; kwitabira kw'abaturage gushishikariza abantu kwemera no kwitabira ingamba nk'izo; ndetse n'ingamba z'ibidukikije nko gusukura imiterere. Ingamba zikomeye zigamije gukumira icyorezo zafashwe mu Bushinwa ubwo ubukana bw'icyorezo bwagaragaye, nko gushyira mu kato imigi yose no guhagarika ingendo mu buryo bukomeye.
Ibindi bihugu na byo byashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda yo gupima abantu benshi no gushyira mu kato abantu bari mu gace runaka, kandi itanga imiburo ku bihereranye n'aho abantu banduye binjira.
Singapore yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku banduye bishyize mu kato kandi itegeka amande menshi ku batakoze ibyo.
Taiwan yongereye umusaruro w'udupfukamunwa kandi ihana abacunga ibikoresho byo kwa muganga. Imigereranyo yo mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika igaragaza ko kugabanya (gugabanya ariko ntiguhagarika ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kucyirinda (guhindura icyorezo) bigira ibibazo bikomeye.
Politiki nziza zo kugabanya ingaruka zishobora kugabanya umubare w'abasaba ubuvuzi ku kigero cya 2/3 n'uw'abapfa ku kigero cya kabiri, ariko bikanazana impfu z'abantu ibihumbi amagana n'ingamba z'ubuzima zirengewe.
Gucunga bishobora kuba byiza ariko bikwiye gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba ruhari, niba ari rwo ruza mbere), kuko ubundi ubwandu bwasubira vuba iyo ingamba zorohewe.
Gahunda ndende yo guhashya icyorezo iteza ibibazo mu mibereho y'abaturage n'ubukungu.
Nta miti yihariye igabanya ubukana bw'agakoko ka COVID-19 yemewe, ariko hari ibikorwa birimo gukorwa, harimo no gupima imiti iriho.
Kumwa imiti yo mu rwego rwa siporo, kunywa ibinyobwa byinshi no kuruhuka bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso by'iyi ndwara.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'icyo cyorezo, umuntu ashobora gukenera guhabwa umwuka wa ogisijeni, imiti yo mu mitsi, no guhumeka.
Gukoresha imiti ya steroid bishobora gutuma ingaruka zirushaho kuba mbi.
Imiti myinshi yari yaremejwe mbere mu kuvura izindi ndwara z'ibyorezo irimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi kugira ngo ikoreshwe mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS kandi yavuze ko "umuti gakondo n'uw'imbere" ushobora koroshya ibimenyetso biterwa na SARS-CoV-19.
OMS ivuga ko kongera ubushobozi no guhuza ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi n'ibikenewe ku barwayi ba COVID-19 ari ingamba z'ingenzi zo guhangana n'icyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'akarere by'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'imirimo y'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze kugira ngo bihindure umutungo ku nzego nyinshi, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu bikorwa byo muri laboratwari kugira ngo bapime COVID-19, guhagarika ibikorwa by'amahitamo igihe cyose bishoboka, gutandukanya no gushyira mu kato abarwayi ba COVID-19 bafite ubwandu, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwaye cyane binyuze mu gutoza abakozi no kongera umubare w'ibikoresho byo guhumeka n'ibitanda bihari.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku birebana n'aho umuntu wa mbere wafashwe (uwitwa umurwayi wa mbere) ashobora kuba yaraturutse.
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanyeho iyi virusi nshya ya korona ashobora kuba yaragaragaye ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan, muri Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wazamutse buhoro buhoro.
Ibi ahanini byari bifitanye isano n'Isoko rya Huanan ry'Ibyokurya byo mu Nyanja, na ryo ryagurishaga inyamaswa nzima, kandi igitekerezo kimwe ni uko virusi yaturutse kuri imwe muri izo nyamaswa; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ifite inkomoko yo mu nyamaswa. Ikigo cya pneumonia y'impamvu itazwi cyabonetse ku ya 26 Ukuboza maze gifatwa na muganga Zhang Jixian mu bitaro by'Intara ya Hubei, wabwiye CDC ya Wuhan Jianghan ku ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo ku Bitaro by'Ikirenga bya Wuhan baburiye bagenzi babo ku "koronavirusi imeze nka SARS".
Abaganga umunani muri abo, barimo Li Wenliang, bahanwe na polisi kubera gukwirakwiza ibihuha, undi, Ai Fen, ahanwe n'abayobozi be kubera ko yazamuriye abantu ubwoba.
Komisiyo y'ubuzima y'Umujyi wa Wuhan yaje gushyira ahagaragara itangazo ku ya 31 Ukuboza maze imenyesha OMS.
Abantu benshi batari bamenyekana barwaye umusonga bari bamaze kubwirwa inzego z'ubuzima zo muri Wuhan kugira ngo hatangizwe iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama. Mu bihe bya mbere by'icyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri hafi buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yakwirakwijwe mu zindi ntara zo mu Bushinwa, ibi bikaba byaratewe n'ingendo z'Abashinwa mu gihe cy'Ubunani n'uko Wuhan ari ihuriro ry'ingendo n'umuhanda munini wa gariyamoshi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatanze raporo y'abantu bashya bagera hafi ku 140 banduye ku munsi umwe, barimo abantu babiri b'i Beijing n'umwe w'i Shenzhen.
Nyuma y'aho, amakuru yemewe yagaragaje ko abantu 6,174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zari zarenganyije u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani mu kugira umubare munini w'abantu banduye ku isi. Ku itariki ya 9 Mata 2020, abantu barenga 1.61 miliyoni banduye ku isi hose; abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye naho abasaga 364,000 barakize.
Ibihugu n'intara bigera kuri 200 byabonye nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije Uburayi, ibihugu byinshi mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu no gushyiraho uburyo bwo kugenzura imipaka.
Mu byo ibihugu byitabiriye harimo ingamba zo kwirinda nk'ibice by'ubwiherero (byitwa kuguma mu rugo, amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo, cyangwa gufunga) n'amasaha yo gutaha. Kugeza ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abaturage, bari mu bihe bimwe na bimwe byo gufunga muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu bihe by'ubwiherero muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 bari muri Afurika y'Epfo, naho abantu miliyari 1.3 bari mu bihe by'ubwiherero mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu buryo runaka bwa gahunda ya Guma mu Rugo, umubare wiyongereye ugera kuri miliyari 2.6 nyuma y'iminsi ibiri - ni ukuvuga hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wafashwe na COVID-19 yagaragaye ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo imwe itaremezwa igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere wafashwe yari uwo ku ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Muganga Zhang Jixian yabonye umubare w'abantu barwaye indwara y'ibihaha y'impamvu itaramenyekana ku ya 26 Ukuboza, maze ibitaro yari arimo bimenyesha CDC ya Wuhan Jianghan ku ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ibizamini bya mbere bya jenoside byakozwe ku bipimo by'abarwayi ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 byagaragaje ko hari coronavirus imeze nka SARS.
Itangazo rigenewe abantu bose ryatanzwe na Komisiyo y'ubuzima ya Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza.
OMS yamenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
Mu gihe ayo makuru yabaga, abaganga bo muri Wuhan baburiwe na polisi ko "bakwirakwiza ibihuha" ku cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'Ubushinwa ishinzwe ubuzima yabanje kuvuga ko nta "bihamya bifatika" by'uko umuntu yandura ku muntu.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukomeye nyuma y'aho bwiswe n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'u Bushinwa Xi Jinping ko ari "intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Mu cyiswe "karantiini nini cyane mu mateka y'abantu", ku ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe ko hashyizweho umurongo w'ubuziranenge uhagarika ingendo zijya no kuva i Wuhan, wagiye ugera mu mijyi 15 muri Hubei, uhitana abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 57.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite byari bibujijwe muri uwo mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (25 Mutarama) byakuweho mu duce twinshi.
Abayobozi kandi batangaje kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Huoshenshan, byarangiye mu minsi 10.
Ubundi bitaro byubatswe nyuma, ibitaro bya Leishenshan, kugirango bikemure abandi barwayi.
Usibye ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 muri Wuhan, nk'ibigo by'inama na sitade, mu bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho izindi ngamba zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga inyandiko z'ubuzima ku bagenzi no kongera iminsi mikuru y'Ubunani.
Kaminuza n'amashuri hirya no hino mu gihugu nabyo byafunzwe.
Uturere twa Hong Kong na Macau twashyizeho ingamba nyinshi, cyane cyane ku bijyanye n'amashuri na kaminuza.
Ingamba zo gukora mu cyerekezo cya kure zashyizweho mu turere dutandukanye tw'Ubushinwa.
Gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo yashyizweho muri Hubei no hanze yayo.
Imodoka zitwara abantu muri rusange zaravuguruwe, kandi amazu ndangamurage yo hirya no hino mu Bushinwa yarafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Gucunga urujya n'uruza rw'abantu rwarakoreshejwe mu mijyi myinshi, kandi byagereranyijwe ko abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (barenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bahuye n'uburyo runaka bwo kubuzwa kujya hanze. Nyuma y'uko icyorezo cyinjiye ku isi muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda ko virusi "yinjira" ivuye mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho gahunda y'iminsi 14 yo kwishyira mu kato ku bantu bose baturuka mu mahanga binjira mu mujyi. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Ubushinwa bw'igihangange bwari bwanduye umuntu umwe gusa mu minsi itanu yabanjirije iyo tariki, muri urwo rwego ni umuntu wari uvuye i Istanbul agaruka i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bushinwa, Li Keqiang, yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bw'indwara bwandurira mu gihugu cyarangiye kandi ko icyorezo cyagenwe mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingendo zabujijwe muri Hubei zarorohejwe, uretse muri Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri ingendo zibujijwe. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira mu gihugu ku bafite viza cyangwa impushya zo gutura ku isi bizaba bihagaritswe guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, nta makuru yihariye atangazwa ku gihe iyo politiki izarangirira.
Abifuza kwinjira mu Bushinwa bazajya basaba visa muri za ambasade cyangwa za konsula za China.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'inganda kongera gufungura ku ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku bigo. Inama y'igihugu yatangaje umunsi w'icyunamo uzatangirana n'isaha ya gatatu y'agacerere ku ya 4 Mata, ku isaha ya saa kumi n'ebyiri, bihuye n'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming, nubwo guverinoma nkuru yasabye imiryango kujya kuri interineti mu kubahiriza gahunda yo kwirinda guhana intera kugira ngo birinde icyorezo cya COVID-19 kongera kwaduka.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yakwirakwijwe muri Koreya y'Epfo ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020 iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu cyita ku buzima cyatangaje ko habayeho kwiyongera kw'abanduye ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare, ahanini bitewe n'iteraniro ryabereye i Daegu ry'umuryango mushya w'idini uzwi nka Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abantu b'intagondwa za Shincheonji basuye Daegu baturutse i Wuhan bakekwaho kuba inkomoko y'icyorezo.
Guhera ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9,336 b'iri torero, 1,261 cyangwa hafi 13% bavuze ko bagaragaje ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko igipimo cyo hejuru cy'ubwirinzi ari ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2,000 byemejwe ko banduye muri Koreya, biyongera bigera ku 3,150 ku ya 29 Gashyantare.
Inzego zose za gisirikare za Koreya y'Epfo zafatiwe mu kato nyuma y'uko ibizamini byemeje ko abasirikare batatu banduye virusi.
Ibihe by'ingendo by'indege nabyo byagizweho ingaruka, bityo bihindurwa. Koreya y'Epfo yatangije gahunda yafashwe nk'ikomeye kandi iteganyijwe neza ku isi yo gusuzuma abaturage kugira ngo barebe ko nta virusi ihari, no gushyira mu kato abantu bose banduye, ndetse no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima harimo ko abimukira bashya bo mu mahanga bagomba kuzajya biyandikisha ubwabo bakamenyekanisha ibimenyetso byabo bakoresheje porogaramu ya telefoni igendanwa, gupima virusi mu modoka, ibizamini bigatangazwa umunsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima kugira ngo abantu bagera ku 20,000 bapimwe buri munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'iyigezeho mu kurwanya iki cyorezo nubwo itashyize mu kato imijyi yose. Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo mu ntangiriro wari ufite ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yitabiriye iki kibazo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon yahanishwa kubera ibyo bavugaga ko ari uburyo leta yakoresheje nabi icyorezo, cyangwa bagashimagiza uko yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byavuzwe ko Koreya y'Epfo yagize umubare muto w'abanduye mu munsi umwe mu byumweru bine bishize.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abava mu mahanga bose bazajya bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibitangazamakuru ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yabonye ibyifuzo byo gufasha mu gupima virusi biturutse mu bihugu 121.
Irani yatangaje ko abantu ba mbere banduye SARS-CoV-2 bayanduye ku ya 19 Gashyantare i Qom, aho, nk'uko Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi mu Buvuzi ibivuga, abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma kuri uwo munsi.
Ingamba za mbere leta yatangaje harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi birori ndangamuco, ibirori by'imikino, amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, ndetse no gufunga za kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yatanze miriyari eshanu z'amafaranga y'amafaranga y'u Rwanda yo kurwanya iyo virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twazahajwe n'icyorezo, kandi abantu bonyine ni bo bari gushyirwa mu kato.
Gahunda zo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi zatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo urujya n'uruza rukomeye hagati y'imijyi mbere y'umwaka mushya w'Abaperesi Nowruz rwakomeje.
Insengero z'Abashiya i Qom zakomeje gufungurirwa abasenga kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020. Iran yabaye ihuriro ry'ikwirakwizwa rya virusi nyuma y'Ubushinwa muri Gashyantare.
Mu gihe hari hari abavuga ko hari ikinyegezo cy'uko icyorezo cyateye muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byasuzumye ko byanduye muri Irani ku ya 28 Gashyantare, bikaba byerekana ko icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha 388 by'abanduye byatangajwe na leta ya Irani kuri uwo munsi.
Inteko Ishinga Amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, aho 23 mu bamenyeshamakuru 290 bayigize batangajwe ko banduye virusi ku ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza muri Irani kurekura byanze bikunze abarengera uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe kubera imyigaragambyo y'amahoro, no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zifite uburenganzira.
Yavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi by'uko virusi yakwirakwira mu bigo bifunze nka za gereza, na zo zidafite ubuvuzi buhagije.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi umwe, ari na bo benshi cyane bapfuye muri icyo gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 bariho cyangwa bahozeho muri Irani n'abategetsi ba leta bari barishwe n'iyo ndwara.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Iran yari ifite abantu bashya 50 buri isaha n'undi muntu umwe buri minota icumi bapfa kubera coronavirus.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umutegetsi wa OMS, muri Irani hashobora kuba hari abanduye bakubye inshuro eshanu ugereranyije n'abatangazwa.
Hari kandi igitekerezo cy'uko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani bishobora kuba bigira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'igihugu mu by'ubukungu bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Komiseri w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ushinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu byoroherezwa ku bihugu byibasiwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Byaremejwe ko icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo abakerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa basuzumwaga bagasanga baranduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Umubare w'abanduye watangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege ziva cyangwa zijya mu Bushinwa, ndetse itangaza ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe.
Nyuma y'aho, habonetse itsinda ry'abantu banduye COVID-19 batari bahuje ubwoko, batangiranye n'abantu 16 byemejwe ko banduye muri Lombardy ku wa 21 Gashyantare. Ku wa 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya rigenga kurwanya icyorezo, harimo gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50.000 bo mu mijyi 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Mu bice birimo icyorezo, kwinjira no gusohoka ntibizatangwa.
Gufunga ibikorwa by'akazi n'ibikorwa bya siporo byamaze gutegekwa muri utwo turere".Ku ya 4 Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza mu gihugu hose zifungwa burundu mu gihe Ubutaliyani bwari bugeze ku bantu 100 bapfuye.
Ibikorwa byose by'imikino ikomeye, harimo n'imikino y'umupira w'amaguru ya Serie A, byari bigomba kuba nyuma y'inzugi zifunze kugeza mu kwezi kwa Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, siporo yose yahagaritswe burundu nibura mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse ko ibikorwa hafi ya byose by'ubucuruzi bihagarikwa uretse ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'amafarumasi. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani gishinzwe ubuvuzi bw'indwara z'ubuhumekero, ubufasha bw'indwara zo mu mutwe, ubufasha bwo guhumeka no kwita ku barwayi bababaye (SIAARTI) cyasohoye amabwiriza ajyanye n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye n'amabwiriza yo kugenzura abagwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwatsinze u Bushinwa buza ku mwanya wa mbere mu bihugu byagize umubare munini w'abantu bishwe na coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutangaza ko abantu 3,405 bishwe n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje indege z'igisirikare icyenda zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari hamaze kuboneka abantu 128,948, abamaze gupfa ni 15,887 naho abakize ni 21,815, abenshi muri abo bakaba ari abo mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN yagaragaje ko kuba mu Butaliyani hari abantu benshi bageze mu zabukuru hamwe no kuba nta bushobozi bwo gupima abantu bose bafite virusi kugeza ubu bishobora kuba ari byo bituma umubare w'abapfa wiyongera.
Igisubizo cy'Ubwongereza kuri virusi cyaje bwa mbere nk'imwe mu bihugu byorohewe cyane mu bihugu byayanduye, kandi kugeza ku itariki ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'Ubwongereza ntiyigeze ishyiraho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kwirinda kwegerana cyangwa ingamba zo gushyira mu kato abantu benshi ku baturage bayo.
Ingaruka yabaye uko, leta yaje kunengwa kubera ko yabonye ko hari ibura ry'umuvuduko n'imbaraga mu gusubiza ibibazo abaturage bahuraga na byo. Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatanze itangazo ryamugira inama yo kwirinda ingendo zose zidakenewe no guhura n'abantu, asaba abantu gukorera mu rugo aho bishoboka no kwirinda ahantu hatandukanye nko mu kabari, muri resitora no mu bibuga by'imikino.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ibigo by'imyidagaduro byose nk'amaduka n'ibigo by'imyitozo bigomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi yemeza ko izatanga 80% by'umushahara w'abakozi ku gipimo cya £2,500 ku kwezi kugira ngo birinde ubushomeri muri iki cyorezo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikakaye zo kwirinda guhura, abuza abantu barenga babiri guteranira hamwe no kugabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze ku bikorwa bibonwa ko ari ngombwa cyane.
Bitandukanye n'ingamba zafashwe mbere, aya mabwiriza yashyirwaga mu bikorwa na polisi binyuze mu gutanga amande no gusakaza abantu.
Ibigo byinshi byategetswe gufunga, usibye ibikorwa bifatwa nk'ibikenewe cyane, harimo amaduka manini, farumasi, amabanki, amaduka y'ibikoresho, za sitasiyo za peteroli, n'igaraji.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 yemejwe muri leta ya Washington mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika, mu muntu wari wasubiye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Itsinda ry'abashinzwe kurwanya icyorezo cya Coronavirus ryashinzwe ku wa 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe by'ubuzima rusange, kandi buhagarika abagenzi baturuka mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara - ikigo cy'ubuzima rusange cya mbere cya leta ya Amerika - cyatangaje ko cyakoze ibikoresho by'igerageza ubwaryo.
Nubwo Amerika yabikoze, yatangiye gupima byikora buhoro, bituma hatagaragara neza urugero icyorezo cyari cyaragezeho icyo gihe.
Ibipimo byaranzwe n'ibikoresho by'ibizamini by'ubwandu byakozwe na leta ya leta muri Gashyantare, kubura kwemerwa na leta y'igihugu ku bikoresho by'ibizamini by'ibizamini by'abikorera (byakozwe n'amashuri, ibigo n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, n'amabwiriza y'abantu batemerewe gukora ibizamini kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (nyuma y'aho byasabwaga ko umuganga atanga icyangombwa).
Kugeza ku ya 27 Gashyantare, The Washington Post yatangaje ko muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hasuzumwe abantu batageze ku 4000.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, The Atlantic yatangaje ko hasuzwe ibizamini 14,000.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko: "Abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso kandi muganga akaba yategetse ko bategereza amasaha cyangwa iminsi kugira ngo bapimwe". Nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika rwatangajwe muri leta ya Washington ku ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe, igikorwa cyaje gukurikirwa n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu gace ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, maze mu kwezi kwa gatatu hagati, amashuri yo mu gihugu hose yari amaze gufunga. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Amerika yamenyeshejwe ko hari ibyatangajwe ku ngaruka z'icyorezo cya koronavirusi nshya ku gihugu n'itsinda ry'inzobere mu by'indwara zo mu rwego rw'ubwandu muri kaminuza ya Imperial College London.
Kuri uwo munsi Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryerekeye kwitegura no kurwanya Coronavirus, ryatanze miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari y'ingoboka y'ibigo bya leta kugira ngo byitabire iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho amategeko abuza abakozi gukora ingendo, yahagaritse inama, kandi ashishikariza abakozi gukorera mu rugo.
Ibikorwa bya siporo n'ibihe by'imikino byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, uretse u Bwongereza, bizaba bifunze ingendo mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yagaragaje ko ibyo bihano bigomba no kongerwa ku Bwongereza na Irilande.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe, byatumye amafaranga ya leta aboneka kugira ngo yitabire iki kibazo.
Guhera ku ya 15 Werurwe, ibikorwa byinshi by'ubucuruzi byafunze cyangwa byagabanyije amasaha yo gukora muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika kugira ngo bigerageze kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari cyemejwe muri leta 50 zose no mu Ntara ya Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko mu mujyi wa New York hari abantu 10,700 banduye coronavirus, bakaba baruta umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, Guverineri yavuze ko kwitandukanya n'abandi byagaragaraga ko ari byiza, kuko imibare y'uko umubare w'abanduye wiyongera kabiri wagabanutse uva ku minsi 2.0 ukagera ku minsi 4.7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, muri New York City hari abarwayi 32,308 bagaragaye ko banduye, kandi abantu 672 bari barishwe na virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zavuzwe ko zifite abantu benshi bagaragaye ko banduye coronavirus kurusha ibindi bihugu byose ku isi, harimo u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ku ya 8 Mata, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hari hamaze kugaragara abarwayi 400,335 bagaragaye ko banduye, kandi abantu 12,841 barapfuye.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku ya 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Trump, yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda guhana intera hagati y'abantu kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, USNS Comfort, ubwato bw'ibitaro bufite ibitanda 1000, bwahagaze i New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Amerika yagize umubare w'abantu 884 bapfuye bazize coronavirus mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Muri leta ya New York, abanduye barenze abantu 100,000 ku ya 3 Mata. White House yanenzwe ko igabanyije ubukana bw'iki kibazo no kugenzura ubutumwa binyuze mu kuyobora abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza imvugo n'ibitabo by'abaturage bijyanye n'iyi virusi n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Impamvu abantu benshi bemera uburyo Trump ayoboye iki kibazo cy'ubukungu, ni uko ibyo yavuze ari ibyerekeye amashyaka.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Amerika n'abatanga ibitekerezo banenze Amerika kuba yishingira ku byo yinjiza mu gihugu bikenewe cyane, birimo ibikoresho by'ibanze by'ubuvuzi, biva mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'ingendo z'indege ryakoreshejwe kugira ngo harebwe kandi hategurwe uko ikwirakwira rizasohoka mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa Mutarama hagati muri 2020.
Hashingiwe ku makuru yo mu 2018 yatanzwe n'Ishyirahamwe Mpuzamahanga ry'Ingabo zo mu Kirere, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo byiganjemo abagenzi bavuye i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne nabyo byavuzwe ko ari ahantu hakunzwe cyane ku bantu bava i Wuhan.
Bali ni wo mujyi wavuzwe ko ufite ubushobozi buke mu mijyi 20 ikunzwe cyane mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yo ifatwa nk'ifite ubushobozi bwinshi. Ositaraliya yasohoye gahunda yo guhangana n'icyorezo cya Koronavirusi (COVID-19) ku ya 7 Gashyantare.
Yavuze ko hari byinshi bigikeneye kuvumburwa kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu kugenzura imipaka no gutumanaho mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko hari ikibazo cy'umutekano w'abantu.
Kubera ko mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei hashyizwe mu kato imodoka zifata abantu mu ngendo, ibihugu byinshi byateguye gutahukana abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi muri ako gace, cyane cyane hakoreshejwe indege z'igihugu cy'iwabo, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bakaba batanze uruhushya.
Kanada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, u Buyapani, u Buhindi, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, u Bufaransa, Arijantine, u Budage na Tayilande ni byo bihugu bya mbere byateguye gahunda yo guhungisha abaturage babyo.
Pakistan yavuze ko nta baturage bayo bazaba bava mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Brezili yavanye 34 bo muri Brezili cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo usibye Abanyapolonye bane, Umunyashinwa n'Umuhinde.
Aba baturage bo muri Polonye, u Bushinwa n'u Buhinde, bavuye mu ndege yabo muri Polonye, aho indege ya Burezili yahagaze mbere yo gukomeza urugendo igana muri Burezili.
Abaturage ba Brazil bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato mu kigo cya gisirikare hafi ya Brasília.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abanyakanada 215 (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere, na 39 bari mu ndege ya kabiri y'ubutegetsi bwa Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan bajyanwa muri CFB Trenton kugira ngo bashyirwe mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege y'Abanyakanada 185 bari baturutse i Wuhan yageze ku kigo cya CFB Trenton.
Ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, abategetsi ba Ositaraliya bafashe abaturage 277 babajyana mu kigo cyo muri icyo kirwa cya Christmas Island, cyari cyarahindutse ahantu ho gushyirwa mu kato, aho bagumye iminsi 14.
Indege yo gutahuka muri Nouvelle Zelande yageze muri Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe baturutse muri Ositaraliya na Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cy'ingabo z'inyanja i Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangaje ko zizakura Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abakerarugendo b'Abanyakanada 129 bari baravanywe muri Diamond Princess, yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubuhinde yatangiye gucyura abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe indege ya South African Airways yakodeshejwe na Guverinoma ya Afurika y'Epfo yasubije mu gihugu abaturage 112 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo.
Ibizamini byo kwa muganga byakozwe mbere yo kugenda, kandi Abanyafurika y'Epfo bane bagaragazaga ibimenyetso bya coronavirus basigaye inyuma kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abaturage bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bapimwe bagasanga nta bimenyetso biranga ko banduye, ni bo bonyine bongeye gutaha.
Ibisubizo by'ibizamini byemeje ko abaturage bose bo muri Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abapilote, abakozi bo muri hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bagize uruhare mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, bose, nk'ingamba zo kwirinda, bagumye mu kato no mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri The Ranch Resort.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangiye gukura igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarusi, Pakistani, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri za kaminuza zo muri Amerika bafatanyije gufasha mu kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'u Bushinwa byibasiwe na virusi, aho itsinda ry'abari mu gace ka Chicago bivugwa ko ryabashije kohereza udupfukamunwa 50,000 twa N95 mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Umuryango w'ubutabazi bw'abantu, Direct Relief, ufatanyije na FedEx, wohereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 tw'amaso hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi, harimo uturindantoki n'imyenda, mu ndege yo mu buryo bw'impanuka ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union, bitarenze ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko batanze miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ku muryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (WHO) mu gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku nkingo no kwivuza ndetse no kurinda "abantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo".
Interaksyon yatangaje ko guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Filipine ku wa 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapore yatangaje ko izohereza inkunga ya miliyoni $2.26 mu Bushinwa.
U Buyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe muri Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje itangwa ry'impamba z'imiti z'ubuvuzi miriyoni 18 mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitandukanye birimo imyenda 10,000 ya Hazmat, kandi Amerika yatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa ndetse n'amasezerano yo kongeramo miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'ubufasha bw'amafaranga mu bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo. Nyuma y'uko abanduye mu Bushinwa basa n'abatuje, iki gihugu cyatangiye kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu bitandukanye byibasiwe n'iki cyorezo.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'inzobere mu gufasha u Butaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya koronavirusi.
Umunyemari Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima 1.1 miliyoni, udupfukamunwa 6 miliyoni, n'imyambaro yo kwikingira 60,000 i Addis Ababa, Ethiopia kugira ngo byatangwe n'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho 5,000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho 5 byo guhumeka muri Panama.
Ma kandi yatanze inkunga y'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Kanada. Ubuholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Tchèque bagaragaje impungenge zabo ku masike n'ibikoresho by'igerageza byakorewe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yahagaritse ibikoresho 58 000 byo gupima coronavirus byakozwe mu Bushinwa bifite ubuziranenge bwa 30%, mu gihe u Buholandi bwo bwahagaritse udupfukamunwa 600 000 tw'Abashinwa twari dufite inenge.
Ububiligi bwongeye kwibuka udupfukamunwa 100.000 tudashobora gukoreshwa, twibwira ko ari utwo mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twari utwo muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubufasha bw'u Bushinwa bwakiriwe neza mu bice bimwe bya Amerika y'Alatini na Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubutabazi bwihutirwa ku bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye imbaraga abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashyizeho mu gucunga no gukumira iki cyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, aho abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwaga ibanga ryatumye ingamba zo gukumira no gukumira zidashoboka, n'ikibazo kiriho ubu aho guverinoma nkuru "yatanze amakuru mashya buri gihe kugira ngo yirinde guhungabana mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'Ubunani bw'umwaka mushya".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu kwitabira icyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ibanze cyo gushyira mu bikorwa itegeko ryo kubuza abantu gutwara abantu mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Gauden Galea uhagarariye OMS yavuze ko nubwo "nta gushidikanya ko atari inama OMS yatanze", ariko kandi ko "ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cy'uko biyemeje guhashya icyorezo ahantu cyiganjemo" kandi ko "ntaho bigeze mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko cyanduriye mu bantu hanze y'Ubushinwa no kwiyongera kw'abanduye mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange gihangayikishije Isi (PHEIC), kikaba ari icya gatandatu PHEIC kuva icyo cyemezo cyatangira gukoreshwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cyo mu 2009.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko icyorezo cya PHEIC cyatewe n'uko "kwiyongera kw'indwara ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite ubukire buri hagati n'uburebure bw'aho, bidafite gahunda z'ubuzima zikomeye.
Mu gusubiza ku ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'amabwiriza yo guhagarika ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zidakenewe mu kubangamira ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "OMS idasaba kugabanya ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira ibikorwa by'ubukangurambaga mu bihugu bikennye, ivuga ko byihutirwa gushyigikira ibyo bihugu "bidafite uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye virusi, kabone n'iyo yaba igaragara".
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "dufite imbaraga nk'iz'uruhande rwacu rw'ibanze rufite intege nke" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "gushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura menshi nyuma". Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru yashyizeho COVID-19 nk'izina ry'iyi ndwara.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, António Guterres, yemeye gutanga "imbaraga z'urwego rwose rwa Loni mu gusubiza".
Iki cyemezo cyatumye hashyirwaho itsinda ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye rishinzwe kurwanya ibiza, ryemera guhuza ibikorwa byose by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, OMS ivuga ko bizatuma "bashobora kwibanda ku bikorwa byo kwita ku buzima mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora gukoresha ubumenyi bwazo mu gukemura ibibazo by'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere by'icyorezo".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'abakozi ba OMS bayoboye mu Bushinwa ryatangiye gutanga impuguke mpuzamahanga na OMS ku butaka mu Bushinwa kugira ngo zifashe mu gucunga no gusuzuma "uburemere n'ubwandu bw'iki cyorezo" binyuze mu gukora amahugurwa no guhura n'ibigo by'ingenzi ku rwego rw'igihugu no gusura ahantu hagamijwe gusuzuma "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo kurwanya mu ntara no mu ntara, harimo n'ibiturage n'utugari". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi igomba gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo gishobora kuba cya coronavirus", ivuga ko nubwo hakiri kare cyane ngo cyitwe icyorezo, ibihugu bikwiye "mu bihe byo kwitegura".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo cyagendaga kivuka muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'abakozi ba OMS muri icyo gihugu kugira ngo barebe uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko igipimo cy'ubukana bwa coronavirus ku rwego rw'isi yose kizazamurwa kiva ku "gikuze" kikagera ku "gikuze cyane", ni ukuvuga igipimo cyo hejuru cy'ubutabazi n'igiciro cy'ibyago.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda y'ibihe byihutirwa byo mu rwego rw'ubuzima ya OMS, yaburiye mu itangazo ko "Ibi ari ibipimo by'ukuri kuri buri butegetsi ku isi: ni ukubyuka.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba igiye kuza kandi ugomba kuba witeguye", asaba ko ingamba ziboneye zo guhangana na yo zafasha isi kwirinda "ibibi cyane".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu adaha abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage uburenganzira bwo gutangaza icyorezo cy'isi yose, avuga ko gutangaza ko icyorezo ari icyorezo cy'isi yose bivuze ko "mu by'ukuri twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi ashobora kwandura iyo virusi".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko OMS "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'urwego rw'ubwandu n'uburemere bwihutirwa, ndetse n'urwego rw'uburangare bwihutirwa". OMS yahuye n'ibihano bikomeye kubera ko itafashe neza icyorezo, harimo no kuba yarateje akaga mu rwego rw'ubuzima rusange kandi ikagashyira virusi mu cyiciro cy'indwara y'icyorezo.
Mu byagarutsweho harimo gusaba ko Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS Tedros Adhanom atanga imihoho, yashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733,000 kugeza ku ya 6 Mata.
Ku wa 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke nyinshi z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu zashimangiye ko uburenganzira bwa buri muntu bugomba kubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryemeje ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo gukora ibikorwa byo kurokora ubuzima kandi ko Leta ari yo ifite ubwo burenganzira.
Iri tsinda ryatangaje ko kuba nta mafaranga cyangwa ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima byemewe, bitagomba na rimwe kuba urwitwazo rwo kurobanura itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bashimangiye ko buri muntu afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abantu bafite ubumuga, abo mu matsinda mato, abageze mu za bukuru, abantu bimuriwe mu byabo, abadafite aho kuba, ababana n'ibibazo by'ubukene, abafungiwe, impunzi n'abandi bantu batagaragajwe bakeneye inkunga ya leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ya leta irimo gukemura ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage byatewe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubumwe n'Iterambere mu by'Ubukungu watangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru ku gihe kandi arambuye ku buryo ibihugu byo hirya no hino ku isi byagiye bikemura ibibazo, ndetse n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku ngamba zo gukomeza gahunda z'ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi kugeza ku gukemura ingaruka zo gufunga no kugabanya ingendo, ihuriro rya digitale ririmo igishushanyo mbonera cy'igihugu, kandi rigamije gufasha ibihugu kwigira ku bindi no korohereza igisubizo gihuriweho cy'isi yose ku kibazo cya coronavirus.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Minisitiri w'Abaminisitiri mu Bwongereza Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brazil Jair Bolsonaro Eduardo Bolsonaro kubera uburyo yakiriye icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei yo mu Bushinwa.
Abategetsi benshi bo mu ntara z'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa (CPC) birukanywe kubera uko bakemuye ibibazo by'ibikorwa byo gushyira mu kato mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, ikimenyetso cy'uko batishimiye uburyo ubutegetsi bwa politiki bwakiriye icyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bemeza ko iki gikorwa cyari kigamije kurinda umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'aba Komuniste b'u Bushinwa Xi Jinping uburakari bw'abaturage kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Abashinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, banze kwemera ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiye i Wuhan, bahitamo kwemera ko hari ibitekerezo by'ubutagondwa ku bijyanye na COVID-19 byaturutse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubutegetsi bwa Donald Trump muri Amerika bwise coronavirus " virusi y'Ubushinwa " cyangwa " virusi ya Wuhan " buvuga ko "kugenzura kw'Ubushinwa kwongereye virusi ubu yahindutse icyorezo ku isi hose", ibyo na byo byanenzwe na bamwe mu banenga ko ari ivangura rishingiye ku moko no "gutesha umutwe [ku] kunanirwa kw'ubutegetsi bwe kurwanya icyorezo".
Daily Beast yabonye ubutumwa bwa leta ya Amerika bugaragaza uburyo bwo gutumanaho bigaragara ko buturuka mu Nama y'Igihugu y'Umutekano, aho ingamba zivugwaho ko "Byose byerekeye Ubushinwa.
Tubwirwa ko tugomba kugerageza gutangaza ubwo butumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo n'inama z'abanyamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo".Ibitangazamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy, na Bloomberg byatangaje ko imbaraga z'u Bushinwa zo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe na virusi ari igice cy'ibikorwa byo gukwirakwiza poropagande yo gushaka kugira ingaruka ku isi.
Umuyobozi wa politiki y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi, Josep Borrell, yaburiye ko hari "igice cya geo-politike kirimo guharanira kugira ingaruka binyuze mu gukinisha no mu 'politiki y'ubuntu'".
Borrell kandi yavuze ko "Ubushinwa burimo butera imbere ubutumwa ko, bitandukanye na Amerika, ko ari umufatanyabikorwa ufite inshingano kandi wizewe".
Ubushinwa kandi bwasabye Amerika gukuraho ibihano yafatiye Syria, Venezuela na Iran, mu gihe bivugwa ko yohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Gutanga udupfukamunwa 100 000 kwa Jack Ma kwahagaritswe n'ibihano bya Amerika ku ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi ba Amerika barashinjwa kandi ko bahinduye imfashanyo yagenewe ibindi bihugu ikajya mu gihugu cyabo.
Hari kandi impaka zijyanye n'udupfukamunwa zavuzwe hagati y'ibindi bihugu, nk'u Budage, Otirishiya n'Ubuswise; na Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe imashini zo guhumeka amagana zari zigenewe Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yanenze Ubumwe bw'u Burayi ku kuba butabaye nk'u Butaliyani bwibasiwe na coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani mu muryango w'ibihugu by'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa ari bwo bwonyine bwasubije mu buryo bw'impande zombi.
Nta gushidikanya, iki si ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubwiyunge bw'u Burayi".
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo guhamagara kuri telefone Minisitiri w'intebe w'u Butaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yateganyije ko ingabo z'u Burusiya zohereza abaganga b'igisirikare, imodoka zihariye zo gukaraba no gukoresha ibindi bikoresho byo kwa muganga mu Butaliyani.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo amagambo y'umuntu utazwi, "umunyapolitiki ukomeye" wavuze ko 80 ku ijana by'imfashanyo z'u Burusiya "ari imfabusa cyangwa ko nta cyo zigeza ku Butaliyani".
Uyu muntu yashinje Uburusiya gutangira igitero cyo "kubeshyera abantu mu rwego rwa politiki n'ubuvugizi".
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Butaliyani, Luigi Di Maio, banze ibyo itangazamakuru ryanditse, kandi bagaragaza ko bashimira.
Uburusiya na bwo bwo bwohereje indege y'indege iherekeje Amerika imfashanyo z'ubuvuzi.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko "iyo Putin atanga ubufasha ku bakozi bagenzi be bo muri Amerika, aba atekereza ko igihe abakora ibikoresho n'ibikoresho byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi muri Amerika bazaba bafite imbaraga, na bo bazaba bashobora kubikora mu gihe bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya OTAN "Defender 2020" iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye, n'ibihugu bya Baltique, imyitozo ya gisirikare ikomeye cyane ya OTAN kuva intambara y'ubutita irangiye, izaba ku rwego ruciriritse.
Umunyamabanga mukuru wa Kaminuza y'Igihugu Ishinzwe Ihagarika ry'Ibitwaro bya Nyukliya, Kate Hudson, yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020 agira ati: "Mu bibazo by'ubuzima rusange biriho ubu, ntabwo bibangamiye ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi byitabiriye gusa, ahubwo binashyira mu kaga ubuzima bw'abaturage bo mu bihugu bakoreramo". Leta ya Irani yagezweho cyane n'iyi virusi, aho abayoboke bagera kuri babiri b'inteko ishinga amategeko bayanduye kimwe n'abandi bantu cumi na batanu ba politiki bariho cyangwa bahoze bayirimo.
Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yandikiye ibaruwa rusange abayobozi b'isi abasaba ubufasha ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, avuga ko igihugu cye kiri guhangana n'icyorezo kubera kubura uburyo bwo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani. Icyorezo cyateye inkunga Amerika yo gushyiraho politiki z'imibereho rusange mu bindi bihugu bikize, harimo kwita ku buzima rusange, kwita ku bana bose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango cyishyurwa, n'ibiciro byo hejuru by'ingengo y'imari ku buzima rusange.
Abasesenguzi mu bya politiki bari biteze ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku bushobozi bwa Donald Trump bwo kongera gutorwa mu matora ya perezida yo mu 2020. Imishyikirano ya dipolomasi hagati ya Japon na Koreya y'Epfo yaragabanutse kubera iki cyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "ibikorwa by'uburangare kandi bidafite ishingiro" by'Ubuyapani nyuma y'uko Ubuyapani butangaje ko umuntu wese uzava muri Koreya y'Epfo azajya ashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri ahantu hashyizweho na leta.
Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo mu ntangiriro wari ufite ibitekerezo binyuranye ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yitabiriye icyo kibazo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko y'isabira Moon gucibwa mu kazi kubera ibyo bavugaga ko ari uburyo leta itakoresheje mu guhangana n'icyorezo, cyangwa bashima uburyo yakiriye. Icyorezo cyemereye ibihugu gushyiraho amategeko y'ubutabazi mu rwego rwo guhangana nacyo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bagaragaje impungenge z'uko bishobora gutuma leta zikomeza ububasha zifite.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko y'icyo gihugu yafashe umwanzuro wo kwemerera Minisitiri w'Intebe, Viktor Orbán, gutegeka mu buryo bw'itegeko riteganyijwe, guhagarika inteko ishinga amategeko ndetse n'amatora no guhana abafatwa nk'abahaye amakuru y'ibinyoma ku cyorezo no ku buryo leta yakemuye icyo kibazo.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyagizwe intandaro y'ibihe byinshi by'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa, biturutse ku kwiyongera kw'ikoreshwa ry'ibikoresho ku rwego rw'isi mu kurwanya icyorezo, guhahira mu buryo bwo gutinya, no guhungabanya ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikoresho.
Ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika cyatanze imiburo ku kubura kw'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'uko abakiriya bayisaba cyane kandi n'abatanga imiti bakaba batabona uko bayitanga.
Mu duce dutandukanye kandi habayeho guhaha biturutse ku gutinya, byatumye amaduka atangira gusurwa n'ibikoresho by'ibanze nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amazi yo mu macupa, bituma ibikomere biboneka.
Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga mu buryo bwihariye cyagiye gitanga umuburo ku bijyanye no gutinda kohereza ibicuruzwa bya elegitoroniki.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, ibyo abantu bakeneye mu bihereranye n'ibikoresho byo kwirinda, byiyongereyeho incuro 100.
Ibi byatumye ibiciro byiyongera inshuro zigera kuri makumyabiri ugereranyije n'ibiciro bisanzwe kandi byanatumye gutangwa kw'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi gutinda mu gihe cy'amezi ane kugeza kuri atandatu.
Byatumye kandi habaho ikibazo cy'ibikoresho byo kwirinda ku isi hose, OMS ikaburira ko ibyo bizashyira mu kaga abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima.
Muri Ositaraliya, iki cyorezo cyatanze amahirwe mashya ku bacuruzi ba daigou yo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Iyi mikorere yatumye habaho ibura ry'ibiribwa by'abana mu masoko amwe n'amwe, nyuma biza kubuzwa na leta ya Ositaraliya. Nubwo umubare munini w'abanduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, ndetse n'uko hakenewe ibiribwa byinshi, ibi bice byombi byirinze ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zashyizweho n'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ububiko no gucuruza mu buryo butemewe n'amategeko ibicuruzwa by'ingenzi byagize ingaruka nziza, bituma habaho ibura ry'ibiribwa ry'ingutu ryari ryitezwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Amajyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani, aho umusaruro w'ubuhinzi uha agaciro, ntiwabaye kugabanuka cyane, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera nk'uko abahagarariye inganda babivuga.
Amashuka y'ibiribwa yari yashize gusa yagezeho by'akanya gato, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'u Bushinwa bashyiragaho ibicuruzwa by'inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage babone ibiribwa bihagije.
Mu Butaliyani na ho hari amategeko nk'ayo asaba ko abakora ibiribwa bagira ibyo babika kugira ngo babigenderemo mu gihe habaye ibintu nk'ibyo by'ingenzi.
Ubushinwa bwumvise ingaruka z'ubukungu bw'isi yose: dukurikije itangazamakuru ryo ku ya 16 Werurwe, ubukungu bw'u Bushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye cyane mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 bitewe n'ingamba zafashwe na leta zo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi, kandi ibicuruzwa byaho byagabanutseho 20.5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa ari igihugu cy'ubukungu bukomeye kandi gifite ibikorwa by'ubwikorezi, iki cyorezo cya virusi cyabonwe ko ari ikibazo gikomeye cyateza umutekano muke ku bukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo mu Kigo cy'Iperereza cy'Ikinyamakuru The Economist yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza guhindagurika kugeza igihe habonetse ishusho isobanutse y'ibishobora kuzayibamo.
Muri Mutarama 2020, bamwe mu basesenguye bagaragaje ko ingaruka z'ubukungu z'icyorezo ku iterambere ry'isi zishobora kurenga iz'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
Umuhanga umwe wo muri kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis, yavuze ko ingaruka z'iyo ndwara ku isoko ry'ibikoresho ku isi zashyizwe ku giciro cy'amadolari agera kuri miriyari 300, zishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Umuryango w'ibihugu bitumiza peteroli (OPEC) bivugwa ko "waguye mu kantu" nyuma yo kugabanuka cyane kw'ibiciro bya peteroli bitewe no kugabanuka kw'ibyifuzo by'Ubushinwa.
Amasoko y'imari ku isi yagabanutse ku ya 24 Gashyantare bitewe n'ubwiyongere bw'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge z'uko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyakwirakwira, ibipimo by'ibiciro bitandukanye by'imigabane ya Amerika birimo NASDAQ-100, S&amp;P 500 Index, na Dow Jones Industrial Average byerekanye ko byagabanyutse cyane kuva mu 2008, aho Dow yagabanutseho amanota 1,191, igabanuka cyane mu munsi umwe kuva mu bibazo by'imari bya 200708.
Ibipimo by'ibiciro bitatu byose byasoje icyumweru bimanuka ku kigero kirenga 10%.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yemeje igipimo cy'inguzanyo y'u Bushinwa, ariko ikomeza kugira Iterambere ribi.
Ibicuruzwa byongeye gucogora bitewe n'ubwoba bwa coronavirus, aho gucogora gukomeye cyane byabaye ku ya 16 Werurwe.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko ubukungu bushobora kuzashya.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu Mohamed El-Erian yashimye ingamba zafashwe n'amabanki nkuru y'igihugu n'ibihugu mu gihe cyagenwe.
Amabanki y'u Burayi yihutira gukora kurusha uko yabigenje mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'ubukungu ryo mu mwaka wa 2008.
Ubukerarugendo ni kimwe mu bice byahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye bitewe n'ibihano byo guhagarika ingendo, gufunga ahantu rusange harimo n'ibintu by'ingenzi bifasha ingendo, ndetse n'inama za leta zo kwirinda ingendo zose ku isi.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, kompanyi nyinshi z'indege zahagaritse ingendo kubera ko abantu batagishaka ingendo, harimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines, na Qantas, mu gihe kompanyi y'indege y'akarere yo mu Bwongereza Flybe yasenyutse.
Ingaruka byagize ku ruganda rw'ingendo zo mu nyanja, zari zigeze ku rwego rutari rwarigeze rubaho mbere.
Hari n'ibyumba by'amagare n'iby'amato na byo byafunzwe.
Iki cyorezo cyabayeho mu gihe cya Chunyun, igihe cy'ingenzi cyo gukora ingendo giherekejwe n'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa.
Ibikorwa byinshi byinjijemo imbaga nyamwinshi byahagaritswe na leta z'ibihugu n'iz'uturere, harimo iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya, aho ibigo byigenga na byo byigenga bifunga amaduka yabyo n'ibintu by'ubukerarugendo nka Hong Kong Disneyland na Shanghai Disneyland.
Ibirori byinshi by'umwaka mushya wa Lunar n'ahantu hakurura ba mukerarugendo hafungiwe kugira ngo hirindwe imikoranire y'abantu benshi, harimo Umujyi Utagatifu i Beijing n'ibirori by'insengero gakondo.
Mu ntara 24 kuri 31 z'u Bushinwa, abayobozi n'uturere, barongereye ikiruhuko cy'Umunsi w'Umwaka Mushya kugera ku ya 10 Gashyantare, bategeka ko ibigo byinshi by'akazi bitazongera gufungura kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Ibi bice by'igihugu byinjiza 80% by'umusaruro mbumbe w'igihugu na 90% by'ibyoherezwa mu mahanga.
Hong Kong yazamuriye igipimo cy'ubutabazi bw'indwara zandura ku rwego rwo hejuru kandi itangaza ko hari ibihe bidasanzwe, ifunga amashuri kugeza muri Werurwe kandi ihagarika ibirori by'umwaka mushya. Urwego rw'ubucuruzi rwarahuye n'ingaruka ku isi hose, aho amasaha y'ubucuruzi yagabanyijwe cyangwa gufunga by'agateganyo.
Abinjira mu masoko yo mu Burayi no muri Amerika y'Epfo bagabanutseho 40%.
Abacuruzi bo muri Amerika ya Ruguru no mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, bahuye n'izamuka rya 50 ku 60%.
Ibi kandi byatumye umubare w'abagenzi bagenda n'amaguru mu masoko ugabanukaho 33 ku ijana na 43 ku ijana mu kwezi kwa Werurwe ugereranyije n'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare.
Abashinzwe ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi mu masoko yo ku isi hose bashyizeho ingamba z'inyongera, zirimo kongera isuku, gushyiraho ibikoresho byo gupima ubushyuhe bw'abaguzi no guhagarika ibikorwa. Nk'uko raporo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ku bukungu bw'Amerika y'Amajyepfo igaragaza, icyorezo cy'icyorezo gishobora gutuma abantu bari hagati ya miliyoni 14 na 22 muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo bagwa mu bukene bukabije kurusha uko byari kuba bimeze iyo hatabaho icyorezo.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, mu gihe icyorezo cyari cyakwiriye cyane mu mujyi wa Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 5 mu Bushinwa batakaje akazi.
Abenshi mu bakozi b'abimukira bo mu cyaro bagera kuri miliyoni 300 bo mu Bushinwa, baheze mu byabo mu ntara zo hagati mu gihugu cyangwa baheze mu ntara ya Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miliyoni 10 batakaje akazi kandi basabye leta kubafasha.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora gutwara miliyoni 47 z'akazi muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika n'umubare w'abashomeri ushobora kugera kuri 32%, nk'uko bigereranywa na Banki y'Ikigega cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika. Itegeko rya guma mu rugo mu Buhinde ryasize abashomeri babarirwa muri za miriyoni z'abakozi b'abimukira b'Abahinde (bahembwa umushahara wa buri munsi). Iperereza ryakozwe n'ikigo Angus Reid ryatangaje ko 44% by'ingo zo muri Kanada zahuye n'ubushomeri runaka. Abakozi hafi 900,000 batakaje akazi muri Esipanye kuva yajya muri guma mu rugo hagati muri Werurwe 2020.
Mu gice cya kabiri cya Werurwe, abakozi miliyoni 4 b'Abafaransa basabye ko bahabwa inguzanyo z'ubushomeri bw'agateganyo naho miliyoni 1 b'Abongereza basaba inguzanyo rusange.
Gahunda yo guhemba abakozi bakora igihe gito mu Budage yakurikiwe n'u Bufaransa n'u Bwongereza.
