Ibizamini byo muri laboratwari ku ndwara ya coronavirus yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 bifitanye isano, harimo uburyo bwo kumenya ko virusi ihari n'ubw'imikorere yo kumenya abasirikare b'umubiri bazanwa n'ubwandu.
Kugira virusi mu bipimo byemezwa na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya coronavirus.
Iki kizamini ni kihariye kandi cyateguwe kugira ngo kibashe gutahura RNA y'agakoko ka SARS-CoV-2 gusa.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu buheruka cyangwa bukiriho.
Kugenzura abasirikare b'umubiri (serology) birashobora gukoreshwa haba mu gusuzuma no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri byerekana umubare w'abantu barwaye iyi ndwara, harimo n'abo ibimenyetso byabo byari bito cyane ku buryo batashoboraga kubivuga cyangwa abo nta bimenyetso bagaragaza.
Umubare nyawo w'abapfa n'ubwirinzi bw'umukumbi mu baturage ushobora kumenyekana hakurikijwe ibisubizo by'iki kizamini.
Kubera ko ibizamini byakozwe ari bike, muri Werurwe 2020 nta gihugu cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku burebure bwa virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu cyari kimaze gupima abaturage barenze 3%, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini cyane ry'uko ibizamini byakozwe mu bihugu bitandukanye.
Iri hinduka kandi rishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'abapfa, ishobora kuba yaragaragajwe cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Gukoresha uburyo bwa rRT-PCR (reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction) mu gihe nyacyo, ibizamini bishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe mu buryo butandukanye, harimo n'igiti cy'umwembe cyangwa icy'umwembe.
Ubusanzwe ibisubizo by'iyo miti biboneka mu masaha make kugeza ku minsi 2.
Igikorwa cyo gupima RT-PCR gikoreshwa mu gupima mu muhogo, kiba gifite icyizere mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'uburwayi.
Nyuma y'aho, iyo virusi ishobora guhera mu muhogo, ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye bapimwa mu cyumweru cya kabiri, ubundi buryo bwo gufata ibipimo bishobora gukurwa mu nzira y'umwuka yo mu buryo bwimbitse hakoreshejwe kateteri yo gukuramo cyangwa gukoresha ibipimo by'umuntu wakoroye (igishishwa).
Bimwe mu bizamini bya mbere bya PCR byakozwe muri Charité i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020 hifashishijwe ikoranabuhanga rya reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) mu gihe nyacyo, bikaba ari byo byashyizwe ku isoko n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) mu kugurisha udukoresho 250.000.
Ubwongereza nabwo bwari bwakoze igerageza ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo cya Kogenebiotech cyakoze ibikoresho byo gupima SARS-CoV-2 (PowerChek Coronavirus) byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi, bishingiye kuri PCR ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Igerageza kubona gen "E" ihuriweho na za beta coronavirusi zose, na gen RdRp yihariye kuri SARS-CoV-2.Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni imwe mu masosiyete ya mbere yahawe uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa na China's National Medical Products Administration ku gikoresho cyo kuvura SARS-CoV-2 gikoresheje PCR. Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara (CDC) kiri gutanga itsinda ryo kuvura Coronavirus nshya ya 2019-Novel Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) mu gihe nyacyo RT-PCR Diagnostic Panel mu mavuriro y'ubuzima rusange binyuze mu bikoresho mpuzamahanga by'ibisubizo.
Bumwe mu bushakashatsi butatu bwagenewe mu bwoko bwa kera bw'ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi bwatumye habaho ibisubizo bidatanga icyizere kubera ko hari ibyangombwa by'ubushakashatsi bitari byo, kandi hari ikibazo cyo gupima ku kigo CDC cyo muri Atlanta; ibi byatumye mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare 2020 hose, ibipimo by'abantu b'ibisanzwe by'abantu batageze ku 100 ku munsi bifatwa neza.
Ibizamini bikoresha ibice bibiri by'umubiri ntibyemejwe ko ari ibyo kwizerwa kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, kandi kugeza icyo gihe ni bwo leta n'ama laboratoire yo mu gace byemerewe gutangira ibizamini.
Iki kizamini cyemejwe n'ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura ibiribwa n'imiti mu rwego rwo gukoresha byihutirwa. Laboratwari zo muri Amerika zatangiye gukora ibizamini mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020.
Guhera ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko mu gihugu hose haboneka ibizamini bya COVID-19 bishingiye kuri RT-PCR.
Quest Diagnostics na yo yakoze ibipimo bya COVID-19 mu gihugu hose kuva ku ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta biciro by'ibimenyetso byatangajwe; gukusanya ibipimo no kubikora bigomba gukorwa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, ikizamini cya COVID-19 cyakozwe kandi gitangwa n'Ikigo cya Leta cy'Ubushakashatsi mu bijyanye n'ubumenyi bw'indwara n'ikoranabuhanga mu binyabuzima VECTOR.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ikizamini cyanditswe na Serivisi y'Igihugu ishinzwe kugenzura ubuzima. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, Mayo Clinic yatangaje ko yakoze ikizamini cyo gupima ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yabonye uruhushya rwa FDA rwo gukora ikizamini gishobora gukorwa mu masaha 3.5 mu buryo buhambaye, bityo ikoranabuhanga rimwe rikemerera gukora ibizamini bigera kuri 4.128 mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa (EUA) kuri Abbott Laboratories kugira ngo hakorwe igeragezwa ku buryo bwa m2000 bwa Abbott; FDA yari yigeze gutanga uruhushya nk'urwo kuri Hologic, LabCorp na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid na we yahawe EUA na FDA mu gusuzuma, byafashe iminota igera kuri 45.
FDA yemeje ikizamini gikoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kongera ubukana bwa aside ya nikleyiki mu mwanya wa PCR.
Kubera ko bidasaba ko habaho uruhererekane rw'imihindagurikire y'ibipimo by'ubushyuhe, ubu buryo bushobora gutanga ibisubizo byiza mu gihe gito nk'iminota itanu, n'ibisubizo bibi mu minota 13.
Kuri ubu muri Amerika hari imashini zigera ku 18,000, kandi Abbott iteganya kongera ingano y'imashini zo gukora ibizamini kugira ngo ishobore gutanga ibizamini 50,000 ku munsi. Hari ikizamini gikoresha umusemburo w'umubiri umwe w'umubiri wihariye uhuza n'umwimerere wa poroteyine ya nucleocapsid (N protein) y'agakoko gashya ka coronavirusi, kirimo gukorwa muri Taiwan, mu cyizere cy'uko gishobora gutanga ibisubizo mu minota iri hagati ya 15 na 20 kimwe n'ibizamini byihuse by'ibicurane.
Isuzuma ryakozwe muri Werurwe 2020 ryemeje ko "radio ya boxo nta kamaro kanini ifite mu gusuzuma indwara mu gihe cy'intangiriro, mu gihe ibyavuye muri CT [computer tomography] bishobora kugaragara mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira".
Ibimenyetso biranga CT harimo opacificities y'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri byinshi, by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri hamwe n'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri.
Uko indwara igenda ikura, ni ko igenda irushaho gukomera, igatera imbere mu buryo bw'inyongera.
Ubushakashatsi bugereranya PCR na CT mu mujyi wa Wuhan aho icyorezo cyatangiriye, bwagaragaje ko CT ifite ubushobozi bwo kumva cyane kurusha PCR, nubwo itabifitiye ubushobozi bwo kumenya neza, aho byinshi mu bimenyetso byayo bihuza n'ibindi bicurane by'ibihaha n'indwara.
Guhera muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika gishinzwe Imibare y'Ubumenyi bw'Ikirere gitanga inama ko "CT idakwiye gukoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa nk'igerageza ry'ibanze ryo gusuzuma COVID-19". Guhera muri Werurwe 2020, CDC itanga inama yo gukoresha PCR mu gupima ku ikubitiro.
Igice cy' ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri mu kurwanya indwara ni ugutunganya abasirikare b'umubiri barimo IgM na IgG.
Ibi bishobora gukoreshwa mu gutahura ubwandu ku bantu batangiye iminsi 7 cyangwa nyuma yo kugaragara kw'ibimenyetso, mu kumenya ubudahangarwa, no mu gukurikirana abaturage. Ibipimo bishobora gukorwa muri laboratwari z'ibanze (CLT) cyangwa mu gupima aho abantu bavurirwa (PoCT).
Sisitemu za automatike zifite ubushobozi bwo gukora cyane muri laboratwari nyinshi z'ubuvuzi zizashobora gukora ibi bipimo ariko kuboneka kwabyo bizaterwa n'umuvuduko w'umusaruro wa buri sisitemu.
Ku bijyanye na CLT, ikigereranyo kimwe cy'amaraso yo mu bice by'umubiri gikoreshwa cyane, nubwo ibipimo bikurikirana bishobora gukoreshwa mu gukurikirana igisubizo cy'ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri.
Ku PoCT, ikigereranyo kimwe cy'amaraso akenshi gikurwamo n'uko uruhu rwatobetswe.
Bitandukanye n'uburyo bwa PCR, icyiciro cyo gukuramo ntabwo gikenewe mbere yo gupima. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, FDA yashyize ahagaragara ibigo 29 byatanze raporo ku kigo nk'uko bisabwa, bityo ubu bikaba bishobora gukwirakwiza ibizamini byazo bya antibody.
Kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, hari igeragezwa rimwe gusa ryemewe na FDA mu gihe cy'ububasha bwo gukoresha byihutirwa. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics na Epitope Diagnostics yabonye ibyemezo by'i Burayi ku bikoresho by'igeragezwa byabo, bishobora kuvumbura abasirikare b'umubiri ba IgG na IgA bahangana n'agakoko mu bipimo by'amaraso.
Ubushobozi bwo gupima ni ibipimo amagana mu masaha make, bityo bikaba byihuta cyane kurusha ibipimo bisanzwe bya PCR bya RNA ya virusi.
Ubusanzwe abasirikare b'umubiri bashobora kuboneka nyuma y'iminsi 14 ubwandu butangiye. Mu ntangiriro za Mata, Ubwongereza bwabonye ko nta gikoresho na kimwe cyo gupima abasirikare b'umubiri bw'umubiri bwigeze bugura gifite ubushobozi bwo gukoreshwa.
Hong Kong yashyizeho gahunda aho abarwayi bakekwaho bashobora kuguma mu rugo, "urwego rwihutira ruha umurwayi urumuri rw'icyitegererezo", bararucaho, bararuboherereza kandi bakagira umusaruro w'ibizamini nyuma y'igihe. NHS yo mu Bwongereza yatangaje ko irimo kugerageza gahunda yo gupima abarwayi bakekwaho mu rugo, bikuraho ibyago by'uko umurwayi yandurira abandi mu gihe baje ku bitaro cyangwa agasaba ko imodoka y'ubutabazi ikoreshwa. Mu gupima COVID-19 mu gihe bikekwaho, umukozi w'ubuzima afata icyitegererezo yifashishije ingamba zo kwirinda zikwiye.
Ibigo by'ikoranabuhanga byafashije Koreya y'Epfo gukora bimwe mu bipimo byihuta kandi byimbitse kurusha ibindi bihugu byose. Mu Budage, Ishyirahamwe ry'Igihugu ry'Abaganga bafite ubwisungane mu kwivuza ryatangaje ku ya 2 Werurwe ko rifite ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini bigera ku 12.000 ku munsi mu buryo bwo gutembera kandi ko abantu 10.700 bapimwe mu cyumweru cyashize.
Ikiguzi cy'ubuvuzi cy'indwara iyo muganga ategetse ko hakorwa ibizamini, gitangwa n'ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima.
Nk'uko bivugwa n'umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Robert Koch, u Budage bufite ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini 160.000 mu cyumweru.
Guhera ku ya 19 Werurwe, ibizamini byo gutwara imodoka byatangijwe mu mijyi myinshi minini.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 umubare w'ibizamini byakozwe mu Budage ntiwari uzwi, kuko habonekaga gusa ibisubizo by'ibizamini byemeza ko umuntu yanduye.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe muri laboratwari bwagaragaje ko guhera mu cyumweru cy'imibarwa 12/2020, ibipimo bigera kuri 483,295 byasuzumwe kugeza mu cyumweru cya 12/2020 ndetse n'ibipimo 33,491 (6.9%) byasanzweho SARS-CoV-2. Muri Isirayeli, abashakashatsi bo mu bitaro bya Technion na Rambam bakoze kandi bagerageza uburyo bwo gupima ibipimo by'abarwayi 64 icyarimwe, mu guhuza ibipimo no gupima gusa mu gihe ibipimo byombi byasanzwe ari byiza. Muri Wuhan, laboratwari yo gupima ibyihutirwa ifite ubuso bwa metero kare 2000 yitwa "Huo-Yan" (mu Gishinwa: 火眼, cyangwa "Ijisho ry'umuriro" mu Cyongereza) yafunguwe ku ya 5 Gashyantare 2020 na BGI, ishobora gupima ibipimo birenga 10,000 ku munsi.
Kubaka byayobowe n'uwashinze BGI, Wang Jian, kandi byatwaye iminsi 5, imiterere yerekana ko abanduye muri Hubei bari kuzamuka ku kigero cya 47% kandi igiciro gihuye cyo gukemura gahunda ya guma mu rugo cyari gukubye kabiri iyo ubu bushobozi bwo gupima butaza ku murongo.
Laboratwari ya Wuhan yahise ikurikirwa na laboratwari za Huo-Yan i Shenzhen, Tianjin, Beijing na Shanghai, mu mijyi 12 yose yo mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 4 Werurwe 2020, ibipimo by'ibipimo bya buri munsi byari 50,000 ku munsi. Hari ibishushanyo by'ibanze, bihuza byinshi byasohotse na Origami Assays bishobora gupima ibipimo bya COVID19 ku barwayi bagera ku 1122 bakoresheje ibipimo 93 gusa. Ibi bishushanyo bihuje neza bishobora gukorwa muri laboratwari ntoya bidakeneye imashini ikora ibipimo by'amazi.
Muri Werurwe, ibura ry'ibipimo by'imiti n'ubwinshi bw'ibisubizo by'ibanze byabaye imbogamizi mu gupima abantu benshi muri EU no mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika.
Ibi byatumye bamwe mu banditsi bakora ubushakashatsi ku mabwiriza yo gutegura ibipimo bakoresheje ubushyuhe ku gipimo cya 98 °C (208 °F) mu gihe cy'iminota 5 kugira ngo bashobore kurekura ADN zo gupima izindi. Ku ya 31 Werurwe byatangajwe ko Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Abarabu zisuzuma abaturage benshi ku murwayi wa Coronavirus ku muntu ku kigero cy'undi gihugu, kandi ko ziri mu nzira yo kongera ibipimo kugira ngo zigere ku bantu benshi.
Ibi byakozwe binyuze mu guhuza ubushobozi bwo gutwara abantu benshi, no kugura laboratwari y'ubwinshi bw'abaturage ku rwego rw'abaturage muri Group 42 na BGI (ishingiye ku ma laboratwari yabo yo gutahura ibyago "Huo-Yan" mu Bushinwa).
Iyi laboratwari yubatswe mu minsi 14, ifite ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini bya RT-PCR ibihumbi icumi ku munsi, ikaba ari iya mbere ku isi muri iki kigero ikora hanze y'u Bushinwa.
Uburyo butandukanye bwo gupima bwibanda ku bice bitandukanye by'imiterere ya jenoside ya coronavirus bwakozwe mu Bushinwa, Ubufaransa, Ubudage, Hong Kong, Ubuyapani, na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryashyize mu bikorwa uburyo bw'Abadage bwo gukora ibikoresho byoherezwa mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, bidafite ubushobozi bwo gukora ibyo bikoresha.
Inyandiko y'ubuvuzi y'Abadage yasohotse ku ya 17 Mutarama 2020; porotoroli yakozwe n'Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara ntiyari iboneka kugeza ku ya 28 Mutarama, bituma ibipimo byari bihari muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika bitinda. Ubushinwa na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika byagize ibibazo mu kwizerwa kw'ibikoresho by'igerageza mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, kandi ibyo bihugu na Ositaraliya ntibashoboye gutanga ibikoresho bihagije byo gupima ibipimo bikenewe n'ibitekerezo by'impuguke mu by'ubuzima.
Ku rundi ruhande, impuguke zivuga ko kuba Koreya y'Epfo ifite uburyo bwo gupima abantu benshi byafashije mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya coronavirus nshya.
Ubushobozi bwo gupima, ahanini mu mavuriro yigenga, bwubatswe mu myaka myinshi na guverinoma ya Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Ryita ku Buzima ryasabye ko hakongerwa gahunda zo gupima abantu mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukana bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19. Ibisabwa byinshi byo gupima kubera ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu byatumye ibizamini bibarirwa mu bihumbi amagana mu mavuriro yigenga yo muri Amerika bidakora, kandi ibikoresho byo gupima no gupima bikoreshwa mu buvuzi bw'imiti byarangiritse.
Muri Werurwe 2020 Ubushinwa bwavuze ko bwagize ibibazo bijyanye n'ubuziranenge mu bikoresho byabo byo gupima.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe na CDC byari bifite "ibikosa"; leta yahise ikuraho inzitizi za bureaucratic zari zarabujije gukora ibipimo by'abantu ku giti cyabo. Esipanye yaguze ibikoresho byo gupima mu ruganda rwo mu Bushinwa rwa Shenzhen Bioeasy Biotechnology Co Ltd, ariko yasanze ibisubizo atari byo.
Isosiyete yasobanuye ko ibisubizo bitari byo bishobora kuba byatewe n'uko ibipimo byatoranyijwe bidakozwe neza cyangwa se kubera ko ibikoresho byakoreshejwe nabi.
Minisiteri ya Esipanye yavuze ko izahagarika ibikoresho byatanze ibisubizo bitari byo, ikabisimbuza ibindi byatanzwe na Shenzhen Bioeasy. 80% by'ibikoresho by'igerageza Repubulika ya Tchèque yaguze mu Bushinwa byatanze ibisubizo bitari byo. Slovakia yaguze mu Bushinwa ibikoresho by'igerageza miliyoni 1.2 byagaragaye ko atari byo.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Matovič yatanze igitekerezo ko ibyo bikoresho byajugunywa mu ruzi rwa Danube. Ateş Kara wo muri Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Turukiya yavuze ko ibikoresho by'igerageza Turukiya yaguze mu Bushinwa byari bifite "ubwandu bwinshi" kandi ko "bitabifashishijwe". Ubwongereza bwaguze ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 3.5 mu Bushinwa ariko mu ntangiriro za Mata 2020 bwatangaje ko ibyo bikoresho bitagikoreshwa.
Gupima, gukurikirwa no gushyira mu kato abageragejwe basanzwemo virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 no gukurikirana abahuye n'abageragejwe basanzwemo virusi ya SARS-CoV-2, byagize ingaruka nziza.
Abashakashatsi bakora mu mujyi wo mu Butaliyani witwa Vò, aho umuntu wa mbere wahitanywe na COVID-19 mu Butaliyani, bakoze ibizamini bibiri ku baturage bose bagera ku 3.400, mu gihe cy'iminsi icumi.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'abantu basuzumye bagasanga baranduye nta bimenyetso bagaragaje, kandi abanduye bose bavumbuwe bashyizwe mu kato.
Kubera ko ingendo muri komini zabujijwe, ibi byakuyeho burundu ubwandu bushya.
Kubera ko hakurikizwa cyane uburyo bwo gukurikirana abantu bahuye n'ubwandu, ingendo z'inzererezi, gupima no gushyira abantu mu kato, icyorezo cya koronavirusi cya 2020 muri Singapuru cyateye buhoro cyane ugereranyije n'ibindi bihugu byateye imbere, ariko nta mabwiriza akaze nk'ihagarika ku ngufu ry'amazu y'uburiro n'amaduka acuruza ibicuruzwa.
Ibikorwa byinshi byasubitswe, kandi Singapour yatangiye gukangurira abaturage kuguma mu rugo ku ya 28 Werurwe, ariko amashuri yongeye gufungura ku gihe nyuma y'ikiruhuko ku ya 23 Werurwe.
Ibindi bihugu byinshi na byo byagenzuye icyorezo binyuze mu gushakisha abantu bahuye na cyo, gukumira ingendo, gupima no gushyira abantu mu kato, ariko bigashyiraho ingamba zo gufunga abantu ku buryo budafite ingamba nk'izo muri Isilande na Koreya y'Epfo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe bwagaragaje ko ibihugu byagiye bigenzura cyane, ugereranyije n'umubare w'abapfuye, bifite umubare muto w'abapfa, wenda kubera ko ibi bihugu bifite ubushobozi bwo kumenya neza abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa cyangwa nta na kimwe.
OMS isaba ko ibihugu bidafite ubushobozi bwo gupima no kuba laboratwari z'igihugu zifite ubumenyi buke kuri COVID-19 zohereza abantu batanu ba mbere bagaragaye ko banduye na cumi ba mbere bagaragaye ko nta bwandu bafite kuri COVID-19 muri laboratwari 16 za OMS kugira ngo bapimwe.
Muri laboratwari 16 z'ubuvugizi, 7 ziri muri Aziya, 5 ziri i Burayi, 2 muri Afurika, 1 muri Amerika y'Amajyaruguru na 1 muri Ositaraliya.
Mu mbonerahamwe ikurikira, inkingi Ibisubizo by'ibizamini mu % by'ibizamini bigengwa n'uburyo ibizamini bikorwa mu gihugu.
Igihugu kigenzura abantu binjiye mu bitaro gusa kizaba gifite igipimo cyo hejuru cy'ibisubizo mu bipimo ugereranyije n'igihugu kigenzura abaturage bose, baba bagaragaza ibimenyetso cyangwa batabigaragaza, ibindi byose ni bimwe.
Gukaraba intoki, nanone bizwi nk'isuku y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gusukura intoki hagamijwe gukuraho ubutaka, amavuta, ibinyabuzima bito cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabune buri gihe mu "bihe bikomeye" mu gihe cy'umunsi bibuza ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'ubuhumekero na kolera, zanduzwa n'umwanda.
Abantu bashobora kandi kwandura indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nka kanseri cyangwa ibicurane, urugero, iyo batarakaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, ku mazuru cyangwa ku munwa (ni ukuvuga ku nkari z'amatembabuzi).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ingenzi harimo: mbere na nyuma yo gukora isuku, nyuma yo gukaraba umwana cyangwa kumuhindurira udupfukamunwa, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya na mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorakora inyama, ifi cyangwa inkoko.
Niba nta mazi na isabune bihari, intoki zishobora gukaraba ukoresheje ivu. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima ryifuza ko gukaraba intoki:
Mbere yo gutegura ibyokurya, mu gihe utegura ibyokurya na nyuma yaho.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura utwenda cyangwa gukaraba umwana wagiye mu bwiherero.
Nyuma yo guhekenya amazuru, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Nyuma yo gukora ku nyamaswa, ifunguro ry'inyamaswa cyangwa imyanda yayo.
Isuku y'amaboko mu buvuzi yerekeza ku bikorwa by'isuku bifitanye isano n'uburyo bwo kwivuza.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo guha umuntu umuti cyangwa kwivuza bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ubukana bw'indwara.
Intego y'ibanze yo gukaraba intoki ni ukweza intoki za virusi (bakiteri, virusi, cyangwa utundi tugingo duto dushobora gutera indwara) n'imiti ishobora gutera uburwayi cyangwa indwara.
Ibi ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakora mu bijyanye n'ibiribwa cyangwa mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi, ariko ni n'ingenzi ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kenshi ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'ibicurane, koronavirusi n'izindi ndwara zandura; gukumira indwara zandura zitera diareya; kugabanya indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero;
no kugabanya igipimo cy'impfu z'abana mu kubyara mu rugo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki byongerewe bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu biyongeraho gato.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bitewe n'indwara z'ubuhumekero n'iseru ushobora kugabanuka mu gihe hakozwe ihinduka ryoroheje mu myitwarire, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Iyi mikorere yoroshye ishobora kugabanya igipimo cy'abapfa kubera iyi ndwara hafi 50%.
Gushyiraho uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya ibyago byo kurwara isesemi ku kigero cya gatatu, kandi ibi bishobora kugereranywa no gutanga amazi meza mu duce dufite abaturage batishoboye.
48% by'igabanuka ry'ibyago byo kurwara isesemi bishobora kuba bifitanye isano no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bw'ingenzi kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda isesemi n'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye (ARI), nk'uburyo bw'ibanze bukorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage ku isi yose.
Indwara y'ibihaha, ARI ikomeye, ni yo mpamvu ya mbere ituma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu bapfa, ihitana abana bagera kuri miliyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Guhirwa n'umusonga byombi bihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 3,5 buri mwaka.
UNICEF ivuga ko gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero, bishobora kurokora ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kurusha urukingo cyangwa ubuvuzi ubwo ari bwo bwose, bikanagabanya umubare w'abahitishwa isuka hafi kimwe cya kabiri, n'uw'abahitishwa n'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye ku kigero cya kimwe cya kane.
Gukaraba intoki akenshi bijyana n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku mu rwego rwa gahunda z'amazi, isuku n'isukura (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki kandi birinda impetigo yandurira umuntu uyikoresheje umubiri.
Ingaruka mbi nke yo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutera kwangirika kw'uruhu bitewe no guhorana kw'uruhu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu gihugu cya Danemark mu mwaka wa 2012, bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutera indwara y'uruhu ituma umuntu agira ibisebe ku mubiri, bikabikururira ibisebe ku mubiri, kandi ibyo bikaba bikunze kugaragara cyane cyane mu bantu bakora mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi na byo bifatwa nk'imwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara yo guhora uhanzwe (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi ku munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa mu kugabanya ubwandu bw'indwara mu kanwa: nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero (gusuka, gusohora), nyuma yo gusukura umwana (guhindura impenure), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya na mbere/nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorana n'inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Mu bindi bihe, uburyo bukwiye bwo gukaraba intoki bugomba gukurikizwa kugira ngo hakwirindwe kwanduza indwara harimo mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igikomere cyangwa igikomere; nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa guhumura; nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'amatungo cyangwa gukora ku nyamaswa; na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, hari umubare muto w'abantu bakaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune.
Ubushakashatsi ku gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 mu mwaka wa 2015 bwerekanye ko, mu kigereranyo, 38.7% by'ingo zikoza intoki mu isabune. Ubushakashatsi bwo mu mwaka wa 2014 bwerekanye ko Arabiya Sawudite yari ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cya 97%, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ziri hagati na 77%, naho u Bushinwa bufite igipimo cyo hasi cya 23%. Ubu hari uburyo butandukanye bwo guhindura imyitwarire mu rwego rwo kongera imikoreshereze yo gukaraba intoki mu isabune mu bihe bikomeye. Gukaraba intoki ku itsinda ku bana biga ku masaha y'umunsi ni uburyo bumwe mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere bwo gushishikariza abana gukaraba intoki mu myitwarire yabo.
"Gahunda y'ibanze yo kwita ku buzima" yashyizwe mu bikorwa n'Urwego rw'Uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa by'imbonekarimwe byo guteza imbere ubuzima bw'abana n'amashuri.
Gucana udukoko kabiri mu mwaka, bigashyigikirwa no gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabune, no gukaraba amenyo buri munsi n'isuku y'amazi, ni byo by'ingenzi muri iyi gahunda y'igihugu.
Nanone kandi, rwatangiye gushyirwa mu bikorwa mu buryo bugira ingaruka nziza muri Indoneziya.
Gukuraho ibinyabuzima bito bito ku ruhu byongerwa no kongeramo amazi isabune cyangwa imiti yo gusukura.
Igikorwa nyamukuru cyisabune na detergent ni ukugabanya inzitizi ku muti, no kongera uburyo bwo kumeneka.
Amazi yonyine nta cyo ageraho mu gusukura uruhu, kubera ko ibinure n'indimu, ari byo bigize ibinyabuzima biba mu butaka, bidapfa kwihanganira amazi.
Ariko kandi, gusukura bifashishwa no gukoresha amazi mu rugero ruhagije.
Isabune ihamye, kubera ko ishobora gukoreshwa kenshi, ishobora kuba irimo mikorobe zaturutse ku zindi zo yakoresheje mbere.
Umubare muto w'ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko kwanduza za mikorobe mu isabune yanduye, byemeje ko bitashoboka kuko za mikorobe zirasukwaho n'umwanda.
CDC iracyatangaza ko "sabune y'amazi ifite ibikoresho byo kugenzura umuntu utamufashe mu ntoki ari yo ikwiriye gukoreshwa mu gutanga".
Imyenda irinda indwara ya za bagiteri yagiye itera abantu benshi bashyira imbere ibyo kwita ku buzima.
Kugeza ubu, nta kimenyetso na kimwe kigaragaza ko gukoresha imiti yo kwirinda cyangwa yo gukaraba indwara bihitamo ibinyabuzima byirinda imiti ya antibiyotike mu bidukikije.
Ariko, amasabune arwanya bagiteri arimo imiti isanzwe irwanya bagiteri nka triclosan, ifite urutonde runini rw'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima bugarana.
Bityo rero, n'ubwo amoko y'imiti itabasha kwanduza virusi atatoranywa n'amasabune arwanya bagiteri, ashobora kuba adafite akamaro nk'uko bivugwa.
Uretse imiti ikora ku ruhu n'imiti irinda uruhu, imiti y'ibikoresho by'ubuhanga ishobora kuba ikubiyemo acides (acide acétique, acide ascorbique, acide lactique) mu rwego rwo kugenzura pH, acide benzoic ikora ku mikorobe n'ibindi bikoresho by'uruhu (aloe vera, vitamin, menthol, extraits de plantes). Isesengura ryimbitse ryakozwe na Kaminuza ya Oregon School of Public Health ryagaragaje ko amasabune asanzwe agira ingaruka nk'amasabune yo mu rwego rw'abaguzi arwanya bagiteri mu kwirinda indwara no gukuraho bagiteriyo mu biganza.
Amazi ashyushye akoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki ntabwo ashyushye bihagije ngo yice mikorobe.
Iyo umubiri ufite ubushyuhe bwa dogere 37 ni bwo mikorobe zikura vuba cyane.
Ariko kandi, amazi ashyushye, arimo isabune arusha amazi akonje, arusha amazi arimo isabune gukuraho amavuta kamere abitse ubutaka n'uducurama.
Ariko kandi, mu buryo bunyuranye n'uko abantu benshi babitekereza, ubushakashatsi bwa siyansi bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye nta ngaruka bigira ku kugabanya mikorobe zanduza intoki.
Umuti wo gukaraba intoki cyangwa umuti wica udukoko mu ntoki ni umuti w'isuku y'intoki utari mu mazi.
Mu mpera za 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, imiti yo gukaraba intoki idafite amazi (ibizwi kandi nka alcohol-based hand rubs, antiseptic hand rubs, cyangwa hand sanitizers) yatangiye gukundwa cyane.
Byinshi biba bishingiye kuri isopropyl alcohol cyangwa etanol ifatirwa hamwe n'imiti yiyongera nka Carbomer (polymer ya acrylic acid) mu buryo bwa gel, cyangwa humectant nka glycerine mu buryo bw'amazi, cyangwa foam kugirango byoroshye gukoresha no kugabanya ingaruka zo kumeneka kwa alcohol.
Kongera hydrogen-peroxide itunganijwe byongera ingufu za antimicrobial. Imiti isukura intoki irimo nibura 60 kugeza kuri 95% bya alcool ni imiti ikora neza mu kwica mikorobe.
Imiti yo gusukura umubiri ikoresheje inzoga yica mikorobe, mikorobe zidashobora kwanduzwa n'imiti myinshi (MRSA na VRE), igituntu, na virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo virusi itera SIDA, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, vaccinia, ibicurane na hepatite) n'ibibyimba.
Imiti isukura intoki irimo 70% by'inzoga yica 99,97% (3.5 log kugabanyuka, bisa no kugabanyuka kwa 35 decibel) by'uducurama tw'udukoko turi ku ntoki nyuma y'amasegonda 30 nyuma yo kuyishyiraho no kuva kuri 99,99% kugera kuri 99,999% (4 kugeza kuri 5 log kugabanyuka) by'udukoko turi ku ntoki nyuma y'umunota 1 nyuma yo kuyishyiraho. Imiti isukura intoki igira ingaruka cyane ku mikorobe kandi igira ingaruka nke ku ndwara zimwe na zimwe.
Imiti isukura intoki irimo inzoga nta cyo ikora ku mikorobe z'ubwoko bwa norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), ari yo mpamvu ikunze gutera indwara y'umwijima yandura.Ibyo kugabanya ubwandu bw'intoki cyangwa kwisiga inzoga bigomba gukoreshwa kugira ngo intoki zose zimirwe neza cyangwa zirebe neza.
Imbere n'inyuma by'amaboko yombi n'ibice by'intoki hagati n'impande by'amaboko yose bikandagirwamo hafi amasegonda 30 kugeza amazi, ishu cyangwa gelye byumye.
Ibikoresho byo mu ntoki bigomba no gukaraba neza, ugakaraba mu biganza byombi. Ikigo cyo muri Amerika cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki ukoresheje imiti isukura intoki, cyane cyane igihe intoki zanduye bigaragara.
Gukoresha cyane izi ntungamubiri bishingiye ku buryo byoroshye gukoresha no kwicisha vuba ibinyabuzima bito cyane; ariko, ntibikwiye gusimbura gukaraba intoki neza keretse igihe nta mazi n'isabuni bihari.
Gukoresha kenshi imiti yo gusukura intoki irimo inzoga bishobora gutera uruhu gukama, keretse iyo mu buryo bw'imiti harimo imiti yo gukosora no/cyangwa imiti yo kongera ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri.
Ingaruka zo gusukura inzoga zishobora kugabanuka cyangwa se zikurwaho hifashishijwe kongeramo glycerine na/cyangwa ibindi bintu by'ubuhumekero mu buryo bw'ibyokurya.
Mu igerageza rya kliniki, imiti isukura intoki ikoreshwa n'inzoga irimo imyanda ihumura, ituma uruhu rugira umujinya kandi rukayuma cyane ugereranyije n'isabune cyangwa imiti yica mikorobe.
Indwara y'umwijima, indwara y'urwungano rw'amaraso cyangwa se kumva cyane inzoga cyangwa ibindi bintu biba biri mu bikoresho byo gukaraba intoki, ni gake cyane.
Kuba abantu batagira ubushobozi bwo gutera indwara y'uruhu y'abanduye, byaje kuba ingirakamaro ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'isabune n'amazi.
Nubwo ibikoresho bidakoresha amazi bifite akamaro, ntibikura mu ntoki ibintu by'ibinyabuzima, ahubwo birazica.
Niyo mpamvu imiti isukura intoki idafite ubushobozi nk'ubw'isabune n'amazi bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, kubera ko indwara zikiri mu biganza.
Ubusanzwe, ubuziranenge bw'imiti yo gukaraba intoki idafite inzoga, buva ku bisobanuro byayo n'uburyo ikoreshwamo, kandi mu mateka y'abantu, inzoga n'imiti ikoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki ntizavuzweho neza.
Vuba aha, uburyo bukoresha benzalkonium chloride bwerekanye ko bufite imikorere ya antimicrobial ihoraho kandi y'inyongera nyuma yo gukoreshwa, bitandukanye na alcohol, byagaragaye ko igabanuka mu mikorere nyuma yo gukoreshwa kenshi, bishoboka ko biterwa n'ibyago by'uruhu bigenda byiyongera.
Abantu benshi batuye mu miryango ikennye ntibashobora kubona isabune, ahubwo bakoresha ivu cyangwa ivu.
Ivu cyangwa ubutaka bishobora kuba ingirakamaro kurusha amazi yonyine, ariko bishobora kuba ingirakamaro cyane kuruta isabune.
Kimwe mu byo abantu bahangayikishijwe ni uko niba ubutaka cyangwa ivu byanduye n'udukoko duto duto dushobora gutuma indwara ikwirakwira cyane aho kugabanya.
Kimwe n'isabune, ivu na ryo ni umuti wo kwica udukoko, kubera ko iyo ryinjiye mu mazi, riba rifite umuti ufite ibara ry'ibinure.
OMS yateye inkunga abantu gukoresha ivu cyangwa umucanga mu mwanya w'isabune mu gihe itaboneka.
Uburyo bukwiye bwo gukaraba intoki bwasabwe n'ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara mu rwego rwo kwirinda kwanduzanya indwara burimo intambwe zikurikira:
Jya umesa intoki ukoresheje amazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Amazi atemba ni byiza kuyakoresha kuko amazi yo mu bibindi by'amazi ashobora kuba yanduye, mu gihe ubushyuhe bw'amazi busa n'aho nta cyo buhindura.
Gupfuka intoki ukoresheje isabune nyinshi, harimo inyuma y'intoki, hagati y'intoki no munsi y'imisumari.
Isuku ikura mikorobe ku ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko abantu bakunze gukaraba intoki cyane iyo bakoresheje isabune aho gukoresha amazi yonyine.
Jya uhanagura nibura amasegonda 20.
Gupfuka bituma habaho imvumbagatanya, bigatuma udukoko tuva mu ruhu, kandi gukaraba igihe kirekire bivanaho udukoko twinshi.
Jya ubiruhutsa neza mu mazi y'imigezi.
Gukaraba mu kibindi bishobora kongera kwanduza ibiganza.
Ujye ukaraba n'umwenda mwiza cyangwa ureke uhumeke.
Ibice bikunze kwibagirana ni urutoki, igitsike, ibice biri hagati y'intoki, n'ibiri munsi y'imisumari.
Ibumba rikozwe n'ipolishi y'imisatsi yafashwe n'ibumba bishobora kuba birimo mikorobe.
Akenshi, inama ni ugukoresha lotion y'amazi kugira ngo amaboko ataguma ashyushye; uruhu rwumye rushobora kwangiza uruhu, ibyo bikaba byongera ibyago byo kwandura.
Hari uburyo butandukanye bworoshye bwo gukaraba intoki mu gihe amazi n'isabune bitagaragara, urugero nko kuvoma mu nkono cyangwa mu nkono zifite imyanya ikwiye, cyangwa gukoresha ivu mu gihe bibaye ngombwa mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere. Mu bihe aho amazi ari make (nk'amashuri cyangwa mu bice by'icyaro mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari uburyo bwo kubungabunga amazi, urugero nka "tippy-taps" n'ubundi buryo bworoshye.
Tipy-tap ni ikoranabuhanga ryoroshye rikoresha igikombe gifashwe n'umugozi, n'uruhande rukoreshwa n'ikirenge kugira ngo usuke amazi make ku biganza n'isabune.
Gushishimura intoki neza ni ikintu cy'ingenzi mu mikorere yo kwita ku isuku y'intoki, ariko hari impaka ku buryo bwiza bwo gukaraba mu byumba by'isuku rusange.
Ubushakashatsi buragenda bwiyongera bugaragaza ko amakaramu y'amaboko arusha isuku ibyuma by'amashanyarazi bikoreshwa mu kwiyuhagira biboneka mu mazu menshi.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Westminster, i Londres, kandi bwatewe inkunga n'uruganda rw'amapapuro y'ipapiro ry'ipapiro ry'i Burayi, mu rwego rwo kugereranya ibyiciro by'isuku bitangwa n'ipapiro ry'ipapiro, ibyuma by'umwuka bishyushye by'intoki n'ibyuma by'umwuka bigezweho.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumisha intoki hakoreshejwe igikoresho cy'umwuka ushyushye, imibare yose y'udukoko twayongeraga ku gipimo cyo hagati ku ntoki ku gipimo cya 194% no ku biganza ku gipimo cya 254%.
Gushushishwa n'umushongi wa jet byagize ingaruka ku kwiyongera kw'umubare rusange w'udukoko dutera ku ntoki ku kigero cya 42% no ku biganza ku kigero cya 15%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumisha intoki ukoresheje agapapuro, umubare w'utunyabuzima twagabanutseho 76% ku bipimo by'intoki no ku maboko ku kigero cya 77%.Abashakashatsi kandi bakoze ibizamini kugira ngo hamenyekane niba hari ibyago byo kwanduzanya kw'abandi bakoresha imisarani n'ibikikije imisarani bitewe n'uburyo bwo kumisha.
Umwijima w'umwuka usukura, usuka umwuka mu cyumba ku muvuduko wa 180 m/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), washoboraga gusuka uturemangingo dutukura mu biganza no mu cyumba kandi bikaba byashobora kwanduza abandi bantu bakoresha imisarani n'ahandi hantu hari metero 2.
Gukoresha igikoresho cy'umwuka ushyushye usukura intoki, bituma mikorobe zikwirakwira kugera kuri metero 0.25 uvuye muri icyo gikoresho.
Amatafari y'ipapiro ntiyagaragaje ikwirakwira ry'ibinyabuzima bito. Mu 2005, mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwelt, uburyo butandukanye bwo gukaraba intoki bwaragenzuwe.
Nyuma yo kumisha intoki, habonetse ibi bikurikira ku mibare y'uducurama:
Hariho abahanga benshi batandukanye bakora ibyonsa by'amaboko, kandi ibyonsa by'amaboko byagereranyijwe no guhumura hamwe n'utubaro tw'impapuro.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje utwogoshi tw'intoki ni ubundi buryo bwo gukora urugendo mu gihe nta mazi n'isabune.
Umuti wo gusukura intoki ukoresheje inzoga ugomba kuba urimo nibura 60% bya alcool.
Gukaraba intoki mu buvuzi byatangiye gushyirwa mu mategeko nyuma y'igihe kirekire umuganga wo muri Hongiriya witwa Ignaz Semmelweis avumbuye akamaro kabyo (mu mwaka wa 1846) mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro.
Hari ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga bitanga amakuru ku buryo bibutsa abakozi bo kwa muganga gukaraba intoki mu gihe babibagiwe.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko iyo bakoreshejwe, umubare w'abandura wagabanutse.
Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bwa muganga bigomba kumara nibura amasegonda 15, hakoreshejwe amazi n'isabune cyangwa gel nyinshi mu gukaraba no gukaraba buri gice cy'intoki.
Ibiganza bigomba gukorakora hamwe n'amano afatanye.
Iyo hari ibizinga munsi y'amano, umuntu ashobora kubikuraho akoresheje akazuyazo.
Kubera ko mikorobe zishobora kuguma mu mazi ku biganza, ni ngombwa kuzisukura neza no kuzisukura ukoresheje agatambaro gasukuye.
Nyuma yo kumesa, agapapuro ko mu munwa kagomba gukoreshwa mu guhagarika amazi (kandi mu gihe bibaye ngombwa ugakoresha urugi rwo gusohokeramo).
Ibyo bituma amaboko atazongera kwanduzwa n'ibyo bintu.
Gucana intoki mu rwego rw'ubuzima ni ugukuraho mikorobe ("mikorobe") kandi ukirinda kuzanduza.
Ikinyamakuru The New England Journal of Medicine cyatangaje ko mu bigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi, abantu bakomeje kwibagirwa gukaraba intoki, aho abaganga n'abaforomo benshi bakunze kwibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bityo bakanduza uturemangingo duto.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki mu buryo bukwiriye hamwe n'indi myiteguro yoroheje bishobora kugabanya umubare w'indwara z'ibyorezo z'amaraso zituruka ku nkokora ku kigero cya 66%. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasohoye urupapuro rugaragaza uburyo busanzwe bwo gukaraba intoki no kuzisokoza mu nzego z'ubuzima.
Igishushanyo cy'amabwiriza y'iryo shyirahamwe ku isuku y'intoki, gishobora kuboneka ku rubuga rwayo kugira ngo rubanda rujye kubivugaho.
Ubushakashatsi buhuje n'ibyo bwakozwe na Whitby et al.
Ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bishobora gupima no kwemeza isuku y'intoki, niba bigomba kwerekwa ko byubahiriza amategeko.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) rifite "Ibihe bitanu" byo gukaraba intoki:
nyuma yo guhura n'amaraso/amazi y'umubiri
mbere y'uko umuntu akora isuku, kandi
nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.Kongera imiti yica udukoko mu isabune ("sabune z'imiti" cyangwa "zaburizi" (anti-microbial) " bituma umuti wo gukaraba intoki ugira ingaruka zo kwica.
Ibyo bikorwa byo kwica bishobora kuba byiza mbere yo kubagwa cyangwa mu turere turimo ibinyabuzima by'inzobere mu kuvura. Kugira ngo umuntu 'azamure' intoki mu gihe ari kubagwa, ni ngombwa ko agira igikoresho cy'amazi gishobora gukingurwa no gucibwa atagikoraho intoki, agakoresho gikorwamo umuti wa chlorhexidine cyangwa wa iodine, ibitambaro byanduye byo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kuzamura, n'umushongi wanduye wo gukaraba n'ikindi gikoresho cyanduye cyo gukaraba munsi y'imisumari.
Ibishushanyo byose by'amabuye y'agaciro byagombye gukurwaho.
Ubu buryo busaba ko umuntu akaraba intoki n'amaboko kugeza ku nkokora, ubusanzwe bimara iminota 2 ku 6.
Si ngombwa ko umuntu amara igihe kirekire cyane mu kwisiga (iminota 10).
Mu gihe cyo gukaraba, amazi yo ku maboko agomba kurindwa kugira ngo atagaruka mu biganza.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, intoki zikumishwa n'umwenda w'umwanda, hanyuma hakambikwa ikanzu yo gukaraba.
Kugira ngo wirinde ikwirakwira ry'uducurama, ni byiza gukaraba intoki cyangwa gukoresha umuti wica udukoko mbere yo kwita ku muntu urwaye na nyuma yo kumwitaho.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya indwara ziterwa na Staphylococcus mu bitaro, byagaragaye ko inyungu ikomeye yo gukaraba intoki yavuye mu bice 20% by'ibanze by'isuku, kandi ko inyungu nke cyane y'inyongera yabonetse igihe gukaraba intoki byongerewe hejuru ya 35%.
Gukaraba n'isabune isanzwe bituma umubare w'indwara z'ibyorezo z'udukoko zigera ku byorezo byanduza ibiribwa wiyongeraho inshuro zirenga eshatu ugereranyije no gukaraba n'isabuni irwanya udukoko. Kugereranya gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umuti urimo inzoga ukoresheje isabune irwanya udukoko mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 buri wese yagaragaje ko gukaraba ukoresheje inzoga byagabanyije ubwandu bw'udukoko ku kigero cya 26% kurusha isabune irwanya udukoko.
Ariko isabune n'amazi bifite akamaro kurusha imiti yo gukaraba intoki ikoreshwa mu rwego rwo kugabanya virusi ya H1N1 y'ibicurane A na spores za Clostridium difficile mu ntoki. Gushyira mu bikorwa ibikorwa byo kunoza isuku y'intoki mu bigo by'ubuzima bishobora kuba bikubiyemo kwigisha abakozi ku bijyanye no gukaraba intoki, kongera umubare w'imiti ikoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki ikoreshwa mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukana bw'ibicurane, no kwibutsa abakozi mu nyandiko no mu magambo.
Hakenewe ubushakashatsi bwinshi mu kumenya uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bw'ubutabazi bukora neza cyane mu bigo bitandukanye by'ubuzima.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune byemerwa ko ari uburyo buhendutse, bw'ingenzi mu kugera ku buzima bwiza, ndetse no mu mirire myiza.
Ariko, kubura amazi yizewe, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo z'abantu, mu mashuri no ku kazi, bituma kugera ku ngeso yo gukaraba intoki ku bantu bose bigorana.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro muri Afurika, ibyuma byo gukaraba intoki biri hafi ya buri bwiherero bwa bwite cyangwa bwa rusange ni bike, nubwo hari uburyo bworoshye bwo kubaka aho gukarabira intoki.
Ariko kandi, umubare muke w'abantu bakaraba intoki ushobora kuba ari ingaruka z'akamenyero gakomeye, aho kuba impamvu yo kubura isabune cyangwa amazi.
Guteza imbere no gushyigikira gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku byemezo bya politiki, guteza imbere ubumenyamuntu ku nyungu zo gukaraba intoki kandi bigatuma abaturage bahindura imyifatire yabo mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ibyo bikore neza, hakenewe kugenzura no gusuzuma.
Isuzuma ryakozwe ku bushakashatsi 70 ryagaragaje ko uburyo bushingiye ku baturage ari bwo bugira ingaruka nziza mu kongera gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, mu gihe ubukangurambaga mu rwego rw'imibereho y'abaturage bwo bufite ingaruka nkeya. Urugero rumwe rwo guteza imbere gukaraba intoki mu mashuri ni "Gukoresha Inshuro Zitatu" na UNICEF itera amashuri inkunga yo gufata ingamba zoroshye kandi zidahenze kugira ngo abanyeshuri bakoreshe isabune mu gukaraba intoki, kimwe n'ibindi bisabwa mu bijyanye n'isuku.
Iyo ibisabwa bigezweho byuzuye, amashuri ashobora kuva ku inyenyeri imwe akajya ku inyenyeri eshatu.
Kubaka ahantu ho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukaraba intoki bikorwa hagamijwe kugabanya indwara n'ubwandu bw'abana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo gukangurira abantu kugira icyo bahindura ku myitwarire yabo. Kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus cya 2019-20, UNICEF yashishikarije abantu gukoresha emoji yo gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwarebye ingano y'amafaranga y'isuku y'amaboko mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere mu bijyanye n'amafaranga y'amafaranga y'amafaranga y'amafaranga y'amafaranga y'umwaka (DALYs) yaburijwemo.
Ariko, isesengura rimwe ryerekana ko guteza imbere gukaraba intoki n'isabune bifite akamaro kanini cyane mu bijyanye n'ikiguzi ugereranyije n'ibindi bikorwa byo gukoresha amazi n'isuku.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'umuntu  cyane cyane ku bantu bafite ibibazo nk'ababyeyi bari bamaze kubyara cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse mu bitaro  bwa mbere bwemejwe mu kinyejana cya 19 n'abapayiniya babiri mu isuku y'intoki: umuganga w'Umudage witwa Ignaz Semmelweis wakoraga i Vienne muri Otirishiya na Florence Nightingale, "uwashinze ubuvuzi bwa none" mu Bwongereza.
Icyo gihe, abantu benshi bari bagitekereza ko indwara ziterwa n'umuyaga uhumeka nabi cyane witwa miasma.
Mu myaka ya 1980, ibyorezo bituruka ku biribwa n'indwara z'ibyorezo bituruka ku buvuzi byatumye Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitangira kurushaho guteza imbere isuku y'intoki nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020 byatumye ibihugu byinshi birushaho kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune kugira ngo umuntu yirinde indwara zandura.
Urugero, inyandiko zigaragaza "uburyo bukwiriye bwo gukaraba intoki" zashyizwe iruhande rw'ibikoresho bikoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki mu bwiherero rusange no mu bwiherero bw'amazu y'ibiro n'ibibuga by'indege mu Budage.
Imvugo ngo "kwiyuhagiraho" ikintu runaka, isobanura ko umuntu atemera ko ari we nyirabayazana w'icyo kintu cyangwa ko nta ruhare abifitemo.
Iri jambo rikomoka mu murongo wo muri Bibiliya wo muri Matayo aho Ponsiyo Pilato yogeje ibiganza bye ku cyemezo cyo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko ryabaye imvugo ikoreshwa cyane mu miryango imwe n'imwe yo mu Cyongereza.
Muri Macbeth ya Shakespeare, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki mu buryo bwo kwiyezaho ikizinga cy'ibitekerezo, agaragaza umutimanama we mubi ku bijyanye n'ibyaha yakoze kandi bigatuma umugabo we akora.
Byaragaragaye kandi ko abantu, nyuma yo kwibuka cyangwa gutekereza ku bikorwa bidafite ishingiro, bakunze gukaraba intoki kenshi kurusha abandi, kandi bakunze guha agaciro ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki cyane.
Byongeye kandi, abantu bemererwa gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gutekereza batyo, ntibakunze gukora ibindi bikorwa byo "kwisukura" mu rwego rwo kwishyura, urugero nko gukora imirimo y'ubwitange.
Amadini ategeka ko abantu bakaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku n'ubw'ikigereranyo. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, ukoresheje amazi ariko nta sabune yo gukaraba intoki, ni kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukaraba intoki byiganje mu madini menshi, harimo idini rya Bahá'í, idini ry'Abahindu, Tevelah na netilat yadayim mu idini ry'Abayahudi, Lavabo mu idini ry'Abakristo, na Wudhu mu idini ya Isilamu. Amadini na yo ategeka ko abantu bakaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku, cyane cyane nyuma y'ibikorwa runaka.
Idini ry'Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abisilamu, byategetse abantu gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero.
Nanone kandi, idini rya Hindu, irya Bouddha, irya Sikh, irya Judaïsme n'irya Islamu, rivuga ko umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kurya.
Ibikorwa byo kurwanya ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 ku kazi
Gucunga ibyago byo ku kazi ku COVID-19 ni ugushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kwirinda no kubungabunga ubuzima ku kazi mu gukumira ibyago byo kwirinda indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Uburyo bukwiye bwo kurwanya ibyago ku kazi buterwa n'aho akazi gakorerwa n'inshingano z'akazi, hashingiwe ku gusuzuma ibyago by'aho umuntu yanduye, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibyago by'abakozi ku giti cyabo bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima bw'abakozi (OSHA), imirimo itarimo ibyago byo kwandura cyane, ikora ku buryo buciriritse mu kazi, aho abantu n'abandi bakozi bakorana, bagirwa inama yo gufata ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kwirinda imyuka ihumanya mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, no gukomeza gusukura no gusukura imiterere y'akazi.
Imirimo ituma umuntu agira ibyago byo kwandura mu rugero ruciriritse harimo iyasaba guhura kenshi cyangwa guhura cyane n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba baranduye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye kubera ko bakomeje kwandura mu baturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibi birimo abakozi bagirana umubano n'abaturage muri rusange nko mu mashuri, ahantu h'akazi hafite umubare munini w'abaturage, hamwe na bimwe mu bicuruzwa bicuruzwa byinshi.
Gukurikirana ibyago by'iki cyiciro, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, harimo guhumeka hakoreshejwe ibikoresho byo guhumeka by'ubuziranenge, ibikoresho byo kwirinda guhumeka, no kuba ufite ibikoresho byo kwirinda ku giti cyawe mu gihe umuntu yaba yanduye COVID-19.
OSHA ifata abakozi bakora mu nzego z'ubuzima n'iz'ubucukuzi bw'abapfuye bagaragaye ku muntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19 nk'abafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, bikaba byongera ibyago byo kwandura cyane iyo abakozi bakora ibikorwa byo gukora ibyuma bitanga umwuka, cyangwa bagakusanya cyangwa bagakoresha ibipimo by'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19.
Ibikoresho byo kugenzura ibyago bibereye aba bakozi harimo inganda zikora nk'ibyumba byo guhumeka umwuka mubi, n'ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye bijyanye n'akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka zitandukanye mu kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutagira aho bajya kubera uburwayi, kubera ko bagomba kwita ku bandi, cyangwa batinya ko bashobora kwandura.
Ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi bishobora guhinduka, haba mu bijyanye n'ibintu bisabwa, n'uburyo bwo kubona ibicuruzwa (nk'ugura mu masaha y'akazi cyangwa binyuze mu gutanga cyangwa gutwara imodoka.
Amaherezo, kohereza ibicuruzwa mu bihugu byazahajwe cyane na COVID-19 bishobora kuhagarikwa. Gahunda yo kwitegura no guhangana n'indwara zandura ishobora gukoreshwa mu kuyobora ibikorwa byo kurinda.
Gahunda zireba ibipimo by'ibyago bifitanye isano n'ahantu hatandukanye h'akazi n'imirimo, harimo n'ibishobora guteza umuntu kwandura, ibyago bishobora guterwa n'abakozi mu rugo no mu baturage, n'ibyago bishobora guterwa n'abakozi ku giti cyabo, urugero nk'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Bagaragaza kandi ingamba z'uburyo bwo kurwanya izo ngaruka, ndetse n'ingamba zo guhangana n'ibibazo bishobora kuvuka bitewe n'uko indwara zateye.
Gahunda zo kwitegura no guhangana n'indwara zandura zishobora gukurikizwa mu nama z'igihugu cyangwa zo hasi.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo zirimo kugabanya ikwirakwira mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku zindi nzego mu byo batanga.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage aho ikigo kiri bugira ingaruka ku buryo bwo guhangana n'indwara.
Urwego rw'ubugenzuzi bw'ibyago ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane mu mutekano w'akazi no mu buzima kugira ngo bigaragaze uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyago binyuze mu gukora.
Aho ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora kuvanwaho, uburyo bwo kugenzura burusha ubundi kuba bwiza ni ubugenzuzi bw'ubwubatsi, bukurikirwa n'ubugenzuzi bw'ubuyobozi, hanyuma ku iherezo ni ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Ubugenzuzi bw'ubwubatsi burimo gutandukanya abakozi n'akaga gakomoka ku kazi, bidashingiye ku myitwarire y'umukozi, kandi bishobora kuba igisubizo cyiza cyane cyo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Ubugenzuzi bw'ubutegetsi ni impinduka mu mikorere y'akazi cyangwa mu mikorere bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho byo kwirinda (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidakora neza kurusha igenzura ry'ubwubatsi n'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha gukumira bimwe mu byanduza.
Ubwoko bwose bw'IBI bugomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku kaga bushobora guteza umukozi, bukagaragazwa uko bikwiye (urugero nk'imyumbati), bukagaragara buri gihe kandi mu buryo bukwiriye, bukagenzurwa buri gihe, bugakorwaho isuku, kandi bugasimburwa, hakenewe, kandi bukagurwa, bukasukurwa, bukabikwa cyangwa bukarimburwa mu buryo bukwiriye kugira ngo hatagira ubwandu buboneka.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima ku kazi (OSHA), akazi karimo ibyago bike cyane byo kwandura, usanga nta mishyikirano myinshi y'akazi bagirana n'abantu bose hamwe n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu zasabwe ku kazi kose harimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi neza, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kubahiriza amahame agenga uburyo bwo guhumeka harimo no gukinga inkorora no kwitsamura, gutanga ibitambaro no gushyiraho imyanda yo kujugunya imyanda, kwitegura gukora ku muhanda cyangwa guhinduranya imirimo mu byiciro iyo bibaye ngombwa, guca intege abakozi mu gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza gusukura no gusukura mu buryo busanzwe no kuvura indwara mu buryo bw'akazi.
Gushakisha no gushyira mu kato byihuse abantu bashobora kuba banduye ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi bantu bari aho bakorera.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga inama ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bagomba kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe basubiranye umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro, n'ibindi bimenyetso by'indwara mu gihe cy'amasaha 24 nibura batiriwe bakoresha imiti igabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti igabanya ibimenyetso, kandi ko gahunda z'ikiruhuko cyo kurwara zitangwa mu buryo buhendutse, ko abakozi bemererwa kuguma mu rugo kwita ku muntu wo mu muryango wabo urwaye, kandi ko abakozi bazi izo gahunda.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, akazi gashyize mu kaga abakozi bafite ubwandu bw'indwara karimo akazi gasaba guhura kenshi cyangwa guhura hafi y'abantu bari muri metero imwe na santimetero umunani (1,8 m) batamenyekanye cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye SARS-CoV-2 kubera ubwandu bukomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage aho bakorera, cyangwa kubera ko umuntu aherutse kujya mu mahanga ahantu hakwirakwira cyane COVID-19.
Aba bakozi bafite aho bahurira n'abandi bantu, nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo abantu benshi, ndetse no mu maduka. Ubugenzuzi bw'ubwubatsi kuri uyu n'abandi bakozi bafite ibyago byinshi harimo gushyiraho filteri z'umwuka zifite ubushobozi bwinshi, kongera ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, gushyiraho inzitizi zisanzwe nk'izirinda gukorora mu plastike, no gushyiraho idirishya ryo kwinjira mu modoka ku bakiriya. Ubugenzuzi bw'ubuyobozi kuri uyu n'abandi bakozi bafite ibyago byinshi burimo gushishikariza abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, gusimbuza inama imbonankubone, gushyiraho imirongo y'akazi, kureka ingendo zidakenewe ahantu hari icyorezo cya COVID-19, gushyiraho uburyo bwo gutangiza abakozi mu bihe by'impanuka, gutanga inyigisho n'amahugurwa mashya ku bibazo bya COVID-19 n'ingaruka zo kwirinda, guha abakozi ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bishobora kuba ngombwa mu gihe cyo gukora no gushyiraho uburyo bwo gukoresha ibikoresho birinda indwara, gutanga ubwiherero busanzwe bukenera isuku, gukaraba intoki, gukaraba intoki, kwambara udupira, no gukaraba mu maso n'abantu, hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho birimo, gushyira umukono ku bikenewe ku bantu, gukingira abakozi, gukoresha udupfukamunwa, no gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku kazi, harimo no kwiyuhagira imyanda, no gukaraba intoki, gukingira no kwiyereka imyanya, gukorana n'abakozi, no gukingira abantu mu gihe bahura mu gihe cyo guhangana COVID-19.
Abakozi bo muri iri tsinda ry'ibyago ntibakunze gukenera gukoresha imashini zifasha guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, uburyo bukwiye bwo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bagendera mu ndege harimo gutandukanya umuntu urwaye n'abandi intera ya metero 6, gushyiraho umwe mu bakozi w'indege ukorera umurwayi, no guha umurwayi agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumusaba kwisiga umunwa n'izuru akoresheje agafuka iyo akohereza cyangwa ashimura.
Abakozi bo mu ndege bagomba kwambara utwuma tw'iburyo tw'imiti dushobora gukoreshwa rimwe igihe bita ku muntu urwaye cyangwa bagakora ku mazi y'umubiri cyangwa ku bintu bishobora kuba byanduye, kandi bashobora no kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'inyongera mu gihe umurwayi afite umuriro, ikiniga gikomeza cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Ingofero n'ibindi bikoresho bikoreshwa rimwe bigomba kujugunywa mu gikapu kirinda ibyago byo kwanduzwa n'ibinyabuzima, kandi ibijumba byanduye bigomba gukurwaho hanyuma bigashyirwamo imiti. Ku by'ubwikorezi bwo mu mazi, harimo n'amato atwara abagenzi n'ibindi byambu bitwara abagenzi, uburyo bwo kwirinda ibyago burimo gusubika urugendo igihe urwaye, no kwigunga no guhita ubimenyesha ikigo cy'ubuvuzi mu gihe umuntu yaba yagize umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso igihe ari mu bwato.
Mu buryo bwiza, gukurikirana kwa muganga bigomba kubera mu cyumba cy'umuntu uri mu kato. Ku mashuri n'ibigo byita ku bana, CDC isaba ko bafunga mu gihe gito kugira ngo basukure cyangwa basese niba umuntu wanduye yari mu nyubako y'ishuri hatitawe ku cyorezo cyakwirakwijwe mu baturage.
Iyo hari ubwandu bw'icyorezo mu baturage bufite ingufu nke cyangwa buciriritse, ingamba zo gukumira intera zishobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa nko guhagarika ingendo, amakoraniro n'andi materaniro manini nko gukora imyitozo ngororangingo cyangwa amasomo ya korali cyangwa kurya muri cafeteria, kongera intera hagati y'imyanya, gutinda ku isaha yo kugera no kuva mu rugo, kugabanya abashyitsi batari ingenzi, no gukoresha ahantu hatandukanye ho gukorera ubuvuzi ku bana bafite ibimenyetso by'ibicurane.
Iyo hari ubwandu bukomeye mu baturage, uretse ingamba zo kwirinda kwegerana, hashobora gutekerezwa ku kurekura abantu mu ishuri igihe kirekire. Ku bakozi bashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bakora ibikorwa bisanzwe bya buri munsi, CDC ivuga ko ibyago byo guhita bifatwa nk'ibiri hasi.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bagomba guhura n'abantu bagaragaweho cyangwa bakekwaho kuba baranduye COVID-19 basabwa gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abaganga b'indembe, harimo no gukoresha ibikoresho bikwiye byo kwikingira.
Mu gihe habayeho guhura kwa hafi mu gihe bafashwe, abakozi bagomba gusukura no kuvura inzogera imyenda yabo y'akazi n'ibikoresho mbere yo kongera kuyikoresha bakoresheje isuku yo mu nzu cyangwa gukaraba, kandi bagakurikiza inzira zisanzwe zo gukoresha mu kubika no kurandura ibikoresho bya KWI byakoreshejwe no mu kubika no kumesa imyenda.
OSHA ibona ko abakozi bamwe na bamwe bakora mu nzego z'ubuzima n'iz'ububiko bw'abapfuye bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura.
Imirimo ishobora guteza ibyago byinshi byo kwandura ni nko gutanga serivisi z'ubuzima, gufasha, gukora muri laboratwari no gukora mu bikorwa by'ubwikorezi bwo kwa muganga, abahuye n'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye.
Ibi biba ibyago byo kwandura cyane iyo abakozi bakora ibikorwa by'ibyuka bitanga umwuka kuri, cyangwa bakusanya cyangwa bagafata ibipimo ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye.
Uburyo bwo gukora ibipimo bya aerosol burimo kubaga, gutangiza inkari, gukoresha bronchoscopie, bimwe mu bikorwa byo kuvura amenyo no gusuzuma amenyo, cyangwa gukusanya ibipimo by'umubiri.
Imirimo yo mu murenge itewe n'ibyago byinshi harimo abakozi bakora mu gutegura imirambo y'abantu bari bafite ubwandu bwa COVID-19 cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bari bufite ubwo bari bapfuye; iyo bakora autopsie, baba bari mu byago bikomeye cyane. Ibindi bigenzura ubuhanga mu rwego rw'izo nzego z'ibyago harimo ibyumba by'ubwiherero ku barwayi bafite COVID-19 cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bayirwaye, harimo n'igihe hakorwa ibikorwa byo gukora impapuro z'ubwandu.
Guhumeka byihariye bishobora kuba ngombwa mu bigo bimwe na bimwe by'ubuzima n'iby'ubufu.
Ibipimo bigomba gukoreshwa mu buryo bwo kwirinda bwo ku rwego rwa 3 rw'ubuziranenge mu by'ibinyabuzima.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (WHO) ryasaba ko abarwayi binjira bashyirwa mu byiciro bitandukanye byo gutegereza bitewe n'uko bakekwaho ko banduye COVID-19. Usibye ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'abantu, OSHA irasaba ko imyenda yo guhumeka ikoreshwa n'abakora mu metero 6 z'abarwayi bazwiho kuba barwaye cyangwa bikekwa ko barwaye SARS-CoV-2, n'abakora ibikorwa byo gukwirakwiza umwuka.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, NIOSH yemeje ko N95 isukura mu maso cyangwa irushaho igomba gukoreshwa mu rwego rwa gahunda yuzuye, yanditse yo kurinda imyanya y'ubuhumekero ikubiyemo gusuzuma ubwiza, amahugurwa, no gusuzuma kwa muganga.
Izindi bwoko z'ibikoresho byo guhumeka bishobora gutanga uburinzi bukomeye kandi bikongera ihumure ry'abakozi. OMS ntishyigikira kwambara imyenda y'umubiri, kuko COVID-19 ari indwara y'ubuhumekero aho kwandurira mu mazi yo mu mubiri.
OMS isaba ko abantu bakora isuzuma ry'abantu binjiye mu gihugu bakoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi gusa.
Ku bantu bakusanya ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, bita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 cyangwa babajyana nta buryo bwo kubarwaza bakoresheje, OMS isaba ko bambara agapfukamunwa, amadarubindi cyangwa agakingirizo, ikanzu n'utuboko.
Iyo umuntu akoze igikorwa cyo gukora indimu, agapfukamunwa gasimbuzwa akandi gakoreshwa mu guhumeka, nko gukoresha N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Bitewe n'uko ibikoresho bya PPE ku isi bidahagije, OMS isaba kugabanya cyane ibyo bikenewe binyuze mu kwifashisha uburyo bwo kwivuza hakoreshejwe telefoni, kurinda inzitizi z'umubiri nk'amadirishya adafite inenge, kureka gusa abantu bakora mu buryo butaziguye mu kwinjira mu cyumba cy'umurwayi wa COVID-19, gukoresha gusa ibikoresho bya PPE bikenewe ku bw'iyo mpamvu, gukomeza gukoresha icyo gikoresho cyo guhumeka nta kugikuraho mu gihe wita ku barwayi benshi barwaye indwara imwe, kugenzura no guhuza ibikorwa byo gutanga PPE, no guca intege abantu batagaragaza ibimenyetso byo gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
