b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni enzyme ifatirwa ku gice cyo hanze (cyitwa membrane) cy'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu matwi.
ACE2 irwanya ibikorwa bya angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) ikurura ingano ya angiotensin-II no kongera Ang ((1-7) bituma iba umuti utegerejwe mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 kandi ikora nk'aho virusi za koronavirusi zimwe zinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Ubwoko bw'abantu bw'iyi enzymes bukunze kwitwa hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ni metaloenzyme irimo zinc iherereye hejuru y'uruhu rw'imbere rw'umubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
ACE2 protein irimo N-terminal peptidase M2 domain na C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 ni poroteyine y'urwagashya ya poroteyine yo mu bwoko bwa I, ifite igice cyayo gikora enzymatically kigaragara ku isura y'uturemangingo mu bihaha no mu bindi bice.
Icyiciro cy'inyuma cy'umuriro cya ACE2 gicibwa mu cyiciro cy'inyuma cy'urwagashya n'ikindi kinyabuzima bita sheddase, maze poroteyine ishyirwa mu maraso igashyirwa mu myanya ndangabwonko.
ACE2 iboneka mu ngingo nyinshi: ACE2 ifatirwa mu mpyiko z'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibice by'ibihaha by'ubwoko bwa II, intanga ntoya z'inda, intanga z'inda z'amaraso n'intanga z'amaraso n'intanga z'uruhu rw'imitsi mu ngingo nyinshi.
ACE2 mRNA igaragara kandi mu gice cy'ubwonko, muri striatum, muri hypothalamus no mu gice cy'ubwonko.
Icy'ingenzi ACE2 ikora ni ugukomeza ACE.
ACE isenya hormone ya angiotensin I ikajya mu angiotensin II ifata imyanya y'amaraso.
ACE2 nayo isenya phenylalanine ya acide aminé carboxyl-terminal iva muri angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) maze ikayisukura mu cyitwa angiotensin (1- 7) cyongera ingano y'amaraso mu maraso (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora kandi gutandukanya peptides nyinshi zirimo [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi igena imikorere y'imiterere y'indangamubiri ya amino acide SLC6A19 kandi ikaba yaragize uruhare mu ndwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'imyororokere yo mu mubiri, ACE2 ikora nk'aho virusi za koronavirusi zinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV ( virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 ( virusi itera COVID-19).
Mu buryo bwihariye, guhuza poroteyine ya spike S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 n'urwego rwa ACE2 ku gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo ku isura y'ingirabuzimafatizo bituma habaho endocytosis no kwimura virusi na enzyme mu bice by'imbere biri mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Ubu buryo bwo kwinjira mu mubiri busaba ko poroteyine ya S ibanza guterwa na serine protease TMPRSS2, ubu ihagarikwa ryayo rikaba rigikorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'uburyo bwo kuvura. Ibi byatumye bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya urugero rwa ACE2, mu ngirabuzima, bishobora gufasha mu kurwanya ubwandu.
Icyakora, imiryango myinshi y'abashakashatsi n'inzego z'ubugenzuzi, zasabye ko hakomeza gukoreshwa imiti isanzwe yo mu bwoko bwa ACE n'imiti ya ARB.
Isesengura ry'imikorere n'isesengura ry'ibanze ryasohotse ku ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, ryagaragaje ko "gukoresha ACE inhibitors byateguwe n'igabanuka ry'ibipimo 34% mu ibyago byo kurwara pneumonia ugereranyije n'abagenzurwa".
Byongeye kandi, "ibyago byo kurwara umusonga byaragabanutse mu barwayi bavurwaga imiti igabanya ubukana bwa ACE bari bafite ibyago byo kurwara umusonga, cyane cyane abafite indwara y' imitsi yo mu bwonko n' umutima.
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors nabyo byari bifitanye isano no kugabanya urupfu ruterwa n'umusonga, nubwo ibisubizo byari bike ugereranyije n'ibyago rusange byo gusinzira umusonga".
Hemezwa ko ACE2 (rhACE2) yo mu muntu ikomatanyije ari uburyo bushya bwo kuvura igikomere gikomeye mu bihaha, kandi yagaragaye ko ishobora kongera umuvuduko w'amaraso mu bihaha no kongera umwuka wa oxygène mu ngurube z'inshira zifite ikibazo cy'ububabare bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bukomeye buterwa n'ibikomere byo mu mitsi.
Igihe cy'igice cy'ubuzima cya rhACE2 ku bantu ni amasaha 10 kandi igihe cy'imikorere ni iminota 30 y'inyongera ku gihe cy'ibikorwa (igihe) cy'amasaha 24.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bitandukanye byerekana ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti w'icyizere ku bantu batagikunda imiti ihindura imikorere ya renin-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa ku barwayi bafite angiotensin II iri hejuru.
Porogaramu za b'COVID-19 ni porogaramu zo kuri interineti zigenewe gufasha mu gushakisha abantu bahuye n'icyorezo cya koronavirusi cyo mu mwaka wa 2019-2020, ni ukuvuga uburyo bwo kumenya abantu ("abantu bahuye") bashobora kuba bahuye n'umuntu wanduye.
Hari porogaramu nyinshi zashyizweho cyangwa zasabwe, zishyigikiwe na leta mu turere tumwe na tumwe.
Ibikoresho byinshi byo kubaka porogaramu zo gukurikirana abahuye nabyo byatunganijwe.
Hari impungenge z'ibanga, cyane cyane kubijyanye na sisitemu zishingiye ku gukurikirana ahantu abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Bimwe mu bintu bishobora gutuma umuntu atabona telefoni ye, ni ugukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth kugira ngo amenye aho umuntu ari n'iyo ari.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko bizashyira hamwe imikorere yo gushyigikira izi porogaramu za Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu zabo za Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, guverinoma y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay, yashyizeho porogaramu ituma abaturage bamenya niba bahuye n'abantu bafite COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa mu mijyi irenga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore, porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether irimo gukoreshwa.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango w'ikoranabuhanga wo muri ako karere, yashyizwe ahagaragara nk'igitabo cy'umwimerere kandi izahabwa leta. Macedonia y'Amajyaruguru yatangije "StopKorona!", porogaramu ikoresha Bluetooth mu kumenya abantu bashobora kuba baranduye kandi igatanga igisubizo cyihuse ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'itumanaho n'ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kuva ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari itegereje kwemezwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, guverinoma yavuze ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu bari mu cyiciro cyambere cy'iterambere, kandi ko ishobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'iyo irateganywa muri Ireland, no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na New Zealand byombi biri gutekereza kuri porogaramu zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya Singapore ya TraceTogether na porogaramu ya BlueTrace. Uburusiya bufite intego yo gushyiraho porogaramu ya geofencing ku barwayi basuzumwe COVID-19 baba i Moscow, igamije kureba ko batagenda iwabo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu w'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yashyize ku rutonde ibibazo byinshi bishoboka byo gukoresha sisitemu ishingiye kuri porogaramu, harimo ibinyoma by'ukuri n'ubushobozi bushoboka bwo kudakora neza niba gukoresha porogaramu byigaruriwe gusa n'igice gito cy'abaturage.
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'impungenge ku ikwirakwira ry'ibya "coronavirus" biyobya cyangwa byangiza, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bwoko bw'imiryango ishobora kongeramo porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus kuri App Store yayo, ikazigera ku miryango "yemewe" gusa cyangwa indi ifite izina ryiza.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashinzwe umutekano w'ibanga bagaragaje impungenge ku bijyanye n'ingaruka zo kugenzura abantu benshi hakoreshejwe porogaramu za koronavirusi, by'umwihariko niba ibikorwa remezo by'ubugenzuzi byakozwe kugira ngo bikemure icyorezo cya koronavirusi bizasenywa igihe cyose iyi mpanuka izaba irangiye.
Amnesty International n'indi miryango isaga 100 yasohoye itangazo isaba ko ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura abantu bugabanywa.
Imiryango yatangaje ibintu umunani by'ingenzi ku mishinga ya leta:
igenzura ryagombaga kuba "ryemewe, rikenewe kandi rifite aho rihuriye n'amategeko";
kongererwa igihe cyo kugenzura no kugenzura bigomba kuba bifite ingingo z'igihe cyo guhagarika;
gukoresha amakuru bigomba kuba byigenzurwa gusa ku mpamvu za COVID-19;
umutekano w'amakuru n'ibanga bigomba kurindwa kandi bikagaragazwa ko birindwa hashingiwe ku bihamya;
ubugenzuzi bwa digitale bugomba kwirinda kongera ivangura no kwishyirwa ku ruhande;
gusangiza amakuru abantu b'abandi byaba bigomba gushyirwaho n'amategeko;
hagomba kubaho ingamba zo kwirinda ihohoterwa n'uburenganzira bw'abaturage bwo guhangana n'ibyo bikorwa;
"Kwifatanya mu buryo bw'ingirakamaro" n' "abaterankunga bose" byari gukenerwa, harimo n'abahanga mu by'ubuzima rusange n'amatsinda y'abantu bari ku ruhande. Ikigo cy'Abadage cy'Ikoranabuhanga mu by'Iterabwoba (CCC) n'Abanyamakuru batagira imbibe (Reporter ohne Grenzen) (RSF) na bo batangaje urutonde rw'ibisobanuro.
Igishushanyo cy'ishyirahamwe Google/Apple giteganya gukemura ikibazo cy'igenzura rihoraho mu gukura uburyo bwo gukurikirana mu bikoresho byabo igihe bitakiri ngombwa.
Ibihugu bimwe byakoresheje gukurikirana ahantu hashingiwe ku muyoboro aho gukoresha porogaramu, bikuraho ko ukeneye gukuramo porogaramu no ubushobozi bwo kwirinda gukurikirana.
Muri Israel, gukurikirana hifashishijwe ikoranabuhanga byemewe.
Ibibazo by'ibanga by'ibisubizo bishingiye ku muyoboro bifite amakuru y'ahantu ha mbere.
Ariko, sisitemu zose zifite seriveri nkuru zisabwa kubona amakuru yihariye; sisitemu nyinshi zo kurinda ubuzima bwite zashyizweho zikoresha seriveri nkuru gusa muburyo bwo gutumanaho (reba igice kiri hasi).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hakoreshejwe uburyo budashingiye kuri porogaramu mu gukora igenzura ry'abo bahuye.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, sisitemu yakusanyije amakuru yo gukurikirana kuva mu masoko atandukanye harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho bya mobile n'amakuru yo kugurisha ikarita, hanyuma ifatanya kugirango itange amatangazo binyuze mu butumwa bwanditse ku bantu bashobora kuba banduye.
Uretse gukoresha ayo makuru mu kuburira abantu bashobora kuba bahura na yo, leta yashyize ayo makuru y'aho umuntu aherereye ku mugaragaro, ibyo bikaba byemewe kubera ko amategeko agenga amakuru y'ibanga yarahindutse cyane nyuma y'uko icyo gihugu cyibasiwe na MERS.
Aya makuru aboneka ku bantu benshi binyuze muri porogaramu nyinshi na za website. Ibihugu birimo n'Ubudage byatekereje gukoresha uburyo bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, amakuru arambuye yari atarasohoka.
Gukurikirana abantu bakoresheje telefone kugira ngo bakomeze kugira ubuzima bwite ni igitekerezo cyashyizweho, kandi hari inyandiko nyinshi z'ubushakashatsi zanditswe kuva nibura mu mwaka wa 2013. Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'inzobere asaga 12 yakoraga ku bisubizo by'ibanga, nko gukoresha Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) kugira ngo igaragaze aho umuntu ari hafi y'izindi telefoni.
Ariko, PEPP-PT ni umuhate wo guhuza urwego rw'ibikorwa rufite uburyo bwo gukusanya amakuru rwagatijwe kandi rwagatijwe, kandi ntabwo ari porogaramu imwe. Porogaramu zidakurikijweho amabwiriza zirimo Decentralized Privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Imibare y'ibanze yo guhamagara (TCN, fka Contact Event Numbers, CEN), Porogaramu zo guhamagara mu buryo bworoshye no gukurikirana amakuru yo guhamagara (PACT) n'izindi.
Muri aya mabwiriza, amakuru yihariye ashobora kumenyekana ntabwo ajya ava mu gikoresho, kandi guhuza byose biba ku gikoresho.
Itsinda ry'ibanga rya MIT Media Lab ryagiye ritangiza SafePaths, urubuga rwo gukoresha uburyo bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite mu gihe cyo gukusanya no gukoresha amakuru y'ahantu cyangwa inzira y'ihurura mu gukurikirana ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Ishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu gitabo "Apps Gone Rogue: Gukomeza ubuzima bwite mu cyorezo" cyasohotse muri Werurwe 2020. Indi mihati nk'iyi ni urubuga rwa SafeTrace rwakozwe na Enigma MPC, isosiyete ikora tekinoroji y'ibanga nayo yashinzwe mu ntangiriro muri MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga ry'ibyuma bya mudasobwa kugira ngo abashobora gukoresha bakoreshe amakuru y'aho baba n'amakuru y'ubuzima bwabo, nta guhungabanya ubuzima bwite bw'ayo makuru.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, itsinda ry'isi yose rya TCN Coalition ryashinzwe n'amatsinda yari yafatanyije mu buryo bumwe kandi hakoreshejwe porotokori nyinshi, hagamijwe kugabanya ibice, no gutuma ibikorwa byo gukurikirana no kuburira porogaramu ku isi yose bikorana neza, ari na cyo kintu cy'ingenzi mu kugera ku ikoreshwa rya porogaramu ku rwego rwo hejuru.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Singapuru yatangaje ko yafunguriye isoko rya BlueTrace ikoreshwa na porogaramu yayo ya leta.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo bigenzura imikorere ya Android na iOS, byatangaje gahunda yo gukurikirana abahuye, bavuga ko bizatuma ubuzima bwite bw'umuntu burindwa, bishingiye ku ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth ry'imbaraga nke na cryptographie yo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite.
Banatangaje kandi ibiranga ikoranabuhanga rikoreshwa muri iyi gahunda.
Nk'uko Apple na Google babivuga, iyi gahunda igomba gushyirwa mu bikorwa mu byiciro bitatu:
Gushyiraho ibikoresho bizafasha za leta gukora porogaramu za leta zirinda ubuzima bwite mu gukurikirana virusi ya corona
Google na Apple bateganya gukemura ibibazo byo gufata no gukomeza kugenzura binyuze mu kubanza gukwirakwiza sisitemu binyuze mu kuvugurura sisitemu y'imikorere, hanyuma nyuma yo kuyikuraho mu buryo bumwe nicyorezo kimaze gushira.
b'Gusubiza imiti mu mwanya wayo (bikunze kwitwa guhindura intego y'umuti, guhindura imiterere, kongera gukora cyangwa guhindura uburyo bwo kuvura) ni ugusubiza umuti wemewe mu bindi bikorwa byo kuvura indwara cyangwa indwara itandukanye n'iyo yari igenewe mbere.
Ubu ni bumwe mu buryo bw'ubushakashatsi bwa siyansi bugikomeje gukorwa mu rwego rwo gushaka uburyo bwo kuvura COVID-19 mu buryo butekanye kandi bw'ingirakamaro.
Ubundi bushakashatsi burimo gukorwaho urukingo rwa COVID-19 no guterwa plasma. SARS-CoV-2 ifite poroteyine zigera kuri 66 zishobora kuvurwa, buri poroteyine ikaba ifite ahantu henshi ishobora gufatira.
Isesengura ry'izo migi ifitanye isano ritanga umushinga ushoboka wo gukora imiti yica virusi ikora neza ku binyabutabire bya COVID-19.
Muri poroteyine z'ingenzi cyane SARS-CoV-2 yibandaho ni nka proteine imeze nka papaine, RNA polymerase ishingiye kuri RNA, helicase, poroteyine S, na ADP ribophosphatase.
Hussein A, et al yize ku binyabutabire byinshi by'ibanze, nyuma y'ibyo, basuzuma kandi bagakora ubushakashatsi ku bushobozi bwabyo bwo kwihuza n'ibiyobyabwenge byemewe bihwanye cyane kugira ngo byihutishe ikorwa ry'umuti ukomeye wo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 mu bushakashatsi bwe bw'ibanze kugira ngo ujye utangazwa mu buryo bw'ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze.
Chloroquine ni umuti urwanya malariya kandi ukoreshwa no mu kurwanya indwara zimwe na zimwe ziterwa n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara.
Ku ya 18 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine bifitanye isano bizaba biri mu miti ine isuzumwa mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi rya Solidarity.
Guverineri wa New York, Andrew Cuomo, yatangaje ko igerageza rya Leta ya New York ku ikoreshwa rya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine rizatangira ku ya 24 Werurwe. Ku ya 28 Werurwe, FDA yatanze uburenganzira bwo gukoresha hydroxychloroquine sulfate na chloroquine phosphate hakurikijwe Uruhushya rwo Gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa (EUA).
Ubuvuzi ntibwemejwe n'ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cya Amerika FDA mu bijyanye n'igerageza ry'ubuvuzi kandi bwemewe n'ikigo cya Amerika cy'ubuvuzi gusa nk'ubuvuzi bw'igerageza ku bakiriya bari mu bitaro ariko badashobora kuvurwa mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi.
CDC yavuze ko "ikoreshwa, ingano, cyangwa igihe cya hydroxychloroquine mu kwirinda cyangwa kuvura ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2" bitarashyirwaho.
Abaganga bavuze ko bakoresha iyo miti iyo "nta bundi buryo" buhari.
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Turukiya i Istanbul barimo gukora ubushakashatsi ku ikoreshwa rya chloroquine ifatanyije na zinc, vitamine A, vitamine C na vitamine D.
Hari n'ubundi bushakashatsi bukomeye buteganyijwe muri kaminuza ya Duke na Oxford.
NYU Langone Medical School irimo gukora igerageza ku mutekano n'ubushobozi bwo gukoresha hydroxychloroquine mu buryo bwo kwirinda.
Ibizamini byo kwa muganga byo mu Bushinwa byakorewe i Wuhan na Shenzhen byavuze ko favipiravir "ikora neza cyane".
Mu barwayi 35 bo muri Shenzhen, ibizamini byaje kugaragaza ko nta bwandu bafite mu gihe cy'iminsi 4, mu gihe igihe indwara yamaze ari iminsi 11 ku barwayi 45 batigeze bayibona.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe i Wuhan ku barwayi 240 bafite umusonga, kimwe cya kabiri cyabo bahawe favipiravir ikindi cya kabiri bahawe umifenovir.
Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani gishinzwe imiti cyibukije abaturage ko ibimenyetso bihari bishyigikira uyu muti ari bike kandi ari iby'intangiriro.
Ku ya 2 Mata, u Budage bwatangaje ko buzajya bugura uyu muti mu Buyapani kugira ngo ujye uba mu bubiko, kandi bukoresha ingabo mu kugeza uyu muti ku bitaro bya kaminuza, aho uyu muti uzakoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikinyamakuru South China Morning Post, Shinzo Abe yagiriye inama ubuyobozi bwa Trump ku bijyanye no kugura uwo muti. Uwo muti ushobora kuba udakora neza cyane mu gihe umuntu arwaye cyane aho virusi yamaze kwiyongera.
Ntibyemewe ko uyu muti wakoreshwa n'abagore batwite cyangwa abagerageza gusama.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku muti witwa lopinavir/ritonavir (Kaletra), ukaba ari umuti urimo imiti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi yitwa lopinavir na ritonavir, bwageze ku mwanzuro w'uko "nta nyungu yagaragajwe".
