Ubuyobozi bw'Ibitaro bya Hong Kong bwabonye ko ubushobozi bw'ibihaha bwagabanutseho hagati ya 20% na 30% mu bantu bamwe na bamwe bakize indwara, kandi ibizamini by'ibihaha byerekanye ko hari ibice by'umubiri byangiritse.
Ibi kandi bishobora gutuma umuntu arwara indwara yo kuvurwa mu buryo bw'ibanze nyuma yo gukira.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, ntihari hamenyekana niba ubwandu bw'igihe cyahise butanga ubudahangarwa bwiza kandi burambye ku bantu bakize indwara.
Ubudahangarwa bwerekanwa nk'ubw'ibishoboka, bushingiye ku myitwarire y'izindi virusi za korona, ariko havuzwe ko hari abantu bakira COVID-19 nyuma bakagenzurwa bagasanga banduye koronavirusi.
Iyi ndwara ngo ishobora kuba ari iy'indwara y'igihe kirekire aho kuba yongeye kwanduza.
Iyi virusi bivugwa ko ari kamere kandi ko ifite inkomoko mu nyamaswa, binyuze mu kwandura.
Inkomoko nyayo ntizwi, ariko mu kwezi kwa 12 umwaka wa 2019 ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu ryari rishingiye hafi ku buryo bwose ku kwanduzanya hagati y'umuntu n'undi.
Ubushakashatsi ku barwayi 41 ba mbere bemejwe ko barwaye COVID-19, bwasohotse muri Mutarama 2020 mu kinyamakuru The Lancet, bwagaragaje ko itariki ya mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira ari 1 Ukuboza 2019.
Ibitabo by'ubuyobozi bya OMS byatangaje ko ibimenyetso byatangiye ku itariki ya 8 Ukuboza 2019.
Ingamba zitandukanye zikoreshwa cyane mu gupima umubare w'abapfa.
Iyi mibare iratandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe kandi igengwa n'umubare w'ibipimo, ubwiza bw'urwego rw'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kwivuza, igihe cy'ubwandu bwa mbere n'ibintu biranga abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima rusange.
Mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2019, OMS yashyize mu bikorwa kode y'indwara yihutirwa ya ICD-10 U07.1 ku bapfuye bazize ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwemejwe na laboratwari na U07.2 ku bapfuye bazize COVID-19 yafashwe mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi cyangwa mu rwego rw'ibyorezo idafite ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwemejwe na laboratwari. Umubare w'abapfuye ku barwayi ugaragaza umubare w'abapfuye ugabanijwe n'umubare w'abamaze kuvurwa mu gihe runaka.
Dukurikije imibare ya kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins, umubare w'abahitanwa n'icyorezo ku isi ni 6.9% (153,822/2,240,191) guhera ku itariki ya 17 Mata 2020.
Umubare uhinduka bitewe n'akarere. Ubundi buryo burimo igipimo cy'umubare w'abapfa (CFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abantu bapfuye bazize indwara, n'umubare w'abapfa bazize indwara (IFR), ugaragaza umubare w'abantu bapfa bazize indwara (bafite cyangwa badafite) bazize indwara.
Iyi mibare ntabwo ifitanye isano n'igihe kandi ikurikirana umubare runaka w'abantu uhereye ku kwandura ukageza ku gukira.
Nubwo atari abantu bose banduye bakwibonamo abasirikare b'umubiri, kuba hari abasirikare b'umubiri bishobora gutanga amakuru y'abantu banduye.
Mu mujyi wa Castiglione d'Adda, umujyi muto utuwe n'abantu 4600, ari na wo wabayemo icyorezo cy'iyi ndwara mu Butaliyani, 80 (1,7%) bamaze gupfa.
Muri Gangelt, iyi ndwara yakwirakwijwe n'ibirori bya Karneval, ikwirakwira mu rubyiruko, bituma umubare w'abapfa ugabanuka, kandi ntabwo abantu bose bapfuye bazize COVID-19 bashobora kuba barashyizwe mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi nk'abapfuye.
Ikindi ni uko mu Budage, gahunda y'ubuvuzi itarengewe n'imbaraga.
Mu Buholandi, abagera kuri 3% bashobora kuba bafite abasirikare, nk'uko byemezwa n'abatanga amaraso.
Abantu 69 (0.004% by'abaturage) byemejwe ko bishwe na COVID-19.
Ingaruka z'iki cyorezo n'umubare w'abapfa bitewe na cyo, biratandukanye ku bagabo no ku bagore.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani, umubare w'abapfa uraruta uw'abagabo.
Ibyago byinshi ku bagabo biba mu myaka 50 y'amavuko, aho icyuho kiri hagati y'abagabo n'abagore kigira icyuho mu myaka 90.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abagabo bapfa wari 2.8 ku ijana, naho uw'abagore ukaba 1.7 ku ijana.
Impamvu nyayo z'iri tandukaniro ry'igitsina ntiziramenyekana, ariko ibintu byo mu rwego rw'ibinyabuzima n'imyifatire bishobora kuba impamvu.
Itandukaniro ry'ubudahangarwa bushingiye ku gitsina, ikwirakwira ryoroheje ry'itabi mu bagore n'abagabo bagaragaza indwara z'indwara nk'umuvuduko w'amaraso ku kigero gito ugereranyije n'abagore, bishobora kuba byaragize uruhare mu izamuka ry'umubare w'abagabo bapfa.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abantu banduye ni abagabo, naho 72% by'abahitanywe na COVID-19 ni abagabo.
Kuva muri Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Amerika ntabwo ikurikirana amakuru ajyanye n'ibitsina ku banduye COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko indwara z'ibyorezo nka Ebola, SIDA, ibicurane na SARS zigira ingaruka ku bagabo n'abagore mu buryo butandukanye.
Abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima, cyane cyane abaforomo, ni abagore, kandi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyi virusi.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko izina ry'umwimerere ry'iyi ndwara ari "COVID-19".
Umuyobozi wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yasobanuye ko CO isobanura corona, VI isobanura virusi, D isobanura indwara, na 19 isobanura igihe icyorezo cyamenyekanye bwa mbere: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Izina ryatoranyijwe kugira ngo ryibagirwe ko ryerekeza ahantu runaka (urugero, mu Bushinwa), ku bwoko bw'inyamaswa cyangwa ku itsinda ry'abantu, mu buryo buhuje n'amabwiriza mpuzamahanga yo kwita izina agamije gukumira amazina y'abantu. Virusi itera COVID-19 yitwa coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
OMS ikoresha kandi "virusi ya COVID-19" na "virusi iteza COVID-19" mu itumanaho rusange.
Bombi, indwara na virusi, bakunze kubyita "coronavirus".
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cyabereye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'indwara byiswe "coronavirus" na "Wuhan coronavirus".
Muri Mutarama 2020, OMS yatanze amabwiriza yo gukoresha 2019-nCov na 2019-nCoV indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero nk'amazina y'igihe gito y'iyi virusi n'indwara hakurikijwe amabwiriza yo mu 2015 yo kudakoresha ahantu mu mazina y'indwara na virusi.
Amazina yemewe ya COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 yashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020.
Kubera ubushobozi buke mu byiciro bisanzwe by'ibicuruzwa, bamwe mu bakora ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga barimo gucapa ibikoresho byo kwita ku buzima nk'ibipfunyika mu mazuru n'ibice by'ibyuma bifasha guhumeka.
Urugero, igihe ibitaro byo mu Butaliyani byasabaga byihutirwa indangururamajwi ya ventilateri, kandi umutangaho ntiyashoboraga gutanga mu gihe cy'igihe cyasabwaga, uruganda rwo mu gace k'aho rwatangiriye rwahinduye uburyo bwo gukora no gucapa indangururamajwi 100 zasabwaga mu ijoro rimwe.
Nyuma y'uko COVID-19 itangiye, ibitekerezo by'uko habayeho umugambi mubisha, amakuru atari yo n'ibinyoma byatangiye kuvugwa ku nkomoko, ubukana, kwirinda, kuvura n'ibindi bintu by'iyi ndwara, kandi byatangiye gukwirakwira ku mbuga nkoranyambaga.
Abantu basa n'abashobora gukwirakwiza iyi virusi ku zindi nyamaswa zimwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ntibwabashije kubona ibimenyetso by'uko virusi yongeye kwiyongera mu ngurube, mu mpanga n'inkoko.
Nta miti cyangwa urukingo rwemewe mu kuvura iyi ndwara.
Ubushakashatsi mpuzamahanga ku nkingo n'imiti kuri COVID-19 burimo gukorwa n'imiryango ya leta, amatsinda y'abashakashatsi n'abashakashatsi mu by'inganda.
Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangije "Igerageza rya SOLIDARITY" rigamije gusuzuma ingaruka zo kuvura imiti ine ya virusi iriho ubu ifite ubushobozi bwo gukora neza.
Nta rukingo ruriho, ariko inzego zitandukanye zirimo gukora ubushakashatsi ku buryo rukingo rwashobora gutangwa.
Ibikorwa byakozwe mbere kuri SARS-CoV birimo gukoreshwa kuko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ACE2 receptor kugira ngo byinjire mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'abantu.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira bukorwaho ubushakashatsi.
Icya mbere, abashakashatsi bafite intego yo gukora urukingo rwa virusi yose uko yakabaye.
Gukoresha virusi nk'iyi, yaba idakora cyangwa yapfuye, bigamije gutuma umubiri w'umuntu uhita utangira guhangana n'ubwandu bushya bwa COVID-19.
Igitekerezo cya kabiri, inkingo z'utugingo, zigamije gukora urukingo rwizeza abasirikare b'umubiri kwirinda ibice bimwe na bimwe by'agakoko.
Ku bijyanye na SARS-CoV-2, ubwo bushakashatsi bwibanda kuri poroteyine ya S-spike ifasha virusi kwinjira mu cyiciro cya ACE2 cy'ingirabuzima fatizo.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni inkingo za nucleic acid (inkingo za DNA cyangwa RNA, uburyo bushya bwo gukora inkingo).
Inkingo z'igerageza z'imwe muri izi ngamba zose zigomba kugeragezwa kugira ngo harebwe niba zirakomeye kandi ko zifite akamaro. Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, igerageza rya mbere ry'ubuvuzi ku nkingo ryatangiye ku bantu bane bitangiye i Seattle.
Urukingo rurimo kode ya genetique itagira ingaruka igaragazwa mu mikorobe y'agakoko gatera iyi ndwara. Gukomeza kw'umubiri w'umubiri w'uburwayi byatangajwe nk'imbogamizi ishobora kuba ihari mu iterambere ry'urukingo rwa SARS-COV-2, ariko ibi ni ibintu bivuguruzwaho.
Kugeza mu kwezi kwa Mata 2020, hari amagerageza y'ubuvuzi arenga 300 arimo gukorwa.
Ibizamini birindwi byasuzumaga uburyo bwo kuvura malaria bwamaze kwemerwa, harimo n'ubw'ubushakashatsi bune ku ikoreshwa rya hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Imiti ikoreshwa mu kuvura virusi y'ibibyimba ni yo igize ubushakashatsi bwinshi bw'Abashinwa, aho mu bihugu 9 hakozwe igerageza rya gatatu ku miti ya remdesivir, biteganyijwe ko rizaba ryamaze gutangwa mu mpera za Mata.
Muri Mata 2020, hakomeje gukorwa isuzuma ry'iterambere ry'ubuvuzi ku rukingo rw'indwara ya COVID-19 n'imiti ishobora gukoreshwa. Imiti myinshi ya virusi irimo gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo remdesivir, chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir na lopinavir/ritonavir ifatanyije na interferon beta.
Hari ibimenyetso by'agateganyo byerekana ko remdesivir igira ingaruka, guhera muri Werurwe 2020.
Abaganga bagaragaje ko abarwayi bavurwa remdesivir mu buryo bufatika, bagira amajyambere.
Ibizamini byo mu cyiciro cya III birimo gukorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Chloroquine, yakoreshwaga mbere mu kuvura malariya, yasuzumwe mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, hagaragazwa ibisubizo by'ibanze.
Icyakora, hari abahamagara ko hakorwa igenzura ry'ubushakashatsi.
Inzego z'ubuzima zo muri Koreya n'u Bushinwa zisaba ko hakoreshwa umuti wa chloroquine.
Ariko, ikigo cya Wuhan Institute of Virology, nubwo gitanga inama yo gukoresha gramu imwe ku munsi, kivuga ko gukoresha dozi ikubye kabiri icyo gipimo, ari bibi cyane kandi bishobora kwica.
Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine ku bushake bw'abaganga bavura abantu barwaye COVID-19. Amabwiriza y'igitabo cya 7 cy'Abashinwa anashyiramo interferon, ribavirin cyangwa umifenovir mu kurwanya COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko ibipimo byinshi bya ribavirin bikenewe kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 ihagarikwe in vitro.
Nitazoxanide yagiriwe inama yo gukora ubundi bushakashatsi in vivo nyuma yo kugaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ibuzwa mu rugero ruto. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gutangiza poroteyine ya spike ya mbere ikorwa na serine 2 ya protease ya transmembrane (TMPRSS2) ari ingenzi kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 yinjire mu mubiri binyuze mu gukorana n'umukandida wa ACE2.
Ubushakashatsi ku miti ya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine irimo cyangwa itagira azithromycin ifite inenge zikomeye zatumye abaganga batemera iyi miti nta bushakashatsi bw'inyongera. Oseltamivir ntitera SARS-CoV-2 in vitro kandi nta ruhare ruzwi ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Icyorezo cya cytokine gishobora kuba ikibazo mu bihe bya nyuma bya COVID-19 ikomeye.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya cytocine. Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza agenga uburyo bwo kuvura na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa nyuma y'ubushakashatsi buto bwarangiye.
Ubu iri mu cyiciro cya 2 cy'igerageza ku rwego rw'igihugu mu Butaliyani nyuma yo kugaragaza umusaruro mwiza ku bantu bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
Ugihujwe n'ibizamini by'amaraso bya serum ferritin kugira ngo hamenyekane cytocin cystorm, igamije kurwanya ibyo bintu, bikekwa ko ari byo bitera urupfu kuri bamwe mu barwayi.
Umuvugizi w'indwara ya interleukin-6 yemejwe na FDA hashingiwe ku byigwa by'ibihe by'ibanze byo kuvura indwara ya Steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome yatewe n'impamvu itandukanye, CAR T cell therapy, mu 2017.
Kugeza ubu, nta bimenyetso by' amahitamo, by' ubugenzuzi byerekana ko tocilizumab ari umuti uboneka mu kuvura indwara ya CRS.
Gushyira mu bantu bakennye abasirikare b'umubiri b'abantu bakira COVID-19 abasirikare b'umubiri bakorerwa n'abasirikare b'umubiri bakira COVID-19 birimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'uburyo bwo gukingira butari ubw'inkingo.
Ubu buryo bwashyizwe mu bikorwa mu kurwanya SARS ariko nta musaruro wabaye.
Gucika virusi ni uburyo bwitezwe bwo gukora bwagufasha gukoresha imiti y'umubiri wa antibody mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2.
Icyakora, izindi nzego, nk' ubumara bugira ingaruka ku ngirabuzimafatizo bitewe n' ubwandu bwa za anticorps na/cyangwa phagocytosis, zishobora kuba zishoboka.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuvura hakoreshejwe abasirikare b'umubiri, urugero nko gukoresha abasirikare b'umubiri bavanze, burimo gukorwa.
Gukora serumu y'abarwaye bagaruye ubuzima, igizwe n'igice cy'amaraso y'abarwaye bagaruwe kandi irimo abasirikare b'umubiri bafasha kurwanya iyi virusi, bishobora kwiyongera kugira ngo byihutishwe vuba.
